NK129(to)001:1: // bla ma rog gi ban d+he shes rab 'od kyis
NK129(to)001:2: mdzad pa'i grub mtha' so so'i bzhed gzhung gsal bar
NK129(to)001:3: ston pa chos 'byung grub mtha' chen mo bstan pa'i
NK129(to)001:4: sgron me zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK129(to)001:5: sku gsum dbyer med rdo rje 'chang gi ngo bo nyid //
NK129(to)001:6: gdul bya'i don du mtsho chen mi yi gzugs 'dzin cing /
NK129(to)001:7: gang 'dul thabs kyis gdul bya'i don la skyo dub med //
NK129(to)001:8: rtsa ba brgyud par bcas pa'i bla ma rnams la 'dud //
NK129(to)001:9: rang bzhin spros bral mkha' ltar dag pa chos kyi sku //
NK129(to)001:10: gnyis med bde chen rol pa longs spyod rdzogs mdzad cing //
NK129(to)001:11: gdul bya'i don du yul dang mthun par cir yang sprul //
NK129(to)001:12: sangs rgyas gtso la gus pa mchog gis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK129(to)001:13: ston pa'i bstan pa dam chos gsung rab bcu gnyis dang //
NK129(to)001:14: bsgrub pa'i thabs mchog 'phags lam yan lag brgyad dang ni //
NK129(to)001:15: don dam spros med zhi ba mya ngan 'das pa'i chos //
NK129(to)001:16: skyob pa'i chos la gus pa mchog gis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK129(to)001:17: thub dbang slob ma 'phags pa nyan thos sde gnyis dang //
NK129(to)001:18: srid pa'i nyes bcom 'phags pa rang rgyal rnam pa gnyis /
NK129(to)001:19: slob dang mi slob rgyal ba sras kyi tshogs mchog ste //
NK129(to)001:20: dge 'dun che la gus pa mchog gis phyag bagyi'o //
NK129(to)001:21: gang gis shes rab mtsho chen mkha' la rab phyar nas //
NK129(to)001:22: ma rtogs log rtog the tshom d+r+wa ba kun bcad de //
NK129(to)001:23: shes bya'i gnas lugs ji bzhin khong du chud pa'i don //
NK129(to)001:24: rog gi ban de shes rab 'od kyis bshad par bya'o //
NK129(to)001:25: gang zhig thos bsam gnyis kyis sgro 'dogs ma bcad cing //
NK129(to)001:26: lta ba'i gnas lugs de nyid khong du ma chud par //
NK129(to)001:27: bdag ni bsgom chen yin zhes glen pa yus kyis rgyal //
NK129(to)001:28: don med 'dug bsran can gyi mi la mkhas pas khrel //
NK129(to)001:29: sgra tshad rig pas tshig don 'brel ba rab brtags te //
NK129(to)001:30: gzhung chen tha snyad tshig la mkhas par gyur na yang //
NK129(to)001:31: rang gi de nyid ma mthong go yul rkyang par 'jal //
NK129(to)001:32: tshig mkhan nga rgyal can la rtogs ldan rnams kyis khrel //
NK129(to)001:33: ji ltar mig gis bltas nas rkang pas bgrod pa bzhin //
NK129(to)001:34: thos bsam nyid kyis shes bya'i sgro 'dogs bcad byas pa'i //
NK129(to)001:35: man ngag snying po gdeng du bcangs te dben par sgom //
NK129(to)001:36: don mchog grub nas 'gro ba'i dpal mgon rin po che //
NK129(to)001:37: 'di ni thub pa'i sras mchog 'gro ba'i mgon po yin /
NK129(to)001:38: rjes 'jug rnams kyang de bzhin thugs la dgongs par zhu //
NK129(to)001:39: 'di na lha dang mi dang lha ma yin du bcas pa'i 'jig rten pa rnams kyi bdren pa /
NK129(to)001:40: ston pa rdo rje thub pa'i dbang po rnams kyis
NK129(to)001:41: legs par gsungs pa'i bstan pa mtha' dag gi don
NK129(to)001:42: mdo tsam du bsdus te chos spyi'i rnam par bzhag
NK129(to)001:43: pa dang / grub matha'i rim pa mdo tsam zhig brjod par bya'o /
NK129(to)001:44: de la spyir grub matha'i rnam par bzhag pa la don gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:45: gtan la dbab par bya ba'i yul shes bya'i chos bstan pa dang gcig /
NK129(to)001:46: shes bya'i yul 'dzin par byed pa shes byed skyes bu'i blo dang gnyis /
NK129(to)001:47: de gnyis gnyis su med pa shes bya'i dngos po'i gnas bstan pa dang gsum mo //
NK129(to)001:48: dang po gtan la dbab bya'i shes bya la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:50: yul de dag gi khyad par ro //
NK129(to)001:52: gzugs nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i bar gyi chos thams cad do //
NK129(to)001:55: rnam par dkar ba'i chos so //
NK129(to)001:57: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ye shes gtan la dbab pa'i mdo las /
NK129(to)001:58: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK129(to)001:59: rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin mod kyang //
NK129(to)001:60: rnam par dkar ba ma yin phyir //
NK129(to)001:61: ngas ni rnam par dkar ba bstan //
NK129(to)001:63: de la rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i chos zhes gang la bya na /
NK129(to)001:64: shes bya dngos po'i chos thams cad la /
NK129(to)001:65: rang rang gi mtshan nyid mi 'dra ba re re yod de /
NK129(to)001:67: chu'i mtshan nyid gsher ba la sogs pa'am /
NK129(to)001:68: bum pa'i mtshan nyid kha g.yel /
NK129(to)001:72: mchu 'phyang ba yin bya ba la sogs pa gzugs nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'am /
NK129(to)001:73: chos can dngos por snang ba thams cad la rang
NK129(to)001:74: gi mtshan nyid mi 'dra ba re re yod pa
NK129(to)001:76: khyab chung ba mi srid pa gsum dang bral ba'i
NK129(to)001:77: rang ldog rdzas su grub pa re re yod pa
NK129(to)001:78: yin no // 'o na de bas rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin na /
NK129(to)001:79: chos zhes ci byar ram snyam na /
NK129(to)001:81: chos can dngos po mtha' dag la /
NK129(to)001:82: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyis khyab par gnas pas
NK129(to)001:83: na rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i chos zhes bya
NK129(to)001:84: ste / des 'khor 'das kun la khyab par gnas so //
NK129(to)001:85: rnam par dkar ba'i chos ni /
NK129(to)001:86: khyad par du thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa
NK129(to)001:87: dngos sam brgyud nas thob par byed pa'i thabs gang
NK129(to)001:88: yin pa'o // de la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:89: brjod bya don gyi bdag nyid kyi chos dang /
NK129(to)001:90: rjod byed tshig gi bdag nyid kyi chos so //
NK129(to)001:91: de yang mdo sde rgyan las /
NK129(to)001:92: ji ltar mnam na rab bsgu ba //
NK129(to)001:93: myang na zhim pa'i sman bzhin du //
NK129(to)001:94: de bzhin chos kyang rnam gnyis te //
NK129(to)001:95: don dang yi ger shes par bya //
NK129(to)001:97: de gnyis kyi khyad par yang /
NK129(to)001:98: gang zhig ming dang tshig dang yi ge'i tshogs kyis dngos po dang /
NK129(to)001:99: zhen pa'i tshul gyis brda sprad par bya ba'i yul ni brjod bya don gyi chos yin la /
NK129(to)001:100: gang zhig don go bar byed pa'i ming dang tshig dang yi ge'i tshogs ni /
NK129(to)001:101: rjod byed tshig gi chos so //
NK129(to)001:102: brjod bya'i don gtan la 'bebs parabyeda pa /
NK129(to)001:103: rjod byed tshig gi chos la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:106: lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK129(to)001:107: chos rnams bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis su 'dus //
NK129(to)001:108: legs par gsungs dang de yi dgongs 'grel ba //
NK129(to)001:109: de yi dbang gis sh+aakya'i bstan pa 'di /
NK129(to)001:110: 'jig rten khams 'dir yun ring gnas par 'gyur //
NK129(to)001:112: de ltar sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po che 'di /
NK129(to)001:113: bka' bstan bcos gnyis kyis gtan la dbab pa la don lnga ste /
NK129(to)001:114: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de ji ltar mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i tshul dang gcig /
NK129(to)001:115: des chos ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul dang gnyis /
NK129(to)001:116: bstan pa ji ltar bsdus pa'i tshul dang gsum /
NK129(to)001:117: lha dang mi yul du ji ltar grags pa'i tshul dang bzhi /
NK129(to)001:118: chos de rnams kyi rnam par bzhag pa bstan pa dang lnga'o //
NK129(to)001:119: dang po ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK129(to)001:120: rgyas ji ltar mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i
NK129(to)001:121: tshul la 'dod pa mi mthun pa bdun te /
NK129(to)001:122: dang po nyan thos sde gnyis na re /
NK129(to)001:123: bskal pa grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags shing /
NK129(to)001:124: skye bo tha ma so so skye bor gnas pa zhig /
NK129(to)001:125: khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung ste /
NK129(to)001:127: gdan gcig gi steng du sa bcu non par byas
NK129(to)001:128: nas rdo rje gdan gyi spo la sangs rgyas pa
NK129(to)001:132: 'phags pa min yang pha ma dang //
NK129(to)001:133: nad pa dang ni chos smra dang //
NK129(to)001:134: skye matha'i byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK129(to)001:135: yon ni gzhal du med pa yin //
NK129(to)001:136: zhes pa'i don go bar bya'o //
NK129(to)001:137: yang mtshan nyid kyi theg pa chen po pa rnams na re /
NK129(to)001:138: ston pa 'dis thugs dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed /
NK129(to)001:139: bar du bya daka'i spyod pa sna tshogs kyi sgo
NK129(to)001:140: nas bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs bsags te
NK129(to)001:141: sa bcu rim gyis bsgrod nas /
NK129(to)001:142: tha ma sa bcu'i dbang phyug dam pa tog dkar
NK129(to)001:143: por sku skye ba bzhes nas lha'i ston pa mdzad
NK129(to)001:144: nas sangs rgyas kyis bskul pa'i sgra la brten nas
NK129(to)001:146: mdzad pa bcu gnyis mthar phyung nas sangs rgyas pa yin zer te /
NK129(to)001:147: mdo rgya cher rol pa nas rgyas par gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:148: yang gsang sngags yo ga pa rnams na re /
NK129(to)001:149: ston pa byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa la sogs pas thun mong dang mthun pa la /
NK129(to)001:150: khyad par du rgyal po don grub la dka' thub
NK129(to)001:151: kyi khog pa mi yul du bzhag nas sems 'og
NK129(to)001:152: min du rnam par snang mdzad chen por sangs rgyas
NK129(to)001:153: te / phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis byang chub pa lnga bstabs so //
NK129(to)001:154: de ltar sangs rgyas nas ri rab ri'i rtse mo
NK129(to)001:155: la sogs par yo ga gzhung dum bu bzhi la
NK129(to)001:157: slar mi yul du byon te /
NK129(to)001:158: dka' thub kyi khog pa zhugs nas //
NK129(to)001:159: rdo rje gdan gyi spo la sangs rgyas pa'i tshul bstan par 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:161: gtsang ma'i gnas ni rab spangs pa'i //
NK129(to)001:162: 'og min gnas ni nyams dga' bar //
NK129(to)001:163: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK129(to)001:167: rnal 'byor gzhung gi don grub nyid //
NK129(to)001:169: dka' thub dka' ba spyod pa'i tshe //
NK129(to)001:170: phyogs bcu'i sprul pa longs spyod skus //
NK129(to)001:171: byang chub lnga ldan dbang bskur nas //
NK129(to)001:172: 'og min nyid du don grub nyid //
NK129(to)001:173: sprul pa'i dka' thub khog pa ru //
NK129(to)001:174: ye shes snang mdzad tshul du gshegs //
NK129(to)001:175: ri rab rtse mor 'khor lo bskor //
NK129(to)001:176: de yang rtogs pa'i gzugs sku yin //
NK129(to)001:179: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa las /
NK129(to)001:180: 'adi'ang sprul pa nyag gcig yin par gsungs so /
NK129(to)001:181: ma h+aa yo ga pa rnams na re /
NK129(to)001:182: thub pa sems bskyed nas grangs med gsum du tshogs
NK129(to)001:183: bsags par bstan pa ni drang don yin gyi nges
NK129(to)001:184: don ltar na / dpal kun tu bzang po yab yum gyi mkha' mtshams nas /
NK129(to)001:185: rigs drug gi gnas su thub pa drug sprul pa bkyes nas /
NK129(to)001:186: rigs drug gi don mdzad pa yin la /
NK129(to)001:187: khyad par du mi'i yul du thub pa'i dbang po sh+aakya seng ge zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK129(to)001:188: sems can rnams yid ches par bya ba'i don du //
NK129(to)001:189: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul du sangs rgyas par bstan pa yin no zer ro //
NK129(to)001:190: de yang rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK129(to)001:191: rigs pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug ces bya ba /
NK129(to)001:192: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'thon to //
NK129(to)001:195: tha ma dga' ldan nas babs zer bden mod kyang /
NK129(to)001:196: byang chub sems dpa' dbang thob pa la 'gal ba med la /
NK129(to)001:197: nges pa na kun du bzang po'i thugs las sprul pa'o //
NK129(to)001:199: yang slob dpon zla ba grags pa dang /
NK129(to)001:200: skal ldan grags pa'i bzhed kyis /
NK129(to)001:201: ston pa 'di bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol nas sangs rgyas nas /
NK129(to)001:203: sprul pa'i sku sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya bar sangs rgyas pa'i tshul bstan pa yin la /
NK129(to)001:204: de bzhin du dus rtag tu 'tshang rgyas pa'i mdzad pa sna tshogs ston cing bzhugs par 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:206: bcom ldan 'das 'di bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol nas sangs rgyas nas /
NK129(to)001:207: 'dir sh+aakya'i rigs su skye ba ston par mdzad do //
NK129(to)001:209: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po ba na re /
NK129(to)001:210: de rnams kyang sems can gyi snang ba la 'gal ba med kyis /
NK129(to)001:212: chos thams cad byed pa po med par ye nas
NK129(to)001:213: sangs rgyas pa'i bdag nyid gnas pa yin pa la
NK129(to)001:214: / de ltar ma rtogs pas 'khrul pa'i rtsal sna tshogs su shar ba ni /
NK129(to)001:215: 'dod khams kyi lha gnyid log pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:216: de ltar 'khrul kyang don las g.yos pa med pa'i yon tan gyis /
NK129(to)001:217: sems can dbang po'i rim pa dang mthun par sku gsum gyi snang ba shar nas /
NK129(to)001:218: bstan pa'i sgo dang theg pa'i rnam grangs du mar bstan nas don byed pa yin no zer ro /
NK129(to)001:220: ye nas sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK129(to)001:221: nyid mngon sum gnas pa la /
NK129(to)001:222: grib ma gzugs kyi dpe bzhin de la rtog pa byung /
NK129(to)001:224: 'o na de rnams gang ltar 'thad snyam na /
NK129(to)001:225: blo chung dag khron pa'i sbal pa bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:226: rang gi 'thad phyogs su drangs nas /
NK129(to)001:227: gzhan dag sun 'byin pa dag yod de /
NK129(to)001:229: yang dag par na sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje dang /
NK129(to)001:230: mdzad pa'i rnam sprul bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK129(to)001:231: sems can rnams rang rang gi las dang /
NK129(to)001:233: snang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:234: de rnams gang yang 'gal ba med par shes par bya'o /
NK129(to)001:235: de nas chos nyid ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:236: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul dang /
NK129(to)001:237: 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul lo //
NK129(to)001:238: dang po rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul ni /
NK129(to)001:239: thub pas mdzad pa bcu gnyis mthar phyin pa ni gzhan don du shes par byas la /
NK129(to)001:240: bye brag tu chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i mdzad pa ni /
NK129(to)001:241: thub pa de lo nyer dgu la rab tu byung /
NK129(to)001:242: sum cu so lnga la mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas /
NK129(to)001:243: zhag bdun phrag bdun du chos ma gsung /
NK129(to)001:244: brgya byin gyis zhus pas ma gnang /
NK129(to)001:245: tshangs pas zhus pas gnang nas /
NK129(to)001:246: 'aka'a 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor ro //
NK129(to)001:247: de yang bka' 'khor lo gsum la de lnga lnga ste /
NK129(to)001:253: de yang bka' 'khor lo dang po ni /
NK129(to)001:255: rgyal po gzugs can snying pos yon bdag byas nas /
NK129(to)001:256: 'khor lnga sde bzang po la sogs pa la /
NK129(to)001:257: dus dpyid zla 'bring po'i tshes brgyad la sangs rgyas nas /
NK129(to)001:258: dbyar zla ra ba'i tshes brgyad kyi bar chos gsungs te /
NK129(to)001:259: lo bdun du zla ba gnyis kyis ma longs par chos gsungs /
NK129(to)001:261: nyan thos sde pa gnyis dang bstun nas /
NK129(to)001:262: gang zhig bdag med la chos bdag med bzung 'dzin don dam par yod par zhal gyis bzhes nas /
NK129(to)001:263: bden pa bzhi la lan bcu gnyis su gsungs pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:264: gnyis pa bka' 'khor lo bar pa mtshan nyid med pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo ni /
NK129(to)001:266: bya rgod phung po'i ri la /
NK129(to)001:267: rgyal po chos sbyin gyis yon bdag byas nas /
NK129(to)001:269: dus lo bzhi bcu zhe gnyis nas lnga bcu rtsa
NK129(to)001:270: bzhi'i bar du lo bcu gnyis su mdo shes rab
NK129(to)001:271: kyi pha rol tu phyin pa mngon par rtogs pa'i
NK129(to)001:273: snying po'i don gyi mdo shes rab snying po la sogs pa gzhung chung bcu gsum gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:275: rang bzhin spros bral theg pa chen po dbu ma'i lta ba gsal bar byas so //
NK129(to)001:276: gsum pa bka' 'khor lo tha ma ni /
NK129(to)001:277: don dam rnam pa nges pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo ste /
NK129(to)001:279: rgyal po rgyal byed kyi tshal la sogs par /
NK129(to)001:280: khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin la sogs pas yon bdag byas nas /
NK129(to)001:281: 'khor theg pa sna tshogs la mos pa la /
NK129(to)001:282: chos mdo dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa la sogs pa /
NK129(to)001:283: dus lo nga bzhi nas gya gnyis kyi bar du lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad du gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:285: theg pa chen po sems tsam gyi lta ba gsal bar byas so //
NK129(to)001:288: sems can rnams dngos po la zhen pa drang ba'i don du /
NK129(to)001:289: gzung 'dzin don dam par yod par zhal gyis bzhes pas /
NK129(to)001:290: de la theg pa chen po ba rnams yid ma ches te /
NK129(to)001:291: rtsod pa'i gnas su gyur to //
NK129(to)001:293: chos thams cad rang bzhin med par gsungs pas /
NK129(to)001:294: nyan thos rnams the tshom za zhing rtsod pa'i gnas su gyur pa la /
NK129(to)001:296: yod pa dang med par 'dod pa thams cad kyi mtshan nyid gtan la phab ste /
NK129(to)001:297: chos thams cad sems kyi 'char lugs tsam du gsungs bas /
NK129(to)001:298: kun yid ches ste rtsod pa bral ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:300: mdo dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa las /
NK129(to)001:301: bcom ldan 'das kyi dang po yul w+aa ra n+aa sir /
NK129(to)001:302: nyan thos kyi theg pa la yang dag par zhugs pa rnams la /
NK129(to)001:303: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi'i rnam pa bstan pas /
NK129(to)001:304: sus kyang ma bskor ba'i 'khor lo bskor te /
NK129(to)001:305: 'khor lo de bla na mchis pa drang ba'i don rtsod pa'i gnas lus gyur pa lags pa /
NK129(to)001:306: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos thams cad ngo bo nyid med pa nas brtsams te /
NK129(to)001:307: theg pa chen po la yang dag par zhugs pa rnams la /
NK129(to)001:308: stong pa nyid smos pa'i rnam pas /
NK129(to)001:309: chos kyi 'khor lo gnyiis pa bskor ro //
NK129(to)001:310: 'khor lo de bla na ma mchis pa /
NK129(to)001:311: drang ba'i don rtsod pa'i gzhir gyur pa lags la /
NK129(to)001:312: bcom ldan 'das kyis chos thams cad ngo bo nyid
NK129(to)001:313: ma mchis pa nas brtsams shing thog mar yod par
NK129(to)001:314: yang brtsam nas / theg pa chen po la yang
NK129(to)001:315: dag par zhugs rnams la legs par phye ba dang
NK129(to)001:316: yang brtsam nas / ldan pa / shin tu ngo
NK129(to)001:317: mtshar ba dang ldan pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo gsum
NK129(to)001:318: yang brtsam nas / ldan pa / pa bskor te
NK129(to)001:319: / chos kyi 'khor lo de bla na ma mchis
NK129(to)001:321: brtson pa'i gnas su gyur pa yang ma lags so zhes gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:322: de ltar bka' 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor ba la /
NK129(to)001:324: chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor ba de yang /
NK129(to)001:325: sangs rgyas kyi gsung gcig la gdul bya'i dbang po'i rim pas so sor thos pas yin zer /
NK129(to)001:327: ngas ni gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid gcig pu las ma gsungs na /
NK129(to)001:328: la las ni gzugs stong zhes bya bar thos /
NK129(to)001:329: la las ni gzugs mi stong zhes bya bar thos so //
NK129(to)001:331: dper na de bzhin sbrid bsangs bzhin gsung gcig sgra yis thams cad go zer ro //
NK129(to)001:332: de la yang 'gal ba med de /
NK129(to)001:333: yang dag par na sangs rgyas la gzugs dang sgrar snang ba med de /
NK129(to)001:334: gdul bya dag pa'i snang ba yin pas gang ltar byas kyang 'gal ba med do //
NK129(to)001:335: gnyis pa gsang sngags ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:339: mi ma yin pa'i gnas so //
NK129(to)001:342: gtsang ma'i rigs dag rab spangs pa'i //
NK129(to)001:343: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK129(to)001:350: ngo bo mtha' gsum las 'das pa /
NK129(to)001:351: ma spangs rgyan rdzogs gzhal yas khang /
NK129(to)001:352: yon tan lnga yi bdag nyid de /
NK129(to)001:353: gru bzhi spyi bor 'khyil snang ba'o //
NK129(to)001:355: gnas der chos sku skye ba med pa'i ngang las
NK129(to)001:356: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhal phyag gi rnam par
NK129(to)001:357: bstan nas / nges pa lnga ldan gyi tshul gyis /
NK129(to)001:358: gdul bya las dag pa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK129(to)001:359: rig pa 'dzin pa mchog gi 'khor rnams la /
NK129(to)001:360: rang rang gi skal pa dang 'tsham pa'i gsang sngags
NK129(to)001:361: kyi rgyud sde dpag tu med pa gcig gsungs so
NK129(to)001:362: // gnyis pa lha'i gnas su gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:363: 'og min der bsgrod par ma nus pa'i /
NK129(to)001:364: lha dang mi'i byang chub sems dpa' skal pa can rnams la /
NK129(to)001:365: 'og min gtsang ma rigs kyi lha gnas dang /
NK129(to)001:366: dbang sgyur gyi khang bzang dang /
NK129(to)001:368: lcang lo can gyi pho brang du /
NK129(to)001:369: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mang du gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:370: gsum pa mi'i gnas su gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:371: gong ltar du lha gnas gsum dang /
NK129(to)001:372: 'og min du bsgrod par mi nus pa'i /
NK129(to)001:373: mii'i gang zag skal pa can rnams kyi don du /
NK129(to)001:374: ston pa sprul pa'i sku de nyid /
NK129(to)001:375: longs sku rdo rje 'chang du bzhengs nas /
NK129(to)001:377: 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u khri drug stong pa gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:378: bsil ba'i tshal la sogs par kri ya'i rgyud mang du gsungs /
NK129(to)001:379: rgyul po in+t+ra bo d+hi'i pho brang du /
NK129(to)001:380: 'og min du gsungs pa'i sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor ldabs pa'i tshul du gsungs zhing /
NK129(to)001:381: gzhan yang gsang sngags ma rgyud mang du gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:382: bzhi pa mi ma yin pa'i gnas su gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:383: phyag na rdo rje'i rgyud phal cher dang /
NK129(to)001:384: rdo rje phur ba'i rgyud mang du gnod sbyin gyi gnas su gsungs /
NK129(to)001:386: 'jigs byed la sogs pa gshin rje'i gnas su gsungs pa dang /
NK129(to)001:388: dpal dam pa la sogs pa srin po'i grong khyer dga' ba can du gsungs pa la /
NK129(to)001:389: rtogs pa'i rgyal po'i rgyud rnams klu'i gnas su gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:390: gsum pa bstan pa ji ltar bsdus pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:391: gang zag gang gis bsdus pa dang /
NK129(to)001:394: dang po gang zag gang gis bsdus pa la lugs gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:395: theg pa chung ba rnams na re /
NK129(to)001:396: 'dul ba thams cad nye ba 'khor gyis bsdus /
NK129(to)001:397: mdo sde thams cad kun dga' bos bsdus /
NK129(to)001:398: mngon pa thams cad 'od srung sgres pos bsdus zer ro //
NK129(to)001:399: theg pa chen po ltar na /
NK129(to)001:400: rgyal po'i khab kyi lho phyogs /
NK129(to)001:401: bi ma la sam b+ha ba zhes bya ba'i ri yon tan dang ldan pa zhig yod pa der /
NK129(to)001:402: byang chub sems dpa' bye ba phrag bcu gcig 'dus nas /
NK129(to)001:403: chos kyi mdzod chen po 'bum phrag bcu bsdus te /
NK129(to)001:406: mngon pa byams pas bsdus pa 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:407: de'i dus su tshig tu bsdus nas yi ge la ma gtab bo //
NK129(to)001:408: gnyis pa dus ji tsam na bsdus pa ni /
NK129(to)001:409: bka' bsdu ba dang po ni /
NK129(to)001:410: ston pa 'das pa'i phyi lo de la /
NK129(to)001:411: rgyal po ma skyes dgras yon bdag byas nas /
NK129(to)001:412: a su ra'i brag phug tu /
NK129(to)001:413: dgra bcom pa lnga brgyas bsdus na'ang yi ge la ma gtab bo //
NK129(to)001:414: bka' bsdu ba gnyis pa ni /
NK129(to)001:415: ston pa 'das nas lo nyis brgya na /
NK129(to)001:416: rgyal po d+ha m+aa r+aa dza a sho ka'i /
NK129(to)001:417: bya gag gi kun dga' rwa bar /
NK129(to)001:418: dgra bcom pa lnga brgyas bsdus so //
NK129(to)001:419: de'itshe'ang yi ge la ma gtab bo //
NK129(to)001:420: bka' bsdu ba gsum pa ni /
NK129(to)001:421: ston pa 'das nas lo sum brgya na /
NK129(to)001:422: rgyal po ka ni ka'i drin las kha che'i yul
NK129(to)001:423: kun dga' rwa ba zhes dgon pa dza lan d+ha
NK129(to)001:425: dgra bcom pa lnga brgya dang /
NK129(to)001:426: ba su mi tra la sogs pa byang chub sems dpa' dpa' lnga brgya dang /
NK129(to)001:427: so so skye bo sgra don la mkhas pa nyis brgya lnga bcus bsdus nas /
NK129(to)001:428: so so skye bo mi brjed pa'i gzungs ma thob pa rnams kyis /
NK129(to)001:429: bka' lhag chad du 'don pa rnams kyi don du yi ger gtab bo zhes grags so //
NK129(to)001:430: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams ni nges par phyag na rdo rje kho nas bsdus te /
NK129(to)001:431: ye shes thig le'i rgyud las /
NK129(to)001:432: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su yang dag pa'i rgyud gsungs pa rnams /
NK129(to)001:433: skal ba dang ldan pa'i sems can la sus bshad pa byed par 'gyur /
NK129(to)001:436: phyag na rdo rje mgon pos bshad pa byed pa'o //
NK129(to)001:438: tshul ji ltar bsdus pa ni /
NK129(to)001:439: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong ji snyed gcig bka' stsal ba rnams /
NK129(to)001:440: don bzhir bsdus te gnyen po la dgongs te rgyas par bka' stsal ba dang /
NK129(to)001:441: dbye ba la dgongs nas 'bring du bka' stsal ba dang /
NK129(to)001:442: bsdu ba la dgongs nas bsdus te bka' stsal ba dang /
NK129(to)001:443: gang zag gi dbang po la dgongs nas theg pa'i rim par bka' stsal ba'o //
NK129(to)001:444: dang po gnyen po la dgongs nas rgyas par bka' stsal ba ni /
NK129(to)001:445: 'dod chags kyi gnyen por 'dul pa nyi khri chig stong ste /
NK129(to)001:446: zhe sdang gi gnyen por mdo sde nyi khri chig stong /
NK129(to)001:447: gti mug gi gnyen por mngon pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK129(to)001:448: dug gsum cha mnyam pa'i gnyen por gsang sngags nyi khri chig stong ste /
NK129(to)001:449: lar chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong dug gsum gyi gnyen por gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:450: dbye ba'i don la dgongs te 'bring du bka' stsal ba ni /
NK129(to)001:451: bstan pa mtha' dag gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis su phye ste /
NK129(to)001:459: chos rmad du byung ba'i sde /
NK129(to)001:461: de lta bu byung ba'i sde /
NK129(to)001:463: gtan la phab pa'i sde dang bcu gnyis so //
NK129(to)001:464: bsdus pa'i don la dgongs nas bsdus te bka' stsal ba ni /
NK129(to)001:465: sangs rgyas kyi bka' thams cad sde snod /
NK129(to)001:466: rin chen gsum du bsdus pa'am /
NK129(to)001:467: theg pa che chung gnyis su bsdus pa'am /
NK129(to)001:468: yang na sngags mtshan nyid gnyis su bsdus pa'o //
NK129(to)001:469: gang zag gis bsam pa la dgongs nas theg pa rim par bka' stsal ba ni /
NK129(to)001:470: yang dag pa'i don la theg pa du ma med kyang /
NK129(to)001:471: dbang po'i rim pas theg pa du mar phye ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:476: dang po theg pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK129(to)001:478: yang na shes rab dang snying rje'o //
NK129(to)001:480: lang kar gshegs pa las theg pa'i rang bzhin shes rab snying rje ste /
NK129(to)001:483: 'degs par byed pas na theg pa ste /
NK129(to)001:487: de yang 'dis 'degs pas na theg pa ste chos so //
NK129(to)001:488: 'di 'degs pas na gang zag go /'dir 'degs pa ni 'bras bu'o //
NK129(to)001:489: dbye ba theg pa gcig tu yang bshad de /
NK129(to)001:491: gsang nyid snying por nges pa na //
NK129(to)001:492: theg pa'i sgo yang gcig las med //
NK129(to)001:495: rtog pa med cing 'khrugs pa med /
NK129(to)001:496: yid 'ong rdo rje'i tshig gcig tu //
NK129(to)001:497: gdul bya'i bsam pa'i dbang gis ni //
NK129(to)001:498: bye brag mang po byung ba yin //
NK129(to)001:502: che chung rim pa'i blo yod phyir //
NK129(to)001:503: theg pa'i rim pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK129(to)001:504: bsdus pas che chung gnyis kyis so //
NK129(to)001:508: theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung la /
NK129(to)001:511: rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK129(to)001:512: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung las //
NK129(to)001:513: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK129(to)001:515: theg pa lngar yang bshad de /
NK129(to)001:518: 'du ba'i dbang gi lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK129(to)001:519: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK129(to)001:520: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang /
NK129(to)001:521: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK129(to)001:522: bla na med pa'i theg pa'o //
NK129(to)001:524: theg pa dgur yang bshad de /
NK129(to)001:526: theg pa dgu dang 'khor ba'i chos rnams kun /
NK129(to)001:528: bsam gyis mi khyab par yang bshad de /
NK129(to)001:530: ji srid 'du shes yod kyi bar /
NK129(to)001:531: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med /
NK129(to)001:533: 'o na gsang sngags theg pa gang du bsdu snyam na /
NK129(to)001:535: mdo sde 'di nyid nyan byed na /
NK129(to)001:541: sngags 'di nang gi mngon pa yin zer ro /
NK129(to)001:543: gsang sngags ni rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod ces la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:544: spyir bgrangs pa'i bzhi pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:545: spyi don bzhi pa lha dang mi'i yul du ji ltar grags pa'i tshul gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:547: mtshan nyid kyi bka' rnams bsdus nas bgo bsha' bya long med par /
NK129(to)001:548: mi dang mi ma yin rnams hab thob shor nas khyer ro //
NK129(to)001:549: mi'i gnas na bzhugs pa rnams kyang rim gyis dar ro //
NK129(to)001:550: mi ma yin gyi gnas na bzhugs pa rnams kyang
NK129(to)001:551: grub thob rnams kyis spyan drangs nas rim gyis dar
NK129(to)001:552: ro / gsang sngags la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:553: rnying ma la grags tshod dang /
NK129(to)001:554: gsar ma la grags tshod do //
NK129(to)001:555: gsang sngags rnying 'gyur ba'i grags tshod ni /
NK129(to)001:556: lha gnas gsum dang 'og min du gsungs pa rnams gsang ba'i bdag pos tshigs su bsdus te /
NK129(to)001:558: bee dar+ya'i zhun mas bris te /
NK129(to)001:559: rtsa ba rang gnas byas nas /
NK129(to)001:560: dgongs pa'i rtsa ba mdun gyi nam mkha' la sbas pa la /
NK129(to)001:561: za hor gyi rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la /
NK129(to)001:562: rmi ltas bdun la brten nas bsgrub pa byas pas /
NK129(to)001:563: glegs bam rnams mi yul du babs te byon no /
NK129(to)001:565: kri ya rnams w+aa ra n+aa sir babs te /
NK129(to)001:567: ba dmar po'i 'o ma yod pas so //
NK129(to)001:568: yo ga rnams ri me ri 'bar ba las babs te /
NK129(to)001:569: ri de lhun zhing brjid che bas /
NK129(to)001:570: yo ga'i lha dang mthun pa'o //
NK129(to)001:571: ma h+aa yo ga ba rnams rgyal po dza'i khang steng du babs te /
NK129(to)001:572: de na longs spyod che bas ma h+aa yo ga'i tshogs bsgrub dang mthun no //
NK129(to)001:573: a nu yo ga rnams ri ma la ya gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse la babs te /
NK129(to)001:574: de na drag po'i rdzas gnam lcags yod pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:575: a ti yo ga rnams o rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i gling du babs te /
NK129(to)001:576: gling de khod snyoms pas rdzogs pa chen po'i chos
NK129(to)001:577: thams cad mnyam pa nyid du ston pa dang mthun
NK129(to)001:578: no / de rnams la rgyud ste gzhan rnams ni dngos su po ti babs pa yin la /
NK129(to)001:579: a ti yo ga ni po ti babs pa ma yin te /
NK129(to)001:580: rdo rje sems dpa'i slob ma /
NK129(to)001:581: lha'i bu kun dga' snying po bya ba /
NK129(to)001:582: mi yul du slob dpon chen po dga' rab rdo rjer sku skye ba bzhes nas /
NK129(to)001:583: rdo rje sems dpas dngos su gser gyi rdo rje
NK129(to)001:584: rtse lnga pa dbu thog tu bzhag nas dbang bskur
NK129(to)001:585: bas / rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud kha sa ma
NK129(to)001:586: t+aa nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud bya ba thugs
NK129(to)001:587: bas / las phyung ste / rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK129(to)001:588: rgyud sde mtha' dag de nas khol du phyung ba
NK129(to)001:589: bas / las phyung ste / yin no / mi yul du gsungs pa rnams kyang /
NK129(to)001:590: sdud pa pos yi ge la gtab nas /
NK129(to)001:591: dpal o rgyan gyi yul du mkha' 'gro ma la gtad /
NK129(to)001:592: lha'i gnas nas byon pa shas gcig kyang mkha' 'gro
NK129(to)001:593: mas bdag byas nas yod pa la grub thob rnams
NK129(to)001:594: kyis bag re blangs te dar bar byas so //
NK129(to)001:595: gnod sbyin gyi gnas na bzhugs pa rnams ni /
NK129(to)001:596: gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje spyan drangs nas /
NK129(to)001:597: sras thu bo r+aa dza has ti la bshad do //
NK129(to)001:598: gshin rje gnas na bzhugs pa rnams ni /
NK129(to)001:599: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis spyan drangs so //
NK129(to)001:600: srin po'i gnas na bzhugs pa rnams ni /
NK129(to)001:601: slob dpon pad+ma rgyal pos spyan drangs so //
NK129(to)001:602: de nas rim par brgyud cing dar ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:603: rgyud sde 'ga' zhig sdud pa po rnams kyis bsdu
NK129(to)001:604: bar ma nus te sgra rang yal la song ngo
NK129(to)001:605: // da 'o na gsungs pa la don med dam snyam na don yod de /
NK129(to)001:606: mngon byung gi 'khor rtogs pa chen po la gnas pa rnams kyi sgro 'dogs bcad pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:607: 'ga' zhig shin tu dar zhing rgyas par 'gyur 'ga' zhig 'gro don bag re byas nas nub /
NK129(to)001:608: 'ga' zhig da rung mkha' 'gro'i phyag nas ma lon te /
NK129(to)001:611: yang dag pa'i tshig dang gtam yin no //
NK129(to)001:612: 'ga' zhig de lta bu'i tshig dang gtam la yid ches pa med do //
NK129(to)001:614: shin tu rmongs pa yin pas /
NK129(to)001:615: lo ts+aa ba gzu dga' rdor gyis dpal sh+r+ai na
NK129(to)001:616: len+da'i gtsug lag khang du po ti'i char babs pa'i
NK129(to)001:617: lo rgyus lha khang la ri mo bris pa mthong
NK129(to)001:618: ba / sngon byung du bstan pa rin po che
NK129(to)001:619: 'di gra ma nyams te dar ba'i dus su sa
NK129(to)001:620: la gnas pa'i pan+di ta dang /
NK129(to)001:621: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba dang /
NK129(to)001:622: byang chub sems dpa'i yon bdag rnams bzhugs pa'i dus
NK129(to)001:623: su gtan la phab pa'i lo rgyus yin pas shin
NK129(to)001:624: tu yid ches pa'i gnas kho na yin no //
NK129(to)001:625: yang gsang sngags gsar 'gyur las grags pa'i dbang du byas nas /
NK129(to)001:628: bcom ldan 'das grong khyer gnyan yod na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)001:629: de nas dpag tshad sum brgya na o rgyan gyi yul yod de /
NK129(to)001:630: de nas rgyal po in dra bo d+hi zhes bya
NK129(to)001:631: ba yod pa la de'i snga 'gro'i dus gcig gi
NK129(to)001:632: tshe / dge slong gi gzugs nam mkha' la 'gro ba mthong ngo /
NK129(to)001:633: des de dag ci yin dris pas /
NK129(to)001:634: 'di ni dpag tshad sum brgya na mnyan yod ces bya ba'i grong khyer na /
NK129(to)001:635: rgyal po zas gtsang ma'i sras sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub
NK129(to)001:636: pa zhes bya ba bzhugs pa'i slob ma yin no
NK129(to)001:637: zer / de skad thos pas rgyal po rab tu dad pas dga' ste /
NK129(to)001:639: thal mo sbyar bas gnyan yod na bcom ldan 'das 'khor dang bcas pa bzhugs par mthong ngo /
NK129(to)001:640: de la dad pa skyes nas bcom ldan 'das rnam
NK129(to)001:641: pa thams cad mkhyen pa thugs rje dang rdzu 'phrul
NK129(to)001:643: sang bdag ni gan du gdugs tshod la gshegs par zhu'o //
NK129(to)001:645: sang gdugs tshod la bcom ldan 'das 'khor dang bcas
NK129(to)001:646: pa byon pa de la bsnyen bkur byas nas gsol
NK129(to)001:647: ba / bdag cag rnams srid pa'i sdug bsngal las thar bar mdzad du gsol zhes zhus pas /
NK129(to)001:649: khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung na thabs yod do //
NK129(to)001:652: bdag ni 'dod yon gyis gdung ba che bas /
NK129(to)001:653: 'di ma spangs par 'khor ba las grol ba'i thabs zhu'o zhes zhus pas /
NK129(to)001:654: gsang sngags kyi snod du gzigs nas /
NK129(to)001:655: de nyid kyi tshe skyes bu chags pa can rjes su bzung ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:656: rdo rje 'chang gi cha lugs su bzhengs nas /
NK129(to)001:657: rdo rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga la bzhugs nas /
NK129(to)001:658: btsun mo'idabusa su rgyal po dbang bskur te grol bar mdzad nas /
NK129(to)001:659: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams gsungs /
NK129(to)001:660: de phyag rdor gyis bsdus nas mkha' 'gro ma la gtad /
NK129(to)001:661: gan+d+ho la'i gtsug lag khang du sbas te /
NK129(to)001:662: grub thob rnams kyis bag re blangs nas dar bar byas pa yin zer ro /
NK129(to)001:664: phyag rdor gyis bsdus pa'i rgyud rnams mkha' 'gro ma la gtad pa yin /
NK129(to)001:665: rgyal po in+d+ra bo d+hi la rgyud sde mtha' dag gsungs pa med de /
NK129(to)001:666: kho rang la dbang bskur nas grol bar byas pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:669: phyag rdor gyi rgyud bsdus pa rnams rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa la gtad /
NK129(to)001:670: de dag gis bsgrubs pas dngos grub rim par thob par gyur /
NK129(to)001:671: de nas o rgyan gyi yul stongs te /
NK129(to)001:672: mtsho chen po gcig tu gyur /
NK129(to)001:674: de nas phyag rdor gyis rgyud rnams klu la gnang
NK129(to)001:675: bas klu rnams kyang rim gyis mi'i gzugs su gyur
NK129(to)001:676: nas / mtsho 'gram du grong bcas te /
NK129(to)001:677: gsang sngags rnams nyams su blangs pas /
NK129(to)001:678: phal cher gyis grub pa thob ste /
NK129(to)001:679: ma thob pa rnams kyang mir gyur /
NK129(to)001:680: bud med rnams kyang mkha' 'gro mar gyur nas /
NK129(to)001:681: o rgyan mkha' 'gro'i gling zhes grags so //
NK129(to)001:682: zhes zer ba yang yod do //
NK129(to)001:683: mdor na rgyud rnams o rgyan nas spyan drangs par 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:684: rgyal po ba su ka la bas gsang ba 'dus pa dang /
NK129(to)001:686: klu sgrub kyis glen par bardzusa nas dgyes rdor spyan drangs /
NK129(to)001:687: ku ku ri pas ma h+aa m+aa y+aa /
NK129(to)001:688: la li ta badz+rasa rdo rje 'jigs byed la sogs pa mang du spyan drangs par 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:689: de ltar lo rgyus mi mthun pa ji ltar yin snyam na /
NK129(to)001:690: dus phyis rgya gar yul na bstan pa gra nyams shing /
NK129(to)001:691: rgyud sde chen po rnams rim gyis nub cing dpe rul bas /
NK129(to)001:692: grub thob kha yar gyis mkha' 'gro ma'i phyag nas dpe gsar du blangs pa rnams la spyod pas /
NK129(to)001:693: rgyud sde rnams kyi byung tshul ji ltar ba bzhin du khong du ma chud pa yin /
NK129(to)001:694: da lta'i pan+di ta gser 'dod kyis bod na chos
NK129(to)001:695: gang la gtsigs che dris nas bcos ma mang po
NK129(to)001:696: byed / lo ts+aa ba mkhas 'dod kyis dbyar mang yul du don byas /
NK129(to)001:698: sngon gyi lo pan byang chub sems dpas bsgyur ba'i chos la /
NK129(to)001:700: rtsa rlung thig le la sogs pa phyi rol pa
NK129(to)001:701: dang thun mong gi chos la ngo mtshar gyis gnas
NK129(to)001:702: su mthong nas gser chos byas pas bstan pa nyams
NK129(to)001:704: 'o na gsang sngags rnying mi'i dpe tsam rgya gar na mi bzhugs sam snyam na /
NK129(to)001:705: spyir sngon gyi dus su rgya gar na bzhugs pa'i chos ma lus pa bsgyur ba yin skad /
NK129(to)001:706: de la dus phyis bskyar nas bsgyur ba rnams la gsar mar grags /
NK129(to)001:707: ma 'gyur ba rnams la rnying mar grags pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:708: gsang sngags ma rgyud 'ga' zhig sngon ma 'gyur te /
NK129(to)001:709: dus phyis mkha' 'gro ma'i phyag nas blangs nas bsgyur ba'ang yod do //
NK129(to)001:710: rnying ma rnams dus phyis mi 'gyur ba ji ltar yin snyam na /
NK129(to)001:711: sngon gyi rgyud sde rnams kyi babs sa rdo rje
NK129(to)001:712: gdan gyi shar lho'i mtshams za hor gyi yul yin
NK129(to)001:713: pas / yul de na gsang sngags dar ro /
NK129(to)001:714: de'i dus su pan+di ta rnams kyang za hor du rig pa sbyong bas /
NK129(to)001:715: de'i dus su bod du spyan drangs pa'i pan+di ta za hor ba dang /
NK129(to)001:716: rgya gar shar phyogs d+ha na da la ba dang /
NK129(to)001:717: gzhan gyis kyang za hor du bslabs pa phal che
NK129(to)001:718: bas yi ge rnams kyang za hor gyi yi ge
NK129(to)001:719: yod pas dus phyis rgya gar dbus kyi pan+di tas
NK129(to)001:721: za hor gyi yul du matha'i rgyal pos dmag drangs nas chos snubs pas /
NK129(to)001:722: dus phyis spyan ma drongs pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:723: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po ni /
NK129(to)001:724: shin tu zab ches pas kun gyi blor ma gshong ste /
NK129(to)001:725: rdo rje gdan gyi 'og tu sbas pa la /
NK129(to)001:726: sh+r+ai sing has bag tsam gcig bton nas bee ro tsa na la bshad /
NK129(to)001:727: lhag ma sbras nas yod pa la /
NK129(to)001:728: phyis lo tsa ba mi gsum gyis slob dpon bi ma la spyan drangs ba'i tshe /
NK129(to)001:729: rgya gar gyi man+di tas phrag dog byas nas /
NK129(to)001:730: bee ro tsa na rgyal mo tsha ba'i rong du spyugs pa'i snying nad dang /
NK129(to)001:731: bi ma la mkhas drag pas rgyal po la lcugs spyugs te /
NK129(to)001:732: pan+di ta lnga brgyas bod du mi 'gro ba'i dbang med pa spyugs pa'i snying nad kyis /
NK129(to)001:733: bi ma la mi tra dpon g.yog gis /
NK129(to)001:734: rgyal po dang pan+di ta rnams la zhu ba phul te /
NK129(to)001:735: bdag bod du mchis phan chad /
NK129(to)001:736: bod du sngon chad yongs su ma grags pa'i chos gcig bsgyur dgos byas pas /
NK129(to)001:738: rdo rje gdan gyi 'og na man ngag gi chos
NK129(to)001:739: sbas nas yod pa de 'o skol rgya gar na
NK129(to)001:741: khyod bod du 'gro ba shin tu yus che ba yin pas /
NK129(to)001:742: ji ltar rigs par thon la khyer zer bas /
NK129(to)001:743: bi ma la dpon g.yog gis man ngag gi chos ma lus par spyan drangs nas /
NK129(to)001:744: rgya'i dpe rtsa bas bcad pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:745: de rnams ni lha dang mi yul du ji ltar grags pa'i tshu la lo //
NK129(to)001:748: mdo khams smad kyi chos 'byung dang /
NK129(to)001:749: smri ti dz+ny+aa na k+ai ra ti la dri ba'i
NK129(to)001:750: the tshom bcad pa'i lo rgyus chen mo dag las
NK129(to)001:751: ji ltar 'byung ba'i tshul brjod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:752: lnga pa chos de rnams kyi rnam par bzhag pa la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:753: rgyu mtshan nyiid kyi theg pa'i dbang du byas nas bka'i rnam par bzhag pa dang /
NK129(to)001:754: bstan bcos kyi rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK129(to)001:755: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi dbang du byas nas /
NK129(to)001:756: rgyud kyi rnam par bzhag pa dang /
NK129(to)001:758: bsgrub thabs kyi rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK129(to)001:759: dang po bka'i rnam par bzhag pa la drug ste /
NK129(to)001:766: dang po bka'i ngo bo ni mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK129(to)001:768: nyi ma dang zla ba 'di yang sa la lhung yang srid /
NK129(to)001:769: rlung zhags pas zin kyang srid kyis /
NK129(to)001:770: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' ni /
NK129(to)001:774: srid pa 'dre ldog kyang bka' 'dre mi ldog go /
NK129(to)001:777: 'da' bardaka'a bas na bka' zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)001:779: rgyal ba'i bka' gsang ji lta bar //
NK129(to)001:780: 'da' bar dka' bas bka' zhes bya //
NK129(to)001:786: zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:787: ston pas mdongs gsol du gsungs pa dang /
NK129(to)001:788: 'khor gyis nus pas zhus te gsungs pa dang /
NK129(to)001:789: skabs las gleng bslangs du gsungs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:790: ston pas mdongs gsol du gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:792: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor bzhi po de
NK129(to)001:793: dag rab tu dga' bar mdzad pa'i phyir yang shes
NK129(to)001:794: rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa 'di ston cing
NK129(to)001:795: / de'i tshe tshigs su bcad pa 'di dag bka' stsal to //
NK129(to)001:797: 'khor gyis zhus te gsungs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:799: glur blangs gar blangs bshad du gsol /
NK129(to)001:801: skabs las gleng du bslangs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:802: dus skabs kyi dgongs 'brel gang yang rung ba la brten nas gsungs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:803: byin gyi rlabs pa'i bka' la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:804: skus byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:805: bcom ldan 'das kyis sems dpa' rdo rje snying po'i
NK129(to)001:806: spyi bor phyag glang po'i sna lta bu bzhag nas
NK129(to)001:808: chos mdo sde sa bcu pa gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:809: gsung gis byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:811: rab 'byor ci nas kyang ci nas kyang shes rab
NK129(to)001:812: kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la spobs par gyis
NK129(to)001:813: shig / ces bsgo bas spobs pa skyes nas pha
NK129(to)001:814: rol du phyin pa bshad ces gsungs pa lta bu'o
NK129(to)001:815: shig / // thugs kyis byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:816: bcom ldan 'das zab mo'i snang ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs nas /
NK129(to)001:817: spyan ras gzigs kyis chos gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:818: gang byin gyis brlabs na gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:819: sems kyi rgyud dang mi 'brel bar byin gyis rlabs pa dang /
NK129(to)001:820: sems kyi rgyud dang 'brel bar byin gyis rlabs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:821: dang po ni thub pa bzhugs pa'i dus su bem po las kyang chos kyi sgra 'byung ste /
NK129(to)001:822: mkha' dang gzugs ni dad pa dang //
NK129(to)001:823: nam mkha' las kyang chos kyi sgra //
NK129(to)001:826: ston pas dga' ldan gnas su ni //
NK129(to)001:827: ri dang shing bu rde'u dang /
NK129(to)001:828: rnga bo che dang pad+ma las /
NK129(to)001:829: sgra byung bas ni bka' zhes brjod //
NK129(to)001:831: sems kyi rgyud dang 'brel bar byin gyis rlabs pa gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:832: sems can gyi sems dang 'brel bar byin gyis rlabs pa dang /
NK129(to)001:833: 'phags pa'i thugs dang 'brel bar byin gyis rlabs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:835: thub pa zhal bzhugs pa'i dus na /
NK129(to)001:836: sems can phal pas kyang chos 'chad par nus te /
NK129(to)001:837: thub dbang khyod kyi byin rlabs las //
NK129(to)001:838: sems can kun gyis chos rab sgrogs /
NK129(to)001:840: 'phags pa'i thugs dang 'brel bar byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:841: rgyal ba'i nyan thos pa dag ji snyed chos ston dang /
NK129(to)001:843: rigs pa dag dang ldan par brjod pa dang //
NK129(to)001:844: mchog 'phags bde ba byed dang de'i 'bras thob pa /
NK129(to)001:845: de dag kun kyang de bzhin gshegs pa'i skyes bu'i mthu //
NK129(to)001:847: rjes su gnang ba'i bka' la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:848: gsung zhig par rjes su gnang ba dang /
NK129(to)001:849: bsdus shig par rjes su gnang ba'o /
NK129(to)001:850: dang po thub pas 'khor rnams shod cig ces gsungs pa'am /
NK129(to)001:851: ji ltar khyod kyis bstan pa bzhin du shes rab
NK129(to)001:852: kyi pha rol du phyin pa zab mo la bslab
NK129(to)001:853: par bya'o // zhes pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:854: bsdus shig par rjes su gnang ba ni /
NK129(to)001:855: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i zhes pa chos rnams kun gyi dbu ru chug cig /
NK129(to)001:856: gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
NK129(to)001:857: zhes pa chos rnams kun gyi zhabs la chug cig ces pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:859: bka' thams cad theg pa che chung gnyis su 'dus pa'am /
NK129(to)001:863: bka' la gang snga ba ni /
NK129(to)001:864: 'ga' zhig na re mdo sde shis par brjod pa snga ste /
NK129(to)001:865: thub pa sangs rgyas te zhag bdun phrag bdun du chos ma gsungs pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)001:866: bdun phrag tha ma la byang chub kyi shing sgrol rgyu'i rtsa na bzhugs pa la /
NK129(to)001:867: tshong dpon mgon bzang skyon dang 'phrad pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)001:868: mdo sde shes pa brjod pa gsungs pas de snga ma yin zhes zer ro //
NK129(to)001:870: de tsa na sangs rgyas ma zin te /
NK129(to)001:871: rdo rje gdan du bzhud pa'i lam ga yin pas de dag ni bkar mi 'gro la /
NK129(to)001:872: sangs rgyas nas brgya byin gyis zhus pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)001:873: zab bzhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas /
NK129(to)001:874: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig bdag gis rnyed /
NK129(to)001:875: su la bstan kyang go bar mi 'gyur bas //
NK129(to)001:876: mi smra nags su gcig pur bsgom par bya /
NK129(to)001:877: zhes gsungs pa de snga ste /
NK129(to)001:878: dbang po rab la yang dag pa'i don ngo sprod pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:880: bka'i chos sde ngos bzung ba ni /
NK129(to)001:881: theg pa chung ngu la nyan thos dang /
NK129(to)001:884: 'dul lung sde bzhi mdo sde las /
NK129(to)001:885: legs nyes ston pa las brgya pa /
NK129(to)001:886: gad mo la sogs pa'i rtogs brjod /
NK129(to)001:889: mngon pa sde bdun la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:890: rang rgyal la bka' la sogs pa'i gzhung mi gzhung de zhar byung yin no //
NK129(to)001:895: sangs rgyas phal po che dang /
NK129(to)001:896: mdo sde lang kar gshegs pa /
NK129(to)001:897: dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa la sogs pa /
NK129(to)001:898: mdo sde phal cher yin no //
NK129(to)001:900: mdo pha rol du phyin pa rgyas 'bring rnam gsum //
NK129(to)001:902: gzhan yang mdo sde ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyal po la sogs pa mang du bzhugs so //
NK129(to)001:911: sems can nyon mong spong zhing /
NK129(to)001:914: slob dpon dbyig gnyen gyi zhal nas /
NK129(to)001:915: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK129(to)001:916: ngan 'gro'i srid las skyabs pa gang yin pa //
NK129(to)001:917: 'chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te /
NK129(to)001:918: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK129(to)001:921: bka'i don dam sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa mi gsal ba rnams gsal bar bcos pa'o //
NK129(to)001:927: bya rog so brtag gi bstan bcos la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:928: don log pa ni mu stegs kyi bstan bcos so //
NK129(to)001:935: brjod bya ngag gi 'grel pa sgra'i bstan bcos dang /
NK129(to)001:936: rjod byed tshig gi 'grel pa tshad ma'i bstan bcos so /
NK129(to)001:937: sgrub pa lhur len pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:938: lung bsdu ba'i bstan bcos dang /
NK129(to)001:939: lung dgrol ba'i bstan bcos so //
NK129(to)001:941: sangs rgyas kyi bka' rgya che /
NK129(to)001:943: de rnams sems can gyis blos bsdur 'dus pas /
NK129(to)001:944: de'i don du 'phags pas bstan bcos mang du mdzad de /
NK129(to)001:945: mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyan lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:946: lung dgrol ba'i bstan bcos ni /
NK129(to)001:947: sangs rgyas kyi bka' rdo rje'i tshig tu gnas pas /
NK129(to)001:948: sems can gyi blos dpag par dka' zhing mi rtogs pas /
NK129(to)001:949: 'phags pa dang gang zag mkhas pa rnams kyis /
NK129(to)001:950: de'i don gsal bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:951: bka'i bshad 'grel chen po rnams mdzad pa yin /
NK129(to)001:952: bstan bcos kyi bsdu ba ni /
NK129(to)001:953: bka' thams cad theg pa che chung gnyis su 'dus pas /
NK129(to)001:954: bstan bcos kyang gnyis su 'dus pa'am /
NK129(to)001:955: bka' thams cad sde snod gsum du 'dus pas /
NK129(to)001:956: bstan bcos kyang sdeee snod gsum du 'dus pa'o //
NK129(to)001:957: bstan bcos la gang snga ba ni /
NK129(to)001:958: gzhung gcig la bstan bcos mngon pa sde bdun snga ste /
NK129(to)001:959: thub pa ma 'das pa'i gong du brtsams pa yin no zer ro //
NK129(to)001:961: bye brag gi bshad mdzod chen mo snga ste /
NK129(to)001:962: bka' bsdu ba mdzad pa'i rjes thogs la dgra bcom pa lnga brgyas mdzad pa yin zer ro //
NK129(to)001:963: chos sde ngos bzung ba ni /
NK129(to)001:964: bka' 'khor lo dang po'i dgongs pa 'grel pa /
NK129(to)001:965: bye brag gi bshad mdzod chen mo dang /
NK129(to)001:966: pra ka ra n+aa sde brgyad dang /
NK129(to)001:967: 'dul ba mdo rtsa la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:968: bka' 'khor lo bar ba'i dgongs pa 'grel bar byed pa /
NK129(to)001:969: don gyi 'grel pa dbu ma rigs pa'i tshogs drug dang /
NK129(to)001:971: tshig gi 'grel pa dam pa'i chos mngon pa /
NK129(to)001:972: tshig don gnyis ka'i 'grel pa mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyan no //
NK129(to)001:973: bka' 'khor lo tha ma'i dgongs pa 'grel bar byed pa /
NK129(to)001:976: chos dang chos min rnam par 'byed pa dang /
NK129(to)001:978: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i sa sde lnga dang /
NK129(to)001:979: don gsal ba la sogs pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:980: de gnyis ka'i thun mong pa rgyud bla ma la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:981: spyir bka' re re la'ang theg pa che chung gnyis ka tshang ba yod do //
NK129(to)001:982: bstan bcos re re la yang gnyis ka tshang ba yod /
NK129(to)001:983: de re res kyang bka' 'khor lo gsum ka'i don gtan la 'bebs pa yod do //
NK129(to)001:984: gsang sngags spyi sdom rnam par bzhag pa la lnga ste /
NK129(to)001:991: yid skyob pa'ang shes pa skyob par byed pa yin te /
NK129(to)001:992: gsang ba 'dus pa'i phyi ma las /
NK129(to)001:993: ma ni yid ces bya ba de /
NK129(to)001:994: dra ni skyob par byed par bshad /
NK129(to)001:996: 'o na pha rol du phyin pas kyang yid dang shes pa skyob pas /
NK129(to)001:997: sngags dang khyad par ci yod ce na /
NK129(to)001:999: sngags ni bde bar skyob pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1000: myur bar skyob pas khyad par du byas pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1003: dka' thub dka' spyad 'dir mi dgos //
NK129(to)001:1004: khrims dang sdom pa 'dir mi dgos //
NK129(to)001:1007: mtshan nyid theg pa ltar bskal pa grangs med gsum du bsgrod mi dgos par gsungs te /
NK129(to)001:1009: de ni 'di dang phyi ma dang /
NK129(to)001:1010: lan grangs gzhan du rab 'bring gis /
NK129(to)001:1011: thob phyir bskal bar mi 'gyangs te /
NK129(to)001:1014: dbang po rab kyis tshe 'di la 'bras bu thob ste /
NK129(to)001:1016: 'di yis bcom ldan bdag nyid che //
NK129(to)001:1017: sku gsum mi phyed las byung ba //
NK129(to)001:1018: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par brgyan //
NK129(to)001:1023: yang na lus ni spangs ma thag /
NK129(to)001:1024: rtson pa mi ldan pas kyang 'grub /
NK129(to)001:1026: tha mas skye ba bdun na 'grub ste /
NK129(to)001:1028: dbang bskur yang dag sbyin ldan na //
NK129(to)001:1029: skye zhing skye bar dbang bskur 'gyur //
NK129(to)001:1030: de yis skye ba bdun na ni //
NK129(to)001:1031: ma bsgrubs par yang dngos grub thob //
NK129(to)001:1033: tha ma'i tha mas skye ba bcu drug na /
NK129(to)001:1036: gal te ltung ba med gyur na //
NK129(to)001:1037: skye ba bcu drug dag na 'grub //
NK129(to)001:1039: mdor na gsang sngags kyi ngo bo ni /
NK129(to)001:1040: skyes skyob bde myur zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)001:1042: yon tan gyi rim pa la'ang /
NK129(to)001:1043: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo ni /
NK129(to)001:1044: stong pa dang snying rje'i khyad par bshad de /
NK129(to)001:1045: stong pa dang ni snying rje gnyis //
NK129(to)001:1046: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis su //
NK129(to)001:1047: gsang sngags zhes ni de la bshad //
NK129(to)001:1050: snod min la gsang zhing snod ldan la sngags pa na /
NK129(to)001:1053: gsang sngags gsang zhes brjod pa ni //
NK129(to)001:1054: chos la skyon yod ma yin te //
NK129(to)001:1055: snod min sems can blo chung la //
NK129(to)001:1056: thugs rje thabs kyis rab tu gsang //
NK129(to)001:1062: de gsum gyi khyad par kyang /
NK129(to)001:1063: mkha' 'gro ma gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK129(to)001:1064: ma rig rnams las gsang ba'i phyir //
NK129(to)001:1065: gsang sngags zhes su bstan pa yin //
NK129(to)001:1066: de don phyin ci ma log pas //
NK129(to)001:1067: rigs sngags zhes su bstan pa yin //
NK129(to)001:1068: stong pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas //
NK129(to)001:1069: gzungs sngags zhes su bstan pa yin //
NK129(to)001:1072: lha pho mo zung 'brel du ston pa gsang sngags /
NK129(to)001:1073: lha pho shas che ba rigs sngags /
NK129(to)001:1074: lha mo shas che ba gzungs sngags zer ro //
NK129(to)001:1076: gyis sngags kyi mgo drangs pa thams cad gsang sngags /
NK129(to)001:1077: tad+ya th+aas drangs pa rig sngags /
NK129(to)001:1078: na morarna tra y+aa yas drangs pa gzungs sngags zer te /
NK129(to)001:1079: gcig tu nges par bzhag pa med do //
NK129(to)001:1081: sangs rgyas kyi thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes so //
NK129(to)001:1082: de yang rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK129(to)001:1083: sngags rnams kun gyi mtshan nyid ni //
NK129(to)001:1084: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs yin pas //
NK129(to)001:1085: chos kyi snying po sgrub byed cing //
NK129(to)001:1086: chos kyi dbyings dang yang dag ldan //
NK129(to)001:1087: sngags kyi mtshan nyid yin par gsungs //
NK129(to)001:1089: rnam grangs rnam par phye na gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:1091: rgyud la brten pa'i sgrub thabs sam //
NK129(to)001:1100: brjod bya don gyi rgyud kyi ngo bo dang /
NK129(to)001:1101: rjod byed tshig gi rgyud kyi ngo bo'o //
NK129(to)001:1104: brjod bya'i rgyud kyi ngo bo ni /
NK129(to)001:1105: gang las gnyis med kyi ye shes snang bar nus pa yin la /
NK129(to)001:1106: rjod byed tshig gi rgyud kyi ngo bo ni /
NK129(to)001:1107: gang la gnyis med kyi ye shes snang ba'i ngag yin gsungs /
NK129(to)001:1109: gnyis med gnyis su med par ston //
NK129(to)001:1111: kun dga' snying po na re /
NK129(to)001:1112: brjod bya'i rgyud kyi ngo bo ni /
NK129(to)001:1113: ston pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi 'khor lo yin la /
NK129(to)001:1114: rjod byed kyi ngo bo ni /
NK129(to)001:1115: sgra spyi'i rnam pa yi ger snang ba'o zer /
NK129(to)001:1116: de yang de gnyis 'dus pa las /
NK129(to)001:1117: rgyud kyi ngo bo ston pas te //
NK129(to)001:1118: sgra yi bdag nyid rgyud ces bya //
NK129(to)001:1121: rgyud kyi ngo bo thabs shes gnyis su med pa yin te /
NK129(to)001:1123: thabs dang shes rab bdag nyid rgyud //
NK129(to)001:1124: 'di ni bdag gis bshad kyis nyon //
NK129(to)001:1128: nges pa'i tshig ni drug yin te //
NK129(to)001:1129: phun sum tshogs lngas 'chad phyir dang //
NK129(to)001:1130: 'brel dang ma tshang med phyir dang //
NK129(to)001:1131: dkrug pa'i phyir dang rag las phyir //
NK129(to)001:1132: gsang sngags bslab pa ston phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:1135: 'brel dang ma tshang med phyir dang //
NK129(to)001:1136: phun gsum tshogs pas rgyud ces bya //
NK129(to)001:1139: rgyun chags pa'i don gyis na rgyud de chu bo'i rgyun lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:1140: 'brel ba'i don gyis rgyud de sa bon dang myu gu lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:1141: ma tshang pa med pa'i don gyis rgyud de /
NK129(to)001:1142: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal srid lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:1143: rgyas pa'i don gyis na rgyud de /
NK129(to)001:1144: dpag bsam gyi shing lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:1145: rang gis rang thums pa'i don gyis na rgyud de /
NK129(to)001:1146: dar gyi srin bu lta bu 'o //
NK129(to)001:1147: dkrugs pa'i do na gyis na rgyud de /
NK129(to)001:1149: rgyud la dbye na gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:1150: brjod bya don gyi rgyud brjod byed tshig gi rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1151: don gyi rgyud la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:1156: bsgrub bya rgyud dang bya ba shes //
NK129(to)001:1157: gzhi de rang bzhin rgyun yin te //
NK129(to)001:1158: bsgrub pa'i rdo rje bdag ces so //
NK129(to)001:1160: rgyud ni rnam pa gsum 'gyur te //
NK129(to)001:1161: gzhi dang de yi rang bzhin dang //
NK129(to)001:1162: mi phrog pa yi rab phye ba //
NK129(to)001:1163: gzhi de rang bzhin rgyu yin te //
NK129(to)001:1171: de la rgyu'i rgyud bya ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1172: sems can rnams kyi sems nyid ye nas bde bar
NK129(to)001:1173: gshegs pa'i snying po can du ye nas gnas pa
NK129(to)001:1174: ste / rkyen lam nyams su blangs na /
NK129(to)001:1175: 'bras bu thob nges pa la bya'o //
NK129(to)001:1177: rgyud ni rgyun chags zhes bya ste //
NK129(to)001:1181: rgyud de 'bras bur byed pa'i thabs lam yin te /
NK129(to)001:1183: sems can ye shes skyes ba'i phyir //
NK129(to)001:1184: thabs ni sangs rgyas nyid kyis bstan //
NK129(to)001:1186: rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK129(to)001:1187: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK129(to)001:1188: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK129(to)001:1189: rang byung sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK129(to)001:1192: sems nyid sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor ye nas rgyun ma chad par gnas kyang /
NK129(to)001:1193: glo bur gyi dri mas bsgribs pa la /
NK129(to)001:1194: dri ma de bsal nas gzhi ji lta ba bzhin du mngon du byas pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1196: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK129(to)001:1197: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK129(to)001:1198: de nyid bsal na sangs rgyas yin //
NK129(to)001:1200: brjod byed tshig gi rgyud ni /
NK129(to)001:1201: brjod bya'i don gtan la 'beb par byed pa'i man
NK129(to)001:1202: ngag bka' gsang sngags su byung ba zhig la bya'o
NK129(to)001:1203: // rgyud kyi rnam grangs rnam par dbye na gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:1204: bka' rnying 'gyur las grags pa dang //
NK129(to)001:1206: bka' rnying 'gyur las grags pa'i dbang du byas na gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:1207: phyi pa thabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK129(to)001:1208: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1209: phyi pa thabs kyi rgyud la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:1210: bya ba'i rgyud kri ya dang /
NK129(to)001:1211: spyod pa'i rgyud u pa ya dang /
NK129(to)001:1213: kri ya la bya ba'i rgyud zer ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1215: khrus dang gtsang sbra gtso bor ston pas bya ba'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1216: de yang bsam gtan phyi ma las /
NK129(to)001:1217: rgyud 'di ni lus ngag gi bya ba gtso bor ston pas na bya ba'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1219: de'i chos sde ngos bzung na kri ya spyi'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)001:1225: gsang ba spyi rgyud la sogs so //
NK129(to)001:1227: rigs gsum gyi rgyud du ma dang /
NK129(to)001:1228: gzungs kyi rigs mang du bzhugs so //
NK129(to)001:1230: u p+aa ya zhes ci'i phyir bya na /
NK129(to)001:1231: spyod pa kri ya ltar spyod cing lta ba yo ga ltar lta bas gnyis ka'i rgyud yin no //
NK129(to)001:1233: rnam snang mngon par byang chub pa'i don bsdus pa las /
NK129(to)001:1234: rgyud 'di ni gtsang sbra la sogs pas sman la
NK129(to)001:1235: ting nge 'dzin gyi 'phags par spyod pas na gnyis
NK129(to)001:1237: de'i chos sde ngos bzung ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1238: rnam pa snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)001:1240: rdo rje sa 'og dang 'byung po 'dul byed kyi rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1241: yo ga la ci'i phyir rnal 'byor gyi rgyud ces bya na /
NK129(to)001:1242: de kho na nyid rnam par 'byed pa'i don bsdus pa las /
NK129(to)001:1243: rgyud 'di ni ting nge 'dzin gtso bor spyod pas na rnal 'byor gyi rgyud de zhes so //
NK129(to)001:1244: de'i chos sde ngos bzung ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1245: rtsa ba'i rgyud de kho na nyid 'dus pa /
NK129(to)001:1246: de dang nye ba'i rgyud ngan song sbyong ba'o //
NK129(to)001:1247: bshad pa'i rgyud la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:1248: sku mdog phyag mtshan 'chad pa dpal mchog dang po //
NK129(to)001:1249: ting nge 'dzin dang mchod pa 'chad pa rdo rje rtse mo /
NK129(to)001:1250: de kho na nyid dang mngon par byang chub pa 'chad pa thabs gsal ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)001:1251: bsgom pa dang bzlas pa 'chad par byed pa dam tshig gi mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1252: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:1253: theg pa spyir dbye ba dang /
NK129(to)001:1254: chos sde bye brag tu dbye ba'o //
NK129(to)001:1255: dang po theg pa spyir dbye na gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:1256: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK129(to)001:1257: lung a nu yo ga dang /
NK129(to)001:1258: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'o //
NK129(to)001:1259: de rnams kyang gtso che ba'i ming 'dogs yin la /
NK129(to)001:1260: bye brag tu re re la yang rgyud lung man ngag gsum ga tshang bar gnas de /
NK129(to)001:1262: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag kyang //
NK129(to)001:1263: dmangs dang rje dang rgyal po'i tshul //
NK129(to)001:1264: gcig la gcig rten gcig gi ngang //
NK129(to)001:1266: chos sde bye brag phye na gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:1272: de yang theg pa dang sbyar na /
NK129(to)001:1273: sgyu 'phrul ni ma h+aa yo ga mdo ni a
NK129(to)001:1274: nu yo ga sems phyogs ni a ti yo ga'o
NK129(to)001:1275: // de rnams ston pa'i chos sde ni /
NK129(to)001:1276: spyi rgyud ma h+aa yo ga la /
NK129(to)001:1277: tan tra sde bco brgyad bzhugs la khyad par du gsang ba sgyu 'phrul la /
NK129(to)001:1278: rgyud sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad du grags so //
NK129(to)001:1279: lung a nu yo ga la /
NK129(to)001:1280: lung gis rgyu sde nyer gcig tu yang grags so //
NK129(to)001:1281: sems phyogs la kun byed rgyal po //
NK129(to)001:1287: bye brag tu rgyud phran bsam gyis mi khyab pa bzhugs so //
NK129(to)001:1288: rgyud kyi rgyal po drug ni /
NK129(to)001:1289: bskyed rdzogs gsum ga'i thun mong gi rgyud yin no yang zer /
NK129(to)001:1290: lung a nu yo ga'i rgyud yin no yang zer ro //
NK129(to)001:1291: sgrub sde ni spyir de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK129(to)001:1292: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lnga'i bdag nyid
NK129(to)001:1293: du gnas pas de sgrub pa'i thabs la yang lnga
NK129(to)001:1296: yang dag thugs kyi sgrub pa /
NK129(to)001:1297: bdud rtsi yon tan gyi sgrub pa /
NK129(to)001:1298: phur pa 'phrin las kyi bsgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1299: dang po 'jam dpal la sku'i sgrub pa zer ba de /
NK129(to)001:1300: dpal ya man+ta ka'i sku la 'khor lo bzhi dang ldan par sgrub pas na'o //
NK129(to)001:1302: gshin rje'i rna rgyud ya ma r+aa dza sku khros pa /
NK129(to)001:1304: thugs khros pa gsang rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1305: pad+ma la gsung gi sgrub pa zer ba de /
NK129(to)001:1306: rta skad thengs gsum la brten nas sgrub pas so //
NK129(to)001:1308: rta mchog rol pa dbang chen 'dus pa /
NK129(to)001:1310: drag po tshar gcod la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1311: yang dag la thugs kyi sgrub pa zer ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1312: dpal chen po'i mkhyen pa'i ye shes chen po dgu mar me dgu la brten nas sgrub pas so //
NK129(to)001:1317: he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)001:1318: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor la sogs pa'o /
NK129(to)001:1319: bdud rtsi la yon tan gyi sgrub pa zer ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1320: dpal che mchog he ru ka'i zhabs kyi gdan khri nas /
NK129(to)001:1321: dbu'i gtsug tor man chad nas /
NK129(to)001:1322: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad yon tan gyi tshul du rdzogs par sgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1324: rgyud bzhi lung dang lnga ste /
NK129(to)001:1327: dngos grub nye ba'i snying po /
NK129(to)001:1330: phur ba phrin las kyi sgrub pa zer ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1331: las kyi gdab ka 'ba' zhig ston pas so //
NK129(to)001:1333: phur bu la rgyud sde sum cu so gcig go /
NK129(to)001:1334: de rnams ni ye shes lha'i sgrub sde'o //
NK129(to)001:1335: bsgrub pa bka' brgyad du byas na /
NK129(to)001:1338: 'das pa'i sgrub pa sde thun mong la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:1339: ma mo rbod stong gi sgrub pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1340: drag sngags dmod mo'i sgrub pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1341: 'jig rten mchod bstod kyi sgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1342: de dag kyang ye shes lha'i sgrub pa'i bstan pa
NK129(to)001:1343: srung ba dgongs nas las bka' bsam gyis mi khyab
NK129(to)001:1344: pa gcig gsungs pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:1345: bka' gsar 'gyur las grags pa ni /
NK129(to)001:1348: drug la sogs par bshad pa yang yod de /
NK129(to)001:1349: 'dir rgyud sde chen po bzhir sdud pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:1353: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1354: de rnams gtan la dbab pa la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:1359: dang po grangs nges pa la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:1360: dang po dus bzhi la dgongs nas kyang rgyud sde bzhir nges te /
NK129(to)001:1362: gsang sngags byung tshul rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:1363: skal pa rdzogs ldan gsum ldan gnyis //
NK129(to)001:1364: rtsod dus rgyud dang rim bzhin du //
NK129(to)001:1365: gdul bya'i ngos la snang ba yin //
NK129(to)001:1367: gnyis pa skye gnas bzhi la dgongs nas kyang rgyud sde bzhir nges te /
NK129(to)001:1369: sgong skyes mngal nas skyes pa'am /
NK129(to)001:1370: drod gsher las skyes rdzus skyes sam /
NK129(to)001:1371: rgyud ni bzhi ru nges pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1373: gsum pa mi rigs bzhi la dgongs nas kyang bzhir nges te /
NK129(to)001:1375: rgyal rigs rje rigs bram ze dang //
NK129(to)001:1376: dmangs rigs gdol pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK129(to)001:1377: rgyud sde so sor bstan pa yin //
NK129(to)001:1379: bzhi pa 'dod khams kyi lha'i chags pa spyod tshul dang bstun nas kyang rgyud sde bzhir nges te /
NK129(to)001:1381: gnyis gnyis 'khyud dang lag bcang dang //
NK129(to)001:1382: bltas dang rgod dang 'khrigs pa yi //
NK129(to)001:1383: srin po yi ni tshul gyis su //
NK129(to)001:1384: rgyud ni rnam pa bzhi ru bshad //
NK129(to)001:1387: sems can gyi dbang po'i rim pa dang bstun nas /
NK129(to)001:1388: rgyud sde bzhin rim par bshad de /
NK129(to)001:1390: sems can dman la bya ba'i rgyud //
NK129(to)001:1391: de lhag rnams la spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK129(to)001:1392: sems can mchog la rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK129(to)001:1393: de lhag rnams la bla med rgyud //
NK129(to)001:1396: khrus dang gtsang sbra la sogs pa lus ngag gi
NK129(to)001:1397: bya ba gtso bor ston pas na bya ba'i rgyud
NK129(to)001:1398: do // spyad pa bya ba dang mthun zhing //
NK129(to)001:1399: ting nge 'dzin rnal 'byor dang mthun te theg pa
NK129(to)001:1400: gnyis kyi don spyod pas na spyod pa'i rgyud do
NK129(to)001:1401: // nang ting nge 'dzin gtso che bas na rnal 'byor gyi rgyud do /
NK129(to)001:1403: ches 'phags pa'i phyir rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1405: ye shes rdo rje'i rgyud las /
NK129(to)001:1406: rtags pa'i rgyud ni stong phrag bzhi //
NK129(to)001:1407: bya ba'i rgyud ni stong phrag bzhi //
NK129(to)001:1408: spyod pa'i rgyud ni stong phrag brgyad //
NK129(to)001:1409: gnyis ka'i rgyud ni stong phrag drug /
NK129(to)001:1410: rnal 'byor stong phrag bcu gnyis so //
NK129(to)001:1411: de ltar stong phrag sum cu sogs //
NK129(to)001:1412: rgyas par bshad na tshad med do //
NK129(to)001:1413: zhes lngar byas nas tshad gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:1416: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud gsum gyi chos sde ngos bzung na /
NK129(to)001:1417: bka' rnying 'gyur gyi phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud gsum dang mthun no //
NK129(to)001:1418: bye brag tu rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud la gsum te /
NK129(to)001:1421: gnyis su med pa snying po don gyi rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1422: pha rgyud dang ma rgyud kyi khyad par kyang /
NK129(to)001:1425: skyes pa rnams ni gdul bya'i phyir //
NK129(to)001:1426: rnal 'byor pha yi rgyud bshad cing //
NK129(to)001:1427: bud med rnams ni gdul ba'i phyir //
NK129(to)001:1428: rnal 'byor ma yi rgyud rab bshad //
NK129(to)001:1430: yang rdzogs rim gyi gnas skabs na /
NK129(to)001:1431: rtsa gtso bor ston pa ni ma rgyud /
NK129(to)001:1432: rlung gtso bor ston pa ni pha rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1434: gnas de rnams su dpa' bo ni //
NK129(to)001:1435: rlung gi khams dang yang dag ldan //
NK129(to)001:1436: gnas de rnams su dpa' mo ni //
NK129(to)001:1437: rtsa yi khams dang yang dag ldan //
NK129(to)001:1439: yang skyed rim kyi skabs na /
NK129(to)001:1440: lha pho shas che ba ni pha rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1441: mo shas che ba ni ma rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1442: gnyis su med pa snying po don gyi rgyud ni /
NK129(to)001:1443: de rnams cha mnyam par ston pa yin te /
NK129(to)001:1445: gnyis med gnyis su med par ston //
NK129(to)001:1447: de la rgyud sde ngos bzung na /
NK129(to)001:1449: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa gshin rje dgra nag /'jigs byed /
NK129(to)001:1450: dam pa dang po'i rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1455: ma h+aa m+aa ya la sogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1456: gnyis su med pa snying po don gyi rgyud ni /
NK129(to)001:1457: rtsa ba'i rgyud rab tu mi gnas pa /
NK129(to)001:1458: bshad pa'i rgyud bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK129(to)001:1459: gnyis ka'i rgyud rnyog pa med pa /
NK129(to)001:1460: rgyab rten gyi rgyud he ru ka bzang po /
NK129(to)001:1461: phan par byed pa'i rgyud ye shes snying po /
NK129(to)001:1462: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i rgyud 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul dra ba le'u khri drug stong pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1463: de rnams ni rgyud sde spyi'i rnam grangs phye ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:1464: rgyud sde re re la yang bye brag tu phye na /
NK129(to)001:1465: rgyud rgyas pa yan lag bdun ldan du 'dod pa dang //
NK129(to)001:1467: bshad rgyud gnyis su 'dod pa'i lugs so //
NK129(to)001:1473: ma tshang ba kha skong ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)001:1474: dka' ba yongs su gcod pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)001:1475: bkol ba dum bur phyung ba'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1477: tho mar ston pa bdag nyid kyis gsungs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)001:1478: de'i rjes la 'chad pa'i skyes bus gsungs pa bshad
NK129(to)001:1479: pa'i rgyud rtsa rgyud du gab pa rnams sngon du
NK129(to)001:1480: phyung ba ni rgyud phyi ma /
NK129(to)001:1481: phyi ma na ma gsal bar gsal bar byas pa ni phyi ma'i phyi ma /
NK129(to)001:1482: rtsa rgyud du ma tshang ba rnams logs su gsungs pa ma tshang ba kha skong ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)001:1483: rtsa ba'i dka' gnad logs su bkral ba yongs su gcod pa'i rgyud /
NK129(to)001:1484: rtsa bshad nas bkol logs su phyung ba ni skol ba dum bu'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1485: yang rtsa bshad gnyis su phyed na /
NK129(to)001:1486: snga mar byung zhing bshad gzhir gyur pa ni rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK129(to)001:1487: rjes la byung zhing 'chad byed du dug pa ni bshad pa'i rgyud do /
NK129(to)001:1488: bshad rgyud la tshul drug ste /
NK129(to)001:1489: mi gsal ba gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1490: ma tshang ba kha skong ba dang /
NK129(to)001:1491: tshul mi 'dra ba ston pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1493: cha mthun nges pa bskyed pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1494: tshig don rnam par phye ba'i bshad pa'i rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1496: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu tshang bar ston pa la /
NK129(to)001:1499: gdams gtad dang bcas par ston pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1500: de rnams tshang na rgyud yongs su rdzogs pa chen po /
NK129(to)001:1501: de rnams ma tshang bar ston na rgyud 'thor ba zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)001:1502: man ngag dang sgrub thabs la yang lnga ste /
NK129(to)001:1508: ngo bo ni mi bslu bas de man ngag dang 'dra bas de man ngag go /
NK129(to)001:1509: de yang bdud rtsi dum pa gsum pa las /
NK129(to)001:1510: bu gcig ma 'tshol bde bas mtshan nas zhes so //
NK129(to)001:1513: thabs che tshegs chung don dpag med /
NK129(to)001:1514: bya sla dpag dka' man ngag dam pa yin /
NK129(to)001:1517: de kho na nyid kyi man ngag dang /
NK129(to)001:1518: mngon par rtogs pa'i rim pa'i man ngag go /
NK129(to)001:1519: de kho na nyid kyi man ngag ni rdzogs pa chen po rtsa ba bco brgyad dam /
NK129(to)001:1521: do ha bskor gsum lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:1522: mngon par rtogs pa'i man ngag la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:1523: shes shing gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1524: bslab cing nyams su blangs ba'o //
NK129(to)001:1528: khog dbub dang sa bcad do //
NK129(to)001:1529: bslab cing nyams su blang ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1530: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu la de'i man ngag kyang bcu'o //
NK129(to)001:1532: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam dang //
NK129(to)001:1536: rgyud sde bzhi'i man ngag bzhi'am /
NK129(to)001:1537: phyi nang gnyis kyi man ngag gnyis sam /
NK129(to)001:1538: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi man ngag go /
NK129(to)001:1540: lung la 'dris shing tshad la mkhas /
NK129(to)001:1541: rang gi nyams myong man ngag ldan /
NK129(to)001:1542: yongs su shing bya'i dngos po la /
NK129(to)001:1543: tshad du phyin pas man ngag brtsam //
NK129(to)001:1545: de rnams ni shes bya'i yul gyi rnam par bzhag pa bstan te /
NK129(to)001:1546: chos spyi'i rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1547: gnyis pa yul de dag gi khyad par la bcu ste /
NK129(to)001:1548: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i khyad par dang /
NK129(to)001:1549: 'jig rten pa'i lam dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam gyi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)001:1550: grub mtha' blos bsgyur ma bsgyur gyi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)001:1552: sangs rgyas pa'i khyad par dang /
NK129(to)001:1553: theg pa che chung gi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)001:1554: sngags mtshan nyid kyi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)001:1555: sngags phyi nang gi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)001:1556: nang pa bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)001:1557: bka' bstan bcos kyi khyad par dang /
NK129(to)001:1558: sngags gsar rnying gi khyad par dang bcu'o //
NK129(to)001:1559: dang po 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:1561: nang skye rgas na 'chi bzhi dang ldan pa ni 'khor ba yin la /
NK129(to)001:1562: de dang bral ba ni mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1565: skye rgas na 'chi bzhi ldan pas //
NK129(to)001:1566: mtshan nyid ther zug ma yin pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1570: mya ngan 'das par der brjod do //
NK129(to)001:1573: ston pa sprul pa'i sku la yang de bzhi dang ldan pas /
NK129(to)001:1574: mya ngan las ma 'das sam zhe na /
NK129(to)001:1575: de ni gzhan don la de ltar snang ba yin la /
NK129(to)001:1576: yang dag par na de bzhi dang bral te /
NK129(to)001:1578: khyod ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK129(to)001:1584: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam gyi khyad par ni //
NK129(to)001:1585: chos 'ga' zhig gi sgor zhugs nas mthar phyin par bsgrubs kyang /
NK129(to)001:1588: mi 'da' bas na 'jig rten pa'i lam zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)001:1589: chos 'ga' zhig gi sgor zhugs nas mthar phyin par bsgrubs pas 'jig rten las g.yo /
NK129(to)001:1592: 'jig rten pa las 'das pa'i lam zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)001:1594: sbyin pa la 'jig rten pa yang yod /
NK129(to)001:1595: 'jig rten las 'das pa na yang yod do //
NK129(to)001:1597: 'jig rten pa'i sbyin pa gang zhe na /
NK129(to)001:1598: gang sbyin pa byin pas 'jig rten las mi g.yo /
NK129(to)001:1600: mi 'da' na 'jig rten pa'i sbyin pa zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)001:1601: gang sbyin pa de byin pas 'jig rten las g.yo /
NK129(to)001:1603: 'da' bas na 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sbyin pa zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)001:1604: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:1605: grub mtha' blos bsgyur ba dang ma bsgyur ba'i khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:1607: phyi ma'i bde ba 'dod cing de sgrub pa'i thabs la zhugs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:1609: phyi ma'i bde ba mi 'dod cing /
NK129(to)001:1610: de sgrub pa'i thabs la ma zhugs pa ni /
NK129(to)001:1611: grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba'o //
NK129(to)001:1612: zhes zer ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:1613: mu stegs chad par smra ba dag tshe phyi ma mi 'dod la /
NK129(to)001:1614: 'on kyang grub mtha' 'dzin pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:1616: thos bsam gyis rang gi lta ba nges par byas pa ni /
NK129(to)001:1618: thos bsam gyis rang gi lta ba nges par ma byas pa ni grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba'o //
NK129(to)001:1619: grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1620: byis pa so so skye bo yin te /
NK129(to)001:1624: tshe snga phyi yod med dang /
NK129(to)001:1625: las dkar nag gang yang mi shes pa'i blun po rnams so //
NK129(to)001:1628: las dkar nag ngo shes kyang de'i rjes su mi 'brang bar /
NK129(to)001:1629: tshe phyi ma rgyang du bzhag nas //
NK129(to)001:1630: tshe 'di yi phan bde sgrub pa ste /
NK129(to)001:1631: 'jig rten pa'i rig pa'i gnas la slob pa rnams so //
NK129(to)001:1632: grub mthas blo bsgyur ba la phyi rol mu stegs pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1634: de gnyis kyi khyad par la 'dod gzhung mang ste /
NK129(to)001:1636: dang po 'ga' zhig na re rten skyabs gnas kyi khyad par yod de /
NK129(to)001:1637: dbang phyug chen po dang khyab 'jug la sogs pa
NK129(to)001:1638: la ston par 'dzin des gsungs pa'i chos la lam
NK129(to)001:1639: du byed / de sgrub pa'i chos la lam dang /
NK129(to)001:1640: de sgrub pa'i dge 'dun la lam sgrub pa'i grogs su byed pa ni mu stegs pa /
NK129(to)001:1641: yang sangs rgyas sku gsum la ston par 'dzin cing /
NK129(to)001:1642: des gsungs pa'i chos la lam dang /
NK129(to)001:1643: de sgrub pa'i dge 'dun la lam sgrub pa'i grogs su byed par ni nang pa sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1644: zhes zer ba yang mi 'thad de //
NK129(to)001:1645: mu stegs gnas ma bu'i sde pa yang nang par 'gyur te /
NK129(to)001:1646: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:1647: lha khyab 'jug la 'jug pa bcu yod pa las /
NK129(to)001:1648: sh+aakya thub pa'ang khyab 'jug gi sprul par 'dod cing de la skyabs su 'gro bas /
NK129(to)001:1652: rtag par lta ba dang ma bral ba'i ngos su mu stegs kyi sde pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:1654: bya ba spyod pa la khyad par yod do //
NK129(to)001:1656: 'dod pa bsod snyoms kyi mthar lhung ba ni phyi rol pa /
NK129(to)001:1657: de gnyis su ma lhung ba ni nang pa yin /
NK129(to)001:1658: zhes zer ba yang mi 'thad de nyan thos kyi
NK129(to)001:1659: sbyangs ba'i yon tan bcu gnyis kyang ngal zhing dub
NK129(to)001:1661: ma h+aa yo gas 'dod yon lnga longs spyod cing /
NK129(to)001:1662: tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK129(to)001:1663: rdo rje slob dpon gyi chas brgyad gon pa yang 'dod pa bsod snyoms kyi mtha' yin no /
NK129(to)001:1665: lta ba la khyad par yod de /
NK129(to)001:1669: bdag med pa khas len pa ni nang pa /
NK129(to)001:1674: chad pa cang med pa khas len pa ni phyi rol pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1676: de bzhin tshogs pa khyad par du stong ngam /
NK129(to)001:1677: kha yar ba khyad par stong /
NK129(to)001:1679: nyan thos pas stong pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1680: chos kyi bdag med khas len mi nus pas phyi par 'gro la /
NK129(to)001:1681: kha yar khyad par du stong na /
NK129(to)001:1682: rgyu 'bras chad pa'i stong pa tsam du mu stegs pa yang khas len no /
NK129(to)001:1683: yang rtag pa chos bzhi ldan du khas len pa mu stegs yin na /
NK129(to)001:1684: mdo sde mya ngan las 'das pa las /
NK129(to)001:1685: thub pa mya ngan las 'da' khar rtag pa chos bzhi ldan khas blangs 'dug pas /
NK129(to)001:1686: de yang mu stegs su 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)001:1690: skra'i lwa ba can la sogs pa'i spyod pa brten pa mu stegs pa /
NK129(to)001:1691: chos spyod bcu spyod pa ni nang pa yin zer ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:1692: mu stegs pa la yang kho rang gi gzhung gi chos spyod bcu shin du yang yod la /
NK129(to)001:1695: ral pa'i thor tshugs can phyi rol pa /
NK129(to)001:1698: zer ba yang mi 'thad de ral pa'i thor tshugs kho na lcang lo can yin te /
NK129(to)001:1699: nang pa'i lha longs sku thams cad la ral pa'i thor tshugs yod do //
NK129(to)001:1700: dbu reg kyang mu stegs kyi dge slong la shin tu yang yod do //
NK129(to)001:1701: des na phyogs re nas de rnams thams cad bden te /
NK129(to)001:1702: skyon phyogs re med pa med do //
NK129(to)001:1703: 'o na ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:1704: bdag rkyen spangs pa dang rtogs pa mthar thug pa'i sangs rgyas kyis byas na /
NK129(to)001:1705: dngos dang brgyud pa'i bstan pa mtha' dag la nang pa sangs rgyas pa zhes bya'o /
NK129(to)001:1706: bdag rkyen mu stegs kyi ston pa drug gis byas
NK129(to)001:1707: nas gsungs pa'i dngos dang brgyud pa'i bstan pa mtha'
NK129(to)001:1708: dag la mu stegs zhes bya'o //
NK129(to)001:1710: mu stegs zhes bya ba rtag par smra ba dang /
NK129(to)001:1711: mur thug pa zhes bya ba chad par smra ba gnyis so //
NK129(to)001:1712: nang pa sangs rgyas la'ang gnyis ste /
NK129(to)001:1715: de gnyis kyi nang pa'i theg pa che chung gi khyad par la yang /
NK129(to)001:1718: chos lnga dag dang rang bzhin gsum //
NK129(to)001:1719: rnam par shes pa brgyad nyid de //
NK129(to)001:1720: bdag med gnyis kyi nang du ni //
NK129(to)001:1721: theg pa chen po mtha' dag 'dus //
NK129(to)001:1724: ming rgyu mtshan rnam rtog de bzhin nyid /
NK129(to)001:1729: yongs grub gsum mo rnam par shes pa brgyad dang /
NK129(to)001:1731: de rnams khas len mi nus na theg pa chung ngu yin /
NK129(to)001:1732: de rnams khas len nus pa theg pa chen po /
NK129(to)001:1734: dbu ma bas rnam shes tshogs brgyad khas len mi
NK129(to)001:1735: nus pas theg pa chung ngu bzhin du 'gyur ro
NK129(to)001:1737: bdag nyid khas len nus so //
NK129(to)001:1739: klu sgrub kyi gzhung gi nyan thos kyis kyang bdag med rtogs par 'dod pas mi stub bo //
