NK129(to)001:1741: dmigs pa che ba nyid dang ni //
NK129(to)001:1742: de ni bsgrub pa gnyis dag dang //
NK129(to)001:1743: ye shes brtson 'grus rtsom pa dang //
NK129(to)001:1744: thabs la mkhas par gyur pa dang //
NK129(to)001:1745: yang dag bsgrub pa chen po dang //
NK129(to)001:1746: sangs rgyas 'phrin las chen po de //
NK129(to)001:1747: chen po bdun dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK129(to)001:1748: theg chen zhes ni nges par brjod /
NK129(to)001:1750: chen po bdun dang ldan pa ni theg pa chung ngu bzhin du gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:1751: yang lang dkar gshegs pa las /
NK129(to)001:1752: theg pa'i rang bzhin shes rab snying rje ste //
NK129(to)001:1753: de dang mi ldan theg chen khas len pa //
NK129(to)001:1754: dper na wa yis seng lpags gon dang mtshungs //
NK129(to)001:1756: shes rab che zhing snying rje che ba ni theg pa chen po /
NK129(to)001:1757: shes rab chung zhing snying rje chung ba ni /
NK129(to)001:1760: theg pa chung ngu gnyis ni /
NK129(to)001:1761: shes rab chung zhing chos kyi bdag med ma rtogs /
NK129(to)001:1762: snying rje chung ste rang don gtso bor byed /
NK129(to)001:1764: theg pa chen po ni snying rje che ste /
NK129(to)001:1767: shes rab che ste bdag med gnyis rtogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1768: de la rgol ba dag na re /
NK129(to)001:1769: klu sgrub kyi gzhung gis nyan thos kyis kyang bdag med gnyis rtogs par bzhed do //
NK129(to)001:1774: 'dzin pa ma spangs phyir dang ni //
NK129(to)001:1775: rten gyi bse ru lta bu ste //
NK129(to)001:1776: nyan thos dag las khyad par 'phags //
NK129(to)001:1778: rang rgyal gyis kyang chos kyi bdag phyogs gcig ma rtogs na /
NK129(to)001:1779: nyan thos kyis bdag gal rtogs so //
NK129(to)001:1780: yang nyan thos mchog chen po gnyis kyis /
NK129(to)001:1781: snga 'gro'i dus su srid pa gsum gyi sems can
NK129(to)001:1782: rnams theg pa gsum gyi byang chub la ma 'khod
NK129(to)001:1783: kyi bar la gro mi bza' bar bya'o //
NK129(to)001:1786: nyan thos mchog chen gnyis ni sprul pa po yang yin la /
NK129(to)001:1787: sangs rgyas kyis byin gyis brlabs pa yang yin no //
NK129(to)001:1788: theg pa che chung gnyis rang rang gi stobs 'gran pa'i dus su /
NK129(to)001:1789: dang po rgyu sems bskyed la khyad yod de /
NK129(to)001:1790: chung ngu ni rang zhi bde la dmigs la /
NK129(to)001:1791: chen po ni sems can gyi don la dmigs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1792: lam 'jug pa la khyad yod de //
NK129(to)001:1793: chung ngu ni rang zhi bde la gnas na lam sgrod de /
NK129(to)001:1794: chen po ni sems can gyi don du lus dang longs spyod thams cad gtong nus pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1795: 'bras bu mdzad pa la khyad yod de /
NK129(to)001:1796: chung ngu yis rang gi zhi bde sngon du byed la /
NK129(to)001:1797: chen pos sems can gyi don du mdzad pa sna tshogs ston pas khyad shin tu che'o //
NK129(to)001:1798: theg pa chen po la rgyu mtshan nyid dang 'bras
NK129(to)001:1799: bu gsang sngags kyi khyad par la 'dod gzhung mang
NK129(to)001:1802: skye bo chags bral gyi don du gsungs pa ni mtshan nyid /
NK129(to)001:1803: chags can gyi don du gsungs pa ni gsang sngags zer ro //
NK129(to)001:1805: skye bo 'dod chags can ched du //
NK129(to)001:1806: 'di yi byed pa rdo rje sems //
NK129(to)001:1809: skye bo mi bzad pa yi las //
NK129(to)001:1811: thabs dang ldan na de nyid kyang //
NK129(to)001:1815: yul 'dod pa'i yon tan spong ba ni rgyu yi theg pa yin la /
NK129(to)001:1816: mi spong ba ni sngags kyi theg pa zer te /
NK129(to)001:1818: chags can ye shes 'dod pa yis //
NK129(to)001:1819: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga brten bya //
NK129(to)001:1821: de la rgol ba na re /
NK129(to)001:1822: 'phags pa chos 'phags la btsun mo drug khri yod /
NK129(to)001:1823: rtag tu ngu la lnga brgya yod pas /
NK129(to)001:1824: de kun kyang chags bcas min te /
NK129(to)001:1826: khyim par gyur kyang rtag tu dngos po kun ma chags /
NK129(to)001:1828: byang chub sems dpa' 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga spyod kyang /
NK129(to)001:1831: byang chub sems dpa' de dag ni sa lam mtho bas /
NK129(to)001:1832: nyon mongs pa dang 'dod yon gyi skyon gyis ma gos pas /
NK129(to)001:1833: gzhan yang sems dpa' che la gzhan don mthong na mi dge ba bdun gnang ba yin gyis /
NK129(to)001:1834: thabs khyad par can gyis nyon mongs pa 'dod yon lam du slongs pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:1835: tshul gsum pa'i sgron ma las /
NK129(to)001:1836: don gcig na'ang ma rmongs pa dang //
NK129(to)001:1837: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1838: dbang po rnon pa'i dbang byed dang //
NK129(to)001:1839: sngags kyi bstan chos khyad par 'phags //
NK129(to)001:1840: zhes pas khyad par bzhi 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:1841: bsgrub bya mthar thug shes bya'i gnas lugs gcig kyang /
NK129(to)001:1842: pha rol tu phyin pa zhor la smos te chos nyid de go yul lam /
NK129(to)001:1843: rjes dpag gi yul du byed la /
NK129(to)001:1844: gsang sngags ni ma rmongs te /
NK129(to)001:1845: thabs khyad par gyi chos nyid mngon sum du bstan la phebs so //
NK129(to)001:1846: yang rgyu'i theg pa ni thabs nyung ste /
NK129(to)001:1847: pha rol tu phyin pa drug tsam las med /
NK129(to)001:1852: mchog thun mong gi sgrub pa dang /
NK129(to)001:1854: 'pho ba grong 'jug la sogs thabs du ma ston no //
NK129(to)001:1855: yang pha rol tu phyin pa ni bya dka' ste /
NK129(to)001:1856: byang chub gyi spyod pa sna tshogs la slob dgos so //
NK129(to)001:1857: gsang sngags ni bya sla ste /
NK129(to)001:1859: dka' spyad la mi ltos so //
NK129(to)001:1860: yang mtshan nyid ni dbang po rtul pos rim gyis rtogs par byed pa'i thabs yin la /
NK129(to)001:1862: dbang po rnon po gcig char rtogs par byed pa'i thabs yin pas khyad par che gsungs /
NK129(to)001:1863: yang mdo gdam ngag bog pa'i rgyal po las /
NK129(to)001:1864: rgyu la spyod pa rgyu yi chos //
NK129(to)001:1865: 'khor lo bzhin du bskor byas nas //
NK129(to)001:1866: 'bras bu'i theg pa nye lam zhig /
NK129(to)001:1867: dus tshig phyi mar 'byung ba snang //
NK129(to)001:1869: sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyu tsam du shes nas
NK129(to)001:1870: lam du byed pa ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg
NK129(to)001:1871: pa / sems nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bor shes nas lam du byed pa ni /
NK129(to)001:1872: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa zer ro //
NK129(to)001:1873: de la rgol ba dag na re /
NK129(to)001:1874: khyed gsang sngags pa 'bras bu lam du byed pa ste /
NK129(to)001:1875: 'bras bu smin pa gcig lam du byed dam /
NK129(to)001:1876: ma smin pa lam du byed /
NK129(to)001:1877: smin nas kyang lam du byed dgos pa'i phyir thug pa med par thal /
NK129(to)001:1878: smin kyang lam du byed dgos pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:1879: ma smin pa lam du byed na /
NK129(to)001:1880: ma smin pa'i phyir 'bras bu ma smin par thal /
NK129(to)001:1886: khyed mtshan nyid pa'i lugs kyi pha rol tu phyin pa drug lam du byed pa yin nam min /
NK129(to)001:1888: kun lam pha rol phyin pa 'di yin gzhan ma yin /
NK129(to)001:1890: lam du byed pa yin na /
NK129(to)001:1891: phyin zin pa lam du byed dam /
NK129(to)001:1892: pha phyin pa lam du byed /
NK129(to)001:1893: phyin this pa lam du byed na thug pa med par thal /
NK129(to)001:1894: ma phyin pa lam du byed na pha rol du phyin pa ma yin par thal lo //
NK129(to)001:1895: kho na re sngar ma phyin par byed pa yin zer na /
NK129(to)001:1896: 'dir yang sngar ma smin pa smin par byed pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:1900: ma smin zhes skur pa mi 'debs te //
NK129(to)001:1901: 'bras bu ngo bo lam du byed pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:1902: 'bras bu'i ngo bo gang yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:1903: sku dang ye shes yin la /
NK129(to)001:1904: de ye nas rang la gnas pa ni 'bras bu yin pas /
NK129(to)001:1905: de ma shes pa shes par byed pa'am /
NK129(to)001:1906: mi gsal ba gsal ba byed pa'am //
NK129(to)001:1907: mngon du ma gyur pa gyur bar byed pa tsam la lam du byed zer ba yin /
NK129(to)001:1908: mdor na thob bya da lta nyid nas rang la gnas pa ni 'bras bu /
NK129(to)001:1909: de la sgrib par byed pa'i zhen pa 'dag par
NK129(to)001:1910: byed pa tsam la lam du byed zer ba yin
NK129(to)001:1911: no // de la skyon gsum te /
NK129(to)001:1912: dang po sangs rgyas skyon dang bcas par 'gyur te /
NK129(to)001:1913: sangs rgyas yin kyang 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:1914: gnyis pa 'khor ba yon tan dang bcas par thal te /
NK129(to)001:1915: 'khor ba'i yon tan thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas du 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:1916: gsum pa lam 'bad pa don med du thal te /
NK129(to)001:1917: ye nas sangs rgyas yin na lam sgom pa la don med pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK129(to)001:1919: dang po sangs rgyas skyon dang bcas par mi 'gyur te /
NK129(to)001:1920: ye nas sangs rgyas yin kyang yin pa la yin par ma shes pa yin te /
NK129(to)001:1921: rgyal bu rmangs su 'khyams kyang rgyal po'i rigs mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:1923: 'khor ba yon tan dang bcas pa 'dod thog ste /
NK129(to)001:1924: 'khor ba ye nas sangs rgyas yin pas yin pa la yin par nyams su blangs pas /
NK129(to)001:1925: yin par rtogs su btub pa ste /
NK129(to)001:1926: rmun loong la 'khor los bsgyur ba'i mtshan dpe lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:1928: lam la 'bad pa don med du yang mi 'gyur te /
NK129(to)001:1929: 'khor ba ye nas sangs rgyas yin kyang yin pa la yin par ngo ma shes pa de /
NK129(to)001:1930: lam gyis shes par byed pa ni /
NK129(to)001:1931: dbul mo gter dang sprod par byed pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:1932: rgyas pa gzhan la yang yod de /
NK129(to)001:1933: lta ba gtan la 'bebs tshul gyi sgo nas rtogs par myur bul gyi khyad par yod de /
NK129(to)001:1934: gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' la mthar lhung ma lhung gi khyad par yod /
NK129(to)001:1935: chos nyid nyams su len pa'i dus su blo yul du byed mi byed kyi khyad par yod /
NK129(to)001:1936: 'bras bu thob pa'i dus la lam myur bul gyi khyad par yod /
NK129(to)001:1937: 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo'i skabs na gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi khyad par yod /
NK129(to)001:1938: gzhung legs par brtags na don gsal gyi bar ston mi ston gyi khyad par yod do //
NK129(to)001:1939: 'bras bu gsang sngags la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:1940: phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)001:1941: nang ba thabs kyi rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:1942: de gnyis kyi khyad par yang /
NK129(to)001:1943: dang po rgyud gzhung gi skabs su /
NK129(to)001:1944: rgyud kyi dngos po bcus phyir 'gyur na phyi ba /
NK129(to)001:1945: nang du gyur na nang ba'o //
NK129(to)001:1946: lta ba'i skabs su rang byung gi ye shes smra mi nus na phyi pa /
NK129(to)001:1947: smra nus pa na nang ba'o //
NK129(to)001:1949: 'khor ba'i chos nyi shu la thabs kyis zin nas spyod nus pa nang pa /
NK129(to)001:1951: yang dngos grub kyi skabs su phyi nas re ba phyi pa /
NK129(to)001:1952: nang nas re ba nang pa'o //
NK129(to)001:1953: dbang gi skabs su zab mo'i dbang gsum ston nus pa nang pa /
NK129(to)001:1955: nang pa bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:1956: ting nge 'dzin gyis rim gyis bskyed pa gtso che ba ma h+aa /
NK129(to)001:1957: lha rdzogs tshul du bskyed pa a nu'o //
NK129(to)001:1958: bskyed rdzogs gnyis las grol ba a ti yo ga'o //
NK129(to)001:1959: yang rang rig pa'i cho 'phrul du snang ba ma h+aa /
NK129(to)001:1960: rang rig pa'i rtsal du snang ba a nu /
NK129(to)001:1961: rig pa rang snang ba a ti'o //
NK129(to)001:1962: yang rgyud kyi dngos po bcu la ched 'dzin che ba ma h+aa /
NK129(to)001:1963: de bas chung ba a nu /
NK129(to)001:1964: ched 'dzin las grol ba a ti'o //
NK129(to)001:1965: sngags gsar rnying gi khyad par la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:1971: mnga' bdag glang dar mas dam pa'i chos ma bsnubs pa'i gong du bsgyur ba thams cad rnying ma /
NK129(to)001:1972: chos bsnubs nas rjes la phyis rgya gar nas bsgyur ba thams cad la gsar mar grags so //
NK129(to)001:1973: 'gyur byed lo tsi'i khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:1976: gzhon gsum la sogs pas bsgyur ba thams cad rnying mar grags /
NK129(to)001:1979: rngog la sogs pas bsgyur ba la gsar mar grags so //
NK129(to)001:1980: lo ts+aa ba rgan gsum ni /
NK129(to)001:1982: gnyags dz+nya na ku m+aa ra /
NK129(to)001:1988: be ro tsa na ni sngags mtshan nyid gnyis ka'i lo ts+aa ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:1989: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra dang /
NK129(to)001:1990: rma rin chen mchog gnyis kyi sngags phal cher bsgyur /
NK129(to)001:1991: lo ts+aa ba gzhon gsum gyis mtshan nyid shas cher bsgyur ro //
NK129(to)001:1992: brjod bya chos kyi khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:1993: spyir mtshan nyid la gsar rnying du ma grags kyang /
NK129(to)001:1994: don gyi gsar rnying du yod de /
NK129(to)001:1997: mngon pa thams cad rnying 'gyur yin /
NK129(to)001:1998: bshad pa yang bka' chad nas med de /
NK129(to)001:1999: phyis rtsal bshad byas pa yin no /
NK129(to)001:2000: tshad ma la gsar rnying gnyis ka yod /
NK129(to)001:2001: dbu ma phar phyin byams chos rnams sngar yang 'gyur /
NK129(to)001:2002: phyis rngog lo ts+aa ba la sogs pas 'gyur bag re bcos pa yin /
NK129(to)001:2003: bshad bka' ni rgya gar gyi bshad bka' yin no //
NK129(to)001:2004: gsang sngags kyi dbang du byas na /
NK129(to)001:2006: sgrub pa bka' brgyad du grags pa rnams rnying ma yin no //
NK129(to)001:2013: gdan bzhi la sogs pa rnams gsar ma yin no //
NK129(to)001:2014: bzhi pa 'gyur gyi khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:2016: sngon sprul pa'i lo ts+aa bas bsgyur bas gcig thog tu gcig yong la 'dra min mi 'byung /
NK129(to)001:2017: slar rgya gar du bsgyur yang zhu tig btub pa yin par gada'o //
NK129(to)001:2019: phyis lo ts+aa ba so so'i skye bas bsgyur bas /
NK129(to)001:2020: rang gi 'dod pa dang bstun nas bod kyis go
NK129(to)001:2021: bde bar bya ba'i phyir mi 'dra ba mang du
NK129(to)001:2023: khyad par med par 'dod pa'i lugs ni gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:2026: tshig la khyad par med de /
NK129(to)001:2027: 'gyur snga phyi'i tshig zur mi mthun tsam las gzhan med /
NK129(to)001:2028: rnying ma rnams phyis mi 'gyur ba'i rgyu mtshan gong du bshad zin no //
NK129(to)001:2029: don la khyad par med lugs ni /
NK129(to)001:2030: gsang sngags mtha' dag la ma smin pa smin par byed pa dbang dang byin rlabs /
NK129(to)001:2031: smin pa grol bar byed pa lam gnyis su 'dus pa yin /
NK129(to)001:2032: dbang la ming mi 'dra ba yang don mthun te /
NK129(to)001:2033: gsar ma la dbang bzhir grags /
NK129(to)001:2034: rnying ma la dbang bzhir grags pa yang yod /
NK129(to)001:2035: ming gzhan du 'dogs pa yang yod /
NK129(to)001:2038: mchog gi dbang gsum du yang ming 'dogs so //
NK129(to)001:2039: thun mong gi dbang ni phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK129(to)001:2040: khyad par gyi dbang ni nus pa'i dbang lnga /
NK129(to)001:2041: de gnyis ni bum dbang du 'dus pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:2045: gnyis su med pa'i dbang ngo //
NK129(to)001:2047: thig le byang chub kyi sems kyis slob ma'i lce thog tu dbang bskur bas /
NK129(to)001:2049: shes rab kyi gsang dbang ni /
NK129(to)001:2050: shes rab ma la brten nas ngo sprod pa ste /
NK129(to)001:2051: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang yin no //
NK129(to)001:2052: thabs shes gnyis su med par ngo sprod pa ste /
NK129(to)001:2053: shes bya bden pa dbyer med gnas lugs la ngo sprod pas /
NK129(to)001:2055: des na dbang yang shin tu mthun pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:2057: grol lam mtha' dag bskyed rim dang rdzogs rim gnyis
NK129(to)001:2058: su 'dus pa la bskyed rim gyi skabs su ming
NK129(to)001:2061: dang po rnying ma'i mtshams gcod dang /
NK129(to)001:2062: gsar ma'i bsrung ba'i 'khor lo gnyis don gcig pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:2063: de bzhin du bshags pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2065: tshogs sogs gnyis po don gcig /
NK129(to)001:2066: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin stong pa sgom pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2067: ye shes kyi tshogs stong nyid bsgom la gnyis don gcig /
NK129(to)001:2068: kun snang gi ting nge 'dzin snying rje sgom pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2069: tshad med pa bzhi sgom pa don gcig gzhal yas
NK129(to)001:2070: khang 'byung ba rim brtsegs dang bcas pa sgom pa
NK129(to)001:2071: yang don gcig / lha'i sku sgom pa la /
NK129(to)001:2072: lha sku yan lag drug gi bskyed pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2073: mngon par byang chub pa lngas bskyed pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2074: cho ga gsum gyis bskyed pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2075: skad cig dran rdzogs su bskyed pa rnams /
NK129(to)001:2076: gsar rnying gnyis ka la yod de don gcig /
NK129(to)001:2078: mchod pa 'bul ba yan don gcig /
NK129(to)001:2079: gsar ma'i bskyed rim bdud rtsi myang ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2080: rnying ma'i sman mchod lung don gcig /
NK129(to)001:2081: bstod pa dang bzlas pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2082: tshogs dang lhag ma yang don gcig go /
NK129(to)001:2083: bye brag mi 'dra ba gsar rnying gnyis ka la so sor yod do //
NK129(to)001:2084: de ni rgyud sde so so'i lugs yin /
NK129(to)001:2086: rdzogs rim gyi gnas skabs na yang steng sgo rnam par grol ba'i lam /
NK129(to)001:2088: srog shing gsum la brten nas /
NK129(to)001:2089: gtum mo'i rnal 'byor sgom pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2090: 'og sgo bde ba chen po'i lam /
NK129(to)001:2091: mkha' gsang gnyis la brten nas thig le'i 'jug ldog du byed cing /
NK129(to)001:2092: lhan cig skyes pa'i nyams spor ba rnams shin tu gcig pa lags so //
NK129(to)001:2093: de ni khyad par med lugs so //
NK129(to)001:2094: rnying ma khyad par gyi che ba ni /
NK129(to)001:2095: rong pa chos bzang gi zhal nas /
NK129(to)001:2096: gsang sngags rnying ma rnams la /
NK129(to)001:2097: gsar ma bas khyad par du 'phags pa'i che ba drug yod gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:2098: dang po spyan 'dren pa yon bdag gi khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:2099: rnying ma ba'i yon bdag ni /
NK129(to)001:2100: mnga' bdag mes dbon gsum sogs 'phags pa rigs gsum mgon pa'i sprul pas spyan drangs pa yin la /
NK129(to)001:2101: de ltar gang zag skya res yon bdag byas nas bsgyur ba'i chos dang mi 'dra gsungs /
NK129(to)001:2102: phyag bzhes gtsug lag khang gi khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:2103: sngon dpal gyi bsam yas sogs chos skor stod smad du gdan phab nas gsungs pa yin la /
NK129(to)001:2104: da lta'i dgon bu lcag lcog dang mi 'dra gsungs /
NK129(to)001:2105: 'gyur byed lo ts+aa ba'i khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:2106: sngon spa sgor bee ro tsa na dang /
NK129(to)001:2107: ska lcog gnyis la sogs pa /
NK129(to)001:2108: sprul pa'i lo ts+aa bas bsgyur ba'i chos yin la /
NK129(to)001:2109: da lta'i lo ts+aa ba dgun bal yul du bsdad /
NK129(to)001:2111: sngon gyi mkhas pa'i 'gyur la rang gzo'i bcos ma sna tshogs byed pa dang mi 'dra gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:2117: pad+ma 'byung gnas la sogs pa rig 'dzin gyi sa
NK129(to)001:2118: la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpas spyan drangs pa'i
NK129(to)001:2119: chos yin la / da lta'i pan+di ta lto ma
NK129(to)001:2120: phyid pa bod du gser 'tshol du yod ba'i bzang
NK129(to)001:2121: sprang tsho gcig dang mi 'dra gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:2122: zhu rten me tog gi khyad par yang /
NK129(to)001:2123: sngon gser phye bre la 'jal nas phul /
NK129(to)001:2124: gser sha ba'i blud bu bkang nas phul /
NK129(to)001:2125: gser rta khal dang drel khal du phul nas zhus pa'i chos yin la /
NK129(to)001:2126: da ltar mchan nas gser zho re re gnyis gnyis
NK129(to)001:2127: nyug nyug byas nas zhus pa'i chos dang mi 'dra
NK129(to)001:2128: gsungs so // brjod bya chos kyi khyad par yang /
NK129(to)001:2129: sngon sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa gra ma nyams pa'i
NK129(to)001:2130: dus sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba bka' 'gyur ba med
NK129(to)001:2131: pa gtan la phab pa shes bya'i dngos po'i 'dug
NK129(to)001:2133: de rtogs par byed pa'i thabs du mas brgyan pa'i chos yin la /
NK129(to)001:2134: dus da lta'i dus lo tsa ba rdzun po ches /
NK129(to)001:2135: sngon gyi 'gyur la bcos ma sna tshogs byed /
NK129(to)001:2136: sangs rgyas kyi bka' dang bla ma'i gsung la ras chod byas nas /
NK129(to)001:2137: mi res chos re bcos nas gcig skyon gcig la 'gel /
NK129(to)001:2138: pha de la bu des mi btub pa'i chos dang mi 'dra ste khyad par yod gsungs skad do /
NK129(to)001:2139: bka' bstan bcos gnyis kyi khyad par ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen mchims kyi zhal nas /
NK129(to)001:2140: gnas rgyun chags pa zhig tu /
NK129(to)001:2141: ston pa rgyun chags pa zhig gis /
NK129(to)001:2143: bstan pa rgyun chags pa zhig gsungs pa ni bka' //
NK129(to)001:2144: ston pa nges pa med pas /
NK129(to)001:2147: dus nges pa med pa ru /
NK129(to)001:2148: chos nges pa med pa gsungs pa ni bstan chos yin gsung ste /
NK129(to)001:2149: cis kyang 'di yin gyi bzhag pa mi 'dug /
NK129(to)001:2151: spangs pa dang ye shes phun sum tshogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis dngos su zhal nas gsungs pa'am /
NK129(to)001:2153: byin gyis brlabs pa la ni bka' zhes bya /
NK129(to)001:2154: bka'i don la brten nas phyis 'phags pa dang gang
NK129(to)001:2155: zag rnams kyis mdzad pa rnams la ni bstan bcos
NK129(to)001:2156: zhes bya ste / de yang mdo sde nyi ma'i snying po las /
NK129(to)001:2157: spangs dngas ye shes phun sum tshogs //
NK129(to)001:2158: de yi mthu dang der snang dang //
NK129(to)001:2159: de nyid kyis gsungs bka' ru brjod //
NK129(to)001:2161: nga min nga 'dra dag gis kyang //
NK129(to)001:2162: sangs rgyas bstan la 'grel byed pa //
NK129(to)001:2163: bstan bcos dag tu nga yis bshad //
NK129(to)001:2164: zhes ngo bo'i sgo nas khyad par du 'jog /
NK129(to)001:2167: sangs rgyas mya ngan las ma 'das pa'i gong du gang ci gsungs pa thams cad bka' yin la /
NK129(to)001:2168: sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas gang na ci gsungs pa thams cad bstan chos yin zer /
NK129(to)001:2170: 'o na bstan bcos mngon pa sde bdun po kyang bkar thal /
NK129(to)001:2171: chos kyi phung po sh+aa ri'i bu /
NK129(to)001:2172: gdags pa'i bstan bcos mo'u 'gal bu /
NK129(to)001:2174: mchog gnyis kyis mdzad bar gsungs pas /
NK129(to)001:2176: sangs rgyas ma 'das pa'i gong du 'das pa'i phyir ro zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2177: 'das pa'i rgyu mtshan yang mo'u 'gal gyi bu /
NK129(to)001:2178: sangs rgyas kyi gong du 'das pa 'dul ba lung nas gsungs la /
NK129(to)001:2179: sh+aa ri'i bu gong du 'das par mdo sde drin lan gsab pa las gsungs so //
NK129(to)001:2183: mchog gnyis thub pa'i gong du 'das par gsungs pa de /
NK129(to)001:2184: nyan thos kyi log rtog yin /
NK129(to)001:2185: mdo sngags gnyis nas mo'u 'gal bu gong du ma 'das par gsungs te /
NK129(to)001:2186: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sgo mtha' yas pa nas /
NK129(to)001:2189: nga yongs su mya ngan las 'das pas /
NK129(to)001:2191: 'jig rten gyi khams na nga yi slob ma ji
NK129(to)001:2192: snyed yod pa rnams bsdus shig zhes bka' stsal nas
NK129(to)001:2193: / mo'u 'gal gyi bus ri rab ri'i rtse mor byon nas /
NK129(to)001:2194: 'khor sdud pa'i tshig 'di skad ces gsungs te /
NK129(to)001:2195: bde gshegs slob mar gyur pa gang su dag /'jig rten khams 'dir gnas pa kun nyon cig /
NK129(to)001:2196: deng 'dir ston pas chos kyi 'char 'bebs kyis /
NK129(to)001:2197: gang dag nyan par 'dod na 'dir gshegs shig /
NK129(to)001:2202: 'jig rten gyi khams na nga'i slob ma ji snyed pa rnams bsdus shig /
NK129(to)001:2203: nges par bzhag par bya ba dag yod de /
NK129(to)001:2205: rdzu 'phrul can des chos kyi sgras skad gcig gis go bar grags pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2206: rgyal ba'i zhing gyur nges par gang su dag nges par 'di bar phyogs pa kun nyon cig /
NK129(to)001:2207: deng 'dir rgyal ba'i bdud rtsi gsum 'jog gis //
NK129(to)001:2208: dug gsum 'joms par byed pa kun nyon cig /
NK129(to)001:2211: thub pa 'das nas mdzad pa'i bstan bcos yin zer ro //
NK129(to)001:2215: mngon pa sde bdun kyang bka' yin te /
NK129(to)001:2216: bka' thor bu bar gsungs pa rnams dgra bcom pa bdun gyis sdebs pa yin gsung ngo //
NK129(to)001:2217: de la bstan bcos zer ba yin /
NK129(to)001:2221: zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos dang gsum yod pa las /
NK129(to)001:2222: 'di bstan pa'i chos yin pa'i bstan chos zer ba yin /
NK129(to)001:2223: dngos su bka' yin no gsung ngo //
NK129(to)001:2224: yang na nyan thos mchog chen po gnyis thub pa'i gong du 'das par 'dod pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2225: ma 'das par 'dod pa yang mi 'gal te /
NK129(to)001:2226: mchog gnyis po thub bstan pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2227: bstan la dbab pa'i yul shes bya'i chos bstan pa ste /
NK129(to)001:2228: sa gcod kyi dmigs dang po'o //
NK129(to)001:2229: gnyis pa shes bya'i yul ngos 'dzin par byed pa shes byed skyes bu'i blo la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:2230: grub mthas blo bsgyur ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2232: ma bsgyur ba la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:2237: las rgyu 'bras ngo shes kyang mi shes de gnyis kyi rjes su mi zhugs te /
NK129(to)001:2238: shin tu blun pa byol song lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:2240: de gnyis ngo shes kyang de gnyis kyi rjes su mi zhugs par /
NK129(to)001:2241: tshe phyi ma rgyang du bzhag nas 'di yi phan pa sgrub pas te /
NK129(to)001:2242: bzo dang sman spyad la sogs pa'i rjes su zhugs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2243: grub mtha' blo bsgyur ba gnyis te //
NK129(to)001:2244: 'bras bu 'dod pa tsam du mthun kyang /
NK129(to)001:2245: lam log pa la zhugs pa mu stegs pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2246: 'bras bu yang 'dod cing lam ma log pa la zhugs pa'i nang la sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2250: de gnyis gtan la dbab pa don bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:2254: ngo bo ni log pa'i shes rab kyi phyin ci log gi grub mtha' la mngon par zhen pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2255: nges tshig ni lta ba ngan pa la mu bcas /
NK129(to)001:2256: spyod pa ngan pa la stegs byas pas na mu stegs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2257: kho rang gi 'dod pa ni don la blo zhugs
NK129(to)001:2258: shing bslab pa'i gzhi ma 'khrul pa la 'dod de
NK129(to)001:2259: / de yang tshangs pa'i dra ba las /
NK129(to)001:2260: mu zhes bya ba chos nyid la /
NK129(to)001:2261: stegs zhes bya ba rtogs pa'i gnas //
NK129(to)001:2263: mu stegs la dbye na lta log sum rgya drug cu /
NK129(to)001:2264: 'jig tshogs kyi ri bo drug cu /
NK129(to)001:2265: grags can gyi bdag lta nyer lnga /
NK129(to)001:2268: ston pa drug gi srol ka /
NK129(to)001:2274: rtag par sgro 'dogs pa gnyis su 'dus te /
NK129(to)001:2276: 'jig tshogs lta bu drug cu rtsa gnyis gnyis 'dus ltar /
NK129(to)001:2279: tshangs pa'i lta ba bsam yas kyang //
NK129(to)001:2280: mdor bsdus rtag dang chad pa gnyis //
NK129(to)001:2281: de ltar sum brgya drug cu la brten lugs gsum te //
NK129(to)001:2282: dus kyi sgo nas bgrang ba dang //
NK129(to)001:2283: ston pa'i sgo nas bgrang ba dang //
NK129(to)001:2284: phung po'i sgo nas bgrang ba'o //
NK129(to)001:2285: 'das pa'i mtha' la rtog pa brgya nyi shu /
NK129(to)001:2286: da ltar gyi mtha' la rtog pa brgya nyi shu /
NK129(to)001:2287: ma 'ongs pa mtha' la rtog pa brgya nyi shu ste sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK129(to)001:2288: ston pa sgo nas bgrang ba ni /
NK129(to)001:2289: ston pa 'od srung rdzogs byed kyi lta ba drug cu /
NK129(to)001:2290: ston pa phug ltas kyi drug cu /
NK129(to)001:2291: ston pa ce ta'i bu thub rgyal gyi drug cu /
NK129(to)001:2292: ston pa ka t+ya'i bu nag po can gyi drug cu /
NK129(to)001:2293: ston pa'i 'od srung rdzogs byed kyi drug cu /
NK129(to)001:2294: ston pa be ru wa snyan gyi lta ba drug cu ste /
NK129(to)001:2296: phung po'i sa nas bgrang ba ni /
NK129(to)001:2297: rang bzhin gyi gol sa brgyad /
NK129(to)001:2298: phyogs log gi gol sa bcu gnyis /
NK129(to)001:2300: rang bzhin gyi gol sa brgyad ni /
NK129(to)001:2302: spyod pa yang dag par lta ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2303: 'tshor ba bcos pas yang dag par blta ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2304: skra spu bcos pas yang dag par blta ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2305: lham gos bcos pas yang dag par blta ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2306: rgyan cha gcos pas yang dag par blta ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2307: dka' thub la brten pas yang dag par blta ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2308: bslab pa 'chal ba dang brgyad do //
NK129(to)001:2309: phyogs log gi gol sa bcu gnyis ni /
NK129(to)001:2313: gsang chen ba dang bzhi las /
NK129(to)001:2326: brtul shugs cher spyod pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2331: bslab pa 'chal ba kun gyis gzhi yin pas dbye ba med do //
NK129(to)001:2333: 'og nas 'byung ba'i bdag lta nyi shu rtsis pas sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK129(to)001:2334: 'jig tshogs kyi ri bo drug bcu ni /
NK129(to)001:2336: bdag las byung ba lta bu /
NK129(to)001:2337: bdag la gnas pa snod lta bu /
NK129(to)001:2339: de phung po lnga la sbyar bas nyi shu /
NK129(to)001:2340: de dus la sbyar bas drug cu'o //
NK129(to)001:2341: grangs can gyi bdag lta nyer lnga ni /
NK129(to)001:2346: rdul mun pa gnyis te bcu drug /'byung ba bzhi ste nyi shu /
NK129(to)001:2353: bdag tu lta ba'i ri bo nyi shu ni /
NK129(to)001:2354: bdag gzugs yin zhes pa lnga /
NK129(to)001:2355: bdag dang ldan zhes pa lnga /
NK129(to)001:2356: gzugs bdag yin zhes pa lnga /
NK129(to)001:2357: gzugs bdag dang ldan zhes pa lnga ste phung po lnga la bdag bzhi sbyar bas nyi shu'o //
NK129(to)001:2362: dbang bsgyur can du 'dzin pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2363: bdag po'i don du 'dzin pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2369: ston pa drug gi gong du bshad pa de'o //
NK129(to)001:2371: wa mgo re thod can gyi sde dang /
NK129(to)001:2372: bco brlag mi sha can gyi sde /
NK129(to)001:2373: bse ru bong 'ded can gyi sde dang /
NK129(to)001:2376: chad pa'i sde dang drug go /
NK129(to)001:2378: rang bzhin rgyur lta ba dag /
NK129(to)001:2379: byed pa po rgyur lta ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2380: dbang phyug rgyur lta ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2382: bsdus pa'i don rtag chad gnyis su gnas pa las /
NK129(to)001:2383: chad par smra ba la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:2386: dang po 'dod pa dgod pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2387: chad par smra ba rnams na re /
NK129(to)001:2390: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ston pa med /
NK129(to)001:2391: 'gro ba yang mi dang byol song ba mthong tshad tsam 'di las /
NK129(to)001:2392: lha dang sangs rgyas kyang med /
NK129(to)001:2393: dmyal ba dang yi dwags kyang med zer ba'o //
NK129(to)001:2394: dang po tshe snga phyi med de /
NK129(to)001:2395: lus 'byung ba bzhi las grub ste /
NK129(to)001:2397: shi ba'i tshe lus 'byung ba bzhi la thim /
NK129(to)001:2398: sems ni nam mkha' la yal te /
NK129(to)001:2399: tshe snga ma 'di nas yong bya ba med /
NK129(to)001:2400: phyi ma 'dir 'gro bya ba med do //
NK129(to)001:2402: mdzes ma legs par g.yos la zhim par zo //
NK129(to)001:2403: mi shi bar du ci gang gis //
NK129(to)001:2404: rta ltar zo la bong ltar 'gres //
NK129(to)001:2405: shi nas de yi spyod yul min //
NK129(to)001:2406: mi shi thal ba rlung khyer 'dra //
NK129(to)001:2407: slar skye ba dag ga la srid //
NK129(to)001:2409: de dgag pa ni gnyis las /
NK129(to)001:2410: dang po 'bras bu'i gtan tshigs kyis tshe snga ma yod par bsgrub pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2411: skyes ma thag gi bu chung 'di chos can skye ba sngon ma sngon du song ste /
NK129(to)001:2412: ma slab par goms pa ngang gis 'dzug pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2413: ka kha bslabs pas klog mkhan 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2414: gtan tshigs ma grub ce na /
NK129(to)001:2415: lu gu skyes ma thag tu 'doms su nu ma yod pa shes pa de cis 'gogs /
NK129(to)001:2416: de ka tshe snga phyi'i bag chags sngon du song ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:2417: gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs kyis tshe phyi ma yod par bsgrub pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2421: gnyid log pa'i sems bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2422: kho na re sems tsam 'dug kyang skye ba phyi
NK129(to)001:2423: ma mi len na ci sto ste khyab pa ma
NK129(to)001:2424: grub zer na / sems tsam du 'dug kyang phyi ma mi len pa ci'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2425: tshogs drug 'gags pa'i phyir zer na /
NK129(to)001:2426: 'o na rgyal 'bogs kyi dus su yang tshogs drug 'gags pas phyis mi mi ldang bar thal lo //
NK129(to)001:2427: gnyis pa las rgyu 'bras med par 'dod pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2428: dge ba byas pa'i 'bras bu mtho ris thob pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2429: las sdig pa byas pa'i 'bras bu ngan song du skye ba bya ba med de /
NK129(to)001:2430: tshe 'di yi bde sdug thams cad glo bur ba yin no zer ro //
NK129(to)001:2432: dkar nag gi las 'di chos can /
NK129(to)001:2433: gang byas kyi 'bras bu smin te dam bca'/
NK129(to)001:2434: rnam smin dang rgyu 'bras la 'chol ba nyung ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2437: rgyu nas btab pa'i 'bras bu sran ma skye bar thal /
NK129(to)001:2439: yang dkar nag gi las 'di chos can /
NK129(to)001:2441: 'gro drug la bde sdug 'dug pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2442: mdze pho dang rgyal po bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2444: de las las byung ba min te /
NK129(to)001:2445: rkyen sna tshogs las grub pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2446: nus pa yin no zer na /
NK129(to)001:2449: rgyu med rang gi brtags mthong na //
NK129(to)001:2450: med pa'i chos bzhi srid par 'gyur //
NK129(to)001:2452: rgyu med rkyen la mi ltos phyir /
NK129(to)001:2453: rtag tu yod pa dang med par thal //
NK129(to)001:2455: rgyu med pa la rkyen gyi rtsol ba mi 'jug ste /
NK129(to)001:2456: sa bon med pa'i myu gu bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2457: yang thams cad mkhyen pa'i ston pa med par 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:2459: dpag tshad dang rgyang grag tsam du mchongs srid kyi /
NK129(to)001:2460: nam mkha' la 'phur ba mi srid pa bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:2461: spyangs ba'i rim pa'i 'jig rten du blo rno rtul
NK129(to)001:2462: tsam srid kyis thams cad mkhyen pa mi srid do
NK129(to)001:2465: nyung du bsdu ba'i khyad par las //
NK129(to)001:2466: shin tu khyad 'phags yongs mi srid //
NK129(to)001:2467: mkha' la 'dom bcu tshun chad du //
NK129(to)001:2468: phyogs par 'gyur gyi de las min //
NK129(to)001:2469: sgom par gyur bas 'grub med cing //
NK129(to)001:2471: de dgag pa ni gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:2472: dang po thams cad mkhyen pa sngar byung bar bsgrub pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2474: 'di gsungs pa'i ston pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ston pa gcig yod par dam bca'/
NK129(to)001:2475: brjod bya la 'khrul pa med pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2476: dper na lha khang legs pa mthong bas lha bzo mkhas par rtogs pa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2478: brjod bya la 'khrul pa med kyang /
NK129(to)001:2479: thams cad mkhyen pas ma gsungs na ci sto ste khyab pa ma grub zer na /
NK129(to)001:2480: 'o na lha khang legs par mthong yang /
NK129(to)001:2481: lha bzo mkhas pas ma byas zer na cis 'gogs /
NK129(to)001:2482: rjes su 'gro ldog nges pa yin /
NK129(to)001:2483: gnyis pa thams cad mkhyen pa phyis 'byung du rung bar bsgrub pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2484: rgyud brtan pa goms pa khyad par can yod pa'i sgom chen pa'i shes rgyud ni chos can /
NK129(to)001:2487: sbyangs pa rab kyi mthar thug pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2488: rgyu rkyen 'dzom pa'i 'bras bu bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2489: gtan tshigs ma grub zer na /
NK129(to)001:2490: 'o na rgyu rkyen 'dzom yang 'bras bu mi 'byung bar thal lo //
NK129(to)001:2491: yang 'gro ba rang rang la ji tsam snang ba de tsam yin gyis gzhan mi bden te /
NK129(to)001:2495: 'ga' zhig gis ma mthong bas 'gro ba gzhan yod par mi bden nam /
NK129(to)001:2496: 'ga' zhig gis ma mthong bas yod par mi bden na /
NK129(to)001:2497: khyod kyis ma mthong ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2498: rdo rje gdan yang med par thal /
NK129(to)001:2499: thams cad ma mthong bas mi bden pa rgyu mtshan med de //
NK129(to)001:2500: 'phags pa rnams kyis 'khor 'das ma lus par gzigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:2501: yang chad pa rnams la spyi skyon 'di yang yod de /
NK129(to)001:2502: khyod kyi chad pa de nyams su myong nas chad dam /
NK129(to)001:2504: nyams su myong nas chad na /
NK129(to)001:2507: myong yang chad do zer na /
NK129(to)001:2508: 'o na mig gi yul du yang gzugs chad par thal /
NK129(to)001:2509: myong yang chad pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:2510: de ma chad par mngon sum gyis gsal lo zer na /
NK129(to)001:2511: khyod kyi yang myong bas gsal lo //
NK129(to)001:2512: yang ma myong kyang chad zer na /
NK129(to)001:2513: 'o na rna ba'i yul du yang gzugs snang bar thal /
NK129(to)001:2515: rna ba'i yul du gzugs yod ma myong bar /
NK129(to)001:2516: chad ma chad kyi dpyad ra mi 'jug go /
NK129(to)001:2517: de bzhin du nyams su ma myong ba la chad rgyu med do //
NK129(to)001:2519: rtag par lta smra ba ni /
NK129(to)001:2523: phung po lnga'i rgyun la za ba po dang /
NK129(to)001:2525: byed pa bdag nyid gcig don dam par yod par 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:2527: rtag pa spyir dgag pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2531: yang dag par na rang bzhin med de /
NK129(to)001:2533: cig char gyis don byed nus pas stong pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:2534: ri bong gi rwa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2535: mdo legs pa'i sgron me las /
NK129(to)001:2536: rim gyi ma yin cig car min /
NK129(to)001:2537: rim dang cig car stong pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2538: rang bzhin med ces rgyal bas gsungs /
NK129(to)001:2542: khyod kyi rtag pa des don byed nus sam mi nus /
NK129(to)001:2543: mi nus na rtag pa ma yin par thal /
NK129(to)001:2544: rtag pa ni dngos po yin la /
NK129(to)001:2545: dngos po'i mtshan nyid don byed nus pa yin la /
NK129(to)001:2546: khyod kyi rtag pa de don byed mi nus pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2547: don byed nus so zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2548: rim gyis byed dam cig car byed /
NK129(to)001:2549: rim gyis byed na rtag pa ma yin par thal /
NK129(to)001:2550: rim pa ni 'gyur ba can yin la /
NK129(to)001:2551: rtag pa mi 'gyur bar 'dod pa 'gal lo //
NK129(to)001:2552: cir car byed na rgyu'i dus su 'bras bu smin par thal /
NK129(to)001:2553: 'dod na mngon sum gyis gsal te /
NK129(to)001:2554: sa bon dang myu gu bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2556: gal te rgyu la 'bras gnas na //
NK129(to)001:2557: zas zos mi gtsang za bar 'gyur //
NK129(to)001:2559: yang sngar don byas nas phyis don byed dam mi byed /
NK129(to)001:2560: byed na rtag pa mi 'gyur pa yin pa la /
NK129(to)001:2561: snga phyi 'gyur ba can yin pas na rtag pa nyams /
NK129(to)001:2562: sngar byas nas phyis mi byed na /
NK129(to)001:2563: sngar don byed pa la phyis mi byed par 'gyur bas rtag pa nyams so //
NK129(to)001:2564: bye brag tu dgag pa la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:2565: mtshan ma rdzas kyi rtag pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2566: gnas lugs rig pa'i rtag pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2567: gsang ba'i mtha' rig byed du smra ba'o //
NK129(to)001:2568: dang po mtshan ma rdzas kyi rtag pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2569: bdag ces bya ba dngos po can gcig /
NK129(to)001:2570: sems can kun gyi snying gi dkyil na yod de /
NK129(to)001:2571: che ste che na mthe bong tsam chung ste chung na yungs 'bru tsam /
NK129(to)001:2572: yang chung skra'i rtse mo tsam /
NK129(to)001:2573: dkar la 'tsher ba snum la 'dril ba gcig rtag par gnas te /
NK129(to)001:2574: des las dge sdig byas pa'i rkyen gyis mtho ris dang ngan song du 'gro bar byed pa la /
NK129(to)001:2575: rtag pa'i rtog pa mi 'gyur la /
NK129(to)001:2578: bdag gi rtag pa blo ni 'gyur //
NK129(to)001:2579: phung po nying 'tshams sbyor ba yang //
NK129(to)001:2580: rdza chag bye phur ji bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2581: rtag pa the bong yungs 'bru tsam //
NK129(to)001:2582: bdag ces bya ba de len no //
NK129(to)001:2585: khyod kyi dkar la 'tsher ba de la mig gis rnam shes kyis 'dren nus sam mi nus //
NK129(to)001:2588: mig gi rnam shes 'dra pa'i rdzas ni dngos po can yin la /
NK129(to)001:2589: dngos po can la rtag pa' rdzas mi grub ste /
NK129(to)001:2590: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2592: mig gis rna shes 'dren mi nus so zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2593: 'o na dkar la 'tsher ba yod pa gang gi shes /
NK129(to)001:2595: dngos po can yin nam yid dpyod yin /
NK129(to)001:2596: dngos po can yin na mig gi rnam shes mi 'dren mi srid de /
NK129(to)001:2598: de tshad mas gtan la phab sam ma phab /
NK129(to)001:2599: phab na yid dpyod mi btub la /
NK129(to)001:2600: ma phab na de rtag pa'i dngos por mi 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)001:2601: gnas lugs rig pa'i rtag pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2602: bdag rtag pa gcig pu byed pas so //
NK129(to)001:2603: rang dbang can shes shing rig pa'i bdag nyid can /
NK129(to)001:2604: 'byung ba bzhi las ma skyed pa rig pa'i chos su grub pa /
NK129(to)001:2605: thams cad kyi byed pa po gcig yod zer ro //
NK129(to)001:2607: de lta bu'i rtag pa de skad cig mar yod dam /
NK129(to)001:2609: skad cig mar yod na mi rtag par thal /
NK129(to)001:2610: skad cig ma ni dus gnyis par mi 'dod de 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2612: rgyun de skad gcig ma khyab sam ma khyab /
NK129(to)001:2614: khyab byed skad cig ma med pa'i phyir khyab bya rgyun kyang med par thal /
NK129(to)001:2616: skad cig mas khyab pa'i phyir mi rtag par thal /
NK129(to)001:2617: gsang ba'i mtha' rigs byed du smra ba na re /
NK129(to)001:2618: chos thams cad shes shing rig pa'i phyir bdag nyid can du 'dod /
NK129(to)001:2619: rig pa de yang rtag pa yang ma yin /
NK129(to)001:2622: rtsal snang rig pa sna tshogs su 'char ba gcig tu 'dod /
NK129(to)001:2623: de yang tshangs pa'i d+r+wa ba las /
NK129(to)001:2624: rtag chad gnyis dang bral ba'i dwangs ma gcig /
NK129(to)001:2625: don dam rang bzhin lta ba yin par 'dod //
NK129(to)001:2628: khyod kyi ngo bo mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2629: rtsal snang 'gyur ba gnyis gcig gam tha dad /
NK129(to)001:2630: gcig na rtsal snang gi rig pa 'gyur ba bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:2631: ngo bo nyid kyang 'gyur ba thal /
NK129(to)001:2633: ga bu gcig na sngon po'ang 'chag pa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2634: 'dod na ngo bo nyid mi 'gyur ba'i dam bca' nyams so /
NK129(to)001:2637: ngo bo mi 'gyur ba de las byung ngam /
NK129(to)001:2639: ngo bo mi 'gyur ba las byung na /
NK129(to)001:2640: ngo bo 'gyur ba bzhin du rtsal snang yang mi 'gyur bar thal /
NK129(to)001:2641: rgyu 'bras rjes su 'gro ldog nges pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2642: gser mi 'gyur bas ser mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2643: 'dod na rtsal snang 'gyur ba'i dam bca' nyams so //
NK129(to)001:2645: ngo bo nyid kyi rtsal snang ma yin par thal lo //
NK129(to)001:2646: rta mgyogs pa de g.yag gi yon tan ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2647: des rtag pa gtan la phab pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2648: mu stegs pa'i grub mtha' bshad zin to //
NK129(to)001:2649: nang pa sangs rgyas pa la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:2653: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas so //
NK129(to)001:2659: ngo bo ni chos kyi bdag nyid du lta ba'i sgo nas rang gi zhi bde sgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2662: nyan nyan thos shing thos thos sgrog zhes so //
NK129(to)001:2664: nyan thos sprul pa ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2665: rang rgyud ba dang zhi bar bsgrod pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2670: nyan thos mchog brgyad lta bu /
NK129(to)001:2671: nyan thos kyi tshul bzung nas nyan thos rnams kyi don byed pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2673: theg pa chen po la sdang zhing skur ba 'debs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2675: de las gyes pa'i sde pa bco brgyad po rnams so //
NK129(to)001:2677: 'gog pa la snyom par bzhugs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2681: bsdu na yang mdo sde pa dang bye brag pa gnyis su 'dus so //
NK129(to)001:2682: de rnams gtan la dbab pa la don bzhi bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:2686: dang po nyan thos kyi lta ba la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:2689: dang po spyir bstan pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2690: mu stegs rtag pa bas rtag pa'i gang zag gis bdag rtag pa ni /
NK129(to)001:2692: gang zag gi bdag rtag pa de gcig pu ma yin ste phung po lnga gyes /
NK129(to)001:2693: byed pa po ma grub ste /
NK129(to)001:2694: rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa khams bco brgyad du gyes /
NK129(to)001:2695: za ba po ma grub ste /
NK129(to)001:2696: rnam shes skye pa'i sgo skye mched bcu gnyis su 'dod pas gang zag gi bdag ma grub pa /
NK129(to)001:2697: chos kyi bdag gzung 'dzin don dam par 'dod de
NK129(to)001:2698: bzung ba'i yul gyi rnam pa rags par snang ba
NK129(to)001:2699: 'di blos gzhig cing gzhom du rung ba kun rdzob
NK129(to)001:2700: yin la / 'di tsam bskyed zer ba'i gzhi rdul
NK129(to)001:2701: phra rab cha med ris med ni blos gzhig cing
NK129(to)001:2702: gzhom du mi rung bas don dam du 'dod /
NK129(to)001:2703: 'dzin pa'i sems kyang rags pa'i sems ni dus gsum gyi chas gzhig tu rung bas kun rdzob yin /
NK129(to)001:2704: de tsam bskyed pa'ang zer ba'i skad cig mas dus
NK129(to)001:2705: kyi cha dang bral ba don dam du 'dod de
NK129(to)001:2707: nyan thos bye brag tu smra ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2709: bye brag tu smra ba ni /
NK129(to)001:2710: rdul phra rab skor ba bar dang bcas pa g.yag rnga dang ne sing ltar 'dod pa la /
NK129(to)001:2711: mdo sde ba ni 'byar yang ma 'byar bar yang med /
NK129(to)001:2712: po ti phyir bsdom pa ltar 'dod /
NK129(to)001:2714: khyod rdul phra rab la brten nas gong bu rtsom pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)001:2715: dbus kyi rdul la phyogs cha drug gi rdul gyi skor ram ma skor /
NK129(to)001:2716: ma skor na gong bu rags pa mi 'grub bo /
NK129(to)001:2717: skor na shar gyi rdul gyi dbus kyi rdul la kha ltas pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)001:2718: nub kyi rdul la kha ltas sam ma ltas /
NK129(to)001:2719: bltas na shar gyi rdul dang dbus kyi rdul la thim par thal /
NK129(to)001:2720: ma thim na dbus kyi rdul gyis bar chod pas
NK129(to)001:2721: nub kyi rdul la kha bltar mi bstub ba'i phyir
NK129(to)001:2723: rdul thams cad gcig gi go sar thim par gong bu rags par gtan nas mi 'grub bo //
NK129(to)001:2724: shar gyi rdul des nub kyi rdul la kha ma ltas na /
NK129(to)001:2725: shar gyi rdul de cha shas dang bcas par thal /
NK129(to)001:2726: dbus la kha bltas pa'i cha dang /
NK129(to)001:2727: nub la kha ma ltas pa'i cha gnyis su byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:2729: bral ba'i dam bca' nyams so //
NK129(to)001:2730: yang bye brag pa'i skor ba bar dang bcas pa yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:2731: bar de kar lhag ge yong na snang ba'i rdul yin la /
NK129(to)001:2732: mun pa'i rdul min par bar mi srid do //
NK129(to)001:2733: mdo sde pa'i 'byar yang ma 'byar bar yang med pa mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:2734: ma 'byar na bar yong ba yin mod /
NK129(to)001:2735: bar med na 'byar ba yin mod /
NK129(to)001:2736: de ltar gzung ba'i yul yang dag tu ma grub tsa na /
NK129(to)001:2737: de la ltos pa'i 'dzin pa yang mi 'grub ste /
NK129(to)001:2738: gzung 'dzin ltos chos yin pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2739: gzhan yang 'dzin pa'i shes pa skad cing ma dus
NK129(to)001:2740: kyi cha dang bral ba yang mi 'thad de skad
NK129(to)001:2741: cig snga ma de bar ma dang phrad pa'i tshe
NK129(to)001:2742: / phyi ma dang phrad dam ma phrad /
NK129(to)001:2743: phrad na skad cig skad cig ma snga ma de bar ma la thim par thal /
NK129(to)001:2744: bar ma la ma thim na skad cig ma snga
NK129(to)001:2745: phyi gnyis bar ma chod nas phrad du mi stub
NK129(to)001:2746: la / thim par 'dod na shes pa thams cad skad cig ma gcig tu thal /
NK129(to)001:2747: bar ma la thim pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2748: de yang 'dod na rgyun gyi shes pa rags pa 'di gtan med du thal lo //
NK129(to)001:2749: yang skad cig ma snga ma de bar ma dang phrad pa'i tshe phyi ma dang ma phrad de /
NK129(to)001:2750: bar du chod de zer na skad cig ma snga ma de chos can /
NK129(to)001:2751: dus kyi shas dang bcas par thal /
NK129(to)001:2752: bar ma dang phrad pa'i cha dang /
NK129(to)001:2753: phyi ma dang phrad pa'i cha gnyis byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:2754: de 'dod na skad cig ma dus kyi cha dang bral ba'i dam bca' nyams so //
NK129(to)001:2755: nyan thos kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK129(to)001:2758: rab nyi tshe ba'i stong ba sgom mo //
NK129(to)001:2760: sbyangs pa'i yon tan bcu gnyis la gnas nas rang don gtso bor spyod cing /
NK129(to)001:2761: gzhan don zhar la byed do //
NK129(to)001:2762: 'bras bu ni 'phags pa dgra bcom pa thob pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2763: rang sangs rgyas la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:2769: gzung ba rang bzhin med par shes pa'i sgo nas rten 'brel sgom pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2770: de yang mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK129(to)001:2771: gzung ba'i cha ni spangs phyir dang /
NK129(to)001:2772: 'dzin pa ma spangs phyir dang ni /
NK129(to)001:2773: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam /
NK129(to)001:2776: rang gi shes rab zab mos /
NK129(to)001:2777: rang gi byang chub rtogs pa ste /
NK129(to)001:2779: dge bshes mi slob rang gi rig pas rtogs /
NK129(to)001:2782: dbang po rtul po ne tso ltar khyus lding ba dang /
NK129(to)001:2783: dbang po rnon po bse ru ltar gcig pur gnas su //
NK129(to)001:2784: bsdu na rang sangs rgyas bya ba gcig tu gnas so //
NK129(to)001:2791: phyi bzung ba'i yul ni phyogs cha drug dang /
NK129(to)001:2792: gcig dang du bral gyis gnod pas rang bzhin med la /
NK129(to)001:2794: gcig dang du ma la sogs pas mi gnod pas /
NK129(to)001:2795: skad cig ma don dam du 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:2797: phyi bzung ba'i yul la phyogs cha drug gis gnod pa bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:2799: skad cig ma dus kyi chas bshig pas ci ste mi gnod /
NK129(to)001:2800: gnod lugs kyang nyan thos kyi skabs su bkag pa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2801: gzhan yang khyod 'dzin pa'i sems skad cig ma don dam du 'dod pa de /
NK129(to)001:2804: yod nas 'dzin na bzung yul ma grub pa'i dam bca' bud /
NK129(to)001:2806: yang shes pa nang gi cha la bzung 'dzin du 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:2808: 'o na shes pa nang gi cha des dus mnyam du 'dzin nam /
NK129(to)001:2811: shes rgyud cha gnyis yod par thal /
NK129(to)001:2813: gzung ba yod tsa na 'dzin pa ma skyes pas /
NK129(to)001:2816: rten 'brel bcu gnyis lugs las zlog pa'i sgo nas
NK129(to)001:2817: ma rig pa'i gnyen por rig pa'i ye shes phra
NK129(to)001:2818: mo bsgom pa'o // spyod pa yang /
NK129(to)001:2819: sangs rgyas mi bzhugs pa'i zhing khams su rdzu 'phrul gyis sems can gyi don byed pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2821: yid bzhin bde ba mchog gis thos pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2822: theg pa chen po la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:2823: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2824: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2825: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:2826: theg pa chen po sems tsam dang /
NK129(to)001:2830: chos thams cad sems tsam du smra ba'o //
NK129(to)001:2832: phyi rol gyi don 'di mi bden te /
NK129(to)001:2833: rang gi sems kyi snang ba tsam du 'dod pas na /
NK129(to)001:2837: khams gsum po 'di dag ni sems tsam mo //
NK129(to)001:2843: sems tsam zhes pa gcig tu 'dus so //
NK129(to)001:2849: dang po lta ba ni bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:2850: nyan thos bas brtags pa'i bzung 'dzin don dam par yod pa bkag nas /
NK129(to)001:2851: chos thams cad sems tsam yin la /
NK129(to)001:2852: sems ni rang rig rang gsal myong ba gnyis med
NK129(to)001:2853: kyi shes pa mar me rlung gis ma skyod pa
NK129(to)001:2854: lta bu gcig don dam par 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:2855: 'o na phyi rol gyi snang ba 'di ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2856: 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas ma rig pa
NK129(to)001:2857: mthu brtas pa las byung ba'i bag chags kyis snang
NK129(to)001:2858: ba 'dod do // rang rig don dam du 'grub par cis shes zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2859: rang rig tsam zhig yod par myong bas shes la
NK129(to)001:2860: de la gzung 'dzin gyis stong par 'thad pa rjes
NK129(to)001:2862: nyan thos kyi gzung 'dzin don dam du 'dod pa bkag pa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2863: de la rig pas mi gnod pas na bden pa yod pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:2864: de la mtshan nyid gsum gyi 'jog lugs ni /
NK129(to)001:2865: phyi rol gyi yul du rgyu rkyen rten 'brel gyis bskyed pa ni gzhan dbang /
NK129(to)001:2866: de la gzung 'dzin med pa la yod par sgro btags pa ni kun brtags /
NK129(to)001:2867: de la yang dag par na gzung 'dzin gyis stong par shes na yongs grub bo //
NK129(to)001:2871: rnam bden pa ni phyi rol gyi don 'di bden
NK129(to)001:2872: par grub pa med zhes pa'i rnam pa tsam yin
NK129(to)001:2873: te / shes pa'i rnam pa tsam du bden par 'dod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2875: phyi rol gyi don 'di bden par ma grub ste shes pa'i rnam pa tsam yin la /
NK129(to)001:2876: shes pa'i rnam pa tsam du yang mi bden te brdzun pa dngos med du 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:2877: rnam bden pa la yang gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:2878: slob dpon chos kyi zla ba'i bzhed kyi shes pa yang gcig la /
NK129(to)001:2879: rnam pa yang gcig tu 'dod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:2880: de yang rnam pa thams cad gsal ba'i ngo bor gcig /
NK129(to)001:2881: shes pa thams cad rang rig gi ngo bo gcig zer ro //
NK129(to)001:2882: de dgag pa ni rnam pa thams cad gcig pa yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:2883: du mar snang zhing phyogs cha drug la sogs par dbye ba yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:2885: du mar snang yang ngo bo gcig pa yin zer na 'o na mu stegs pa na re /
NK129(to)001:2886: yan lag can gyi rdzas bya ba dngos po gcig
NK129(to)001:2887: gis thams cad la khyab pa gcig yod zer ba
NK129(to)001:2888: de cis 'gegs / mi 'gegs na sems tsam ma
NK129(to)001:2889: yin te phyi rol gyi don khas blangs par thal
NK129(to)001:2890: de cis 'gegs / / kho na re bum pa lta bu'i rdzas gcig la /
NK129(to)001:2891: cha shas du ma dang bcas nas 'bug pas /
NK129(to)001:2892: yan lag can gyi rdzas mi grub bo zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2893: 'dir yang snang la cha shas du ma dang bcas pa gcig mi 'grub bo //
NK129(to)001:2894: du mar snang yang gcig tu bden zer na /
NK129(to)001:2895: bum pa la cha shas du mar snang yang /
NK129(to)001:2896: yan lag can gyi rdzas gcig tu bden te khyad med do /
NK129(to)001:2897: shes pa rang rig gcig tu mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:2898: 'das ma 'ongs la sogs pa'i dus kyi dbye ba yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:2899: dus kyi dbye ba yod kyang shes pa'i ngo bo gcig go zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2900: 'o na mu stegs pa'i bdag rtag pa mi 'gyur ba cis 'gegs /
NK129(to)001:2901: rim gyis dang gcig char gyi don byed nus pas stong pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2902: bdag rtag pa mi 'grub zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2903: 'dir yang 'das ma 'ongs la sogs pa'i dus kyi dbye ba yod pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2906: 'das ma 'ongs la sogs pa shes pa'i gnas skabs tsam las rtag pa yin gyis /
NK129(to)001:2907: de dag kyang shes pa'i ngo bor gcig go zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2909: cig char bas don byed pas rtag pa'i gnas skabs 'gyur ba tsam la brtags pa yin /
NK129(to)001:2910: rtag pa'i ngo bo la 'gyur ba med de /
NK129(to)001:2912: yang slob dpon sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyis bzhed pas /
NK129(to)001:2913: shes pa yang du ma la /
NK129(to)001:2914: snang ba yang du mar bzhed de /
NK129(to)001:2915: yul gcig nye bar gyur pa na /
NK129(to)001:2916: der 'dzin pa'i shes pa yang gcig skye /
NK129(to)001:2917: yul gnyis nyer bas gyur pa na /
NK129(to)001:2918: der 'dzin pa'i shes pa gnyis skye bar 'dod pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:2920: yul dang shes pa gnyis ka du mar bden na /
NK129(to)001:2921: du ma'i khyab byed gcig bden par grub bam ma grub /
NK129(to)001:2922: gcig bden par grub ba du mar bden pa yang 'gal /
NK129(to)001:2923: gcig bden par ma grub na khyab byed gcig pas /
NK129(to)001:2924: khyab bya du mar yang mi 'grub bo //
NK129(to)001:2925: yang yul dang shes pa gnyis ka du ma'i bdag nyid du bden na /
NK129(to)001:2926: rang snang 'di gtan med du thal /
NK129(to)001:2927: rang snang med pa 'dod pa yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2928: 'o na rdul phra rab la phyogs chas dbye mi dgos par thal lo //
NK129(to)001:2929: yang slob dpon shes rab 'byung gnas sbas pa'i bzhed pas /
NK129(to)001:2930: rnam pa du ma shes pa gcig gi ngo bor gnas par bzhed do //
NK129(to)001:2931: rnam pa ni dkar dmar sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK129(to)001:2932: shes pa gcig gi bdag nyid du bden pa yin zer ro //
NK129(to)001:2934: tshor ba bde sdug gnyis kyang rdzas gcig yin bya yis /
NK129(to)001:2936: rdzas gcig pa 'dod pa yin na /
NK129(to)001:2937: tshor ba dbye ba med par thal /
NK129(to)001:2939: bde sdug rdzas gcig tu mi gtub te myong ba dang 'gal zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2940: khyod kyi rnam pa du ma shes pa gcig gi ngo bor bden na /
NK129(to)001:2941: shes pa du mar 'char ba dang 'gal /
NK129(to)001:2942: du mar snang ba tsam yin /
NK129(to)001:2943: ngo bo la du ma med zer na /
NK129(to)001:2944: tshor ba yang bde sdug du snang ba tsam yin /
NK129(to)001:2945: ngo bo la bde sdug med do //
NK129(to)001:2946: bde sdug med pa 'dod thog zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2947: mtho ris dang ngan 'gro khyad med par thal lo //
NK129(to)001:2948: bde sdug med pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:2949: yang rnam bden pa la spyi skyon 'di yang yod de /
NK129(to)001:2950: khyed rnams bden pa ltar na /
NK129(to)001:2951: shes pa'i rnam pa thams cad bden par 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:2954: rags pa snang ba bden kyang rags par grub pa mi bden no zhe na /
NK129(to)001:2955: 'o na snang ba las ma gtogs pa'i grub pa gcig logs na yod par thal /
NK129(to)001:2956: de 'dod na shes pa la yul bden rdzun gnyis yod par thal lo //
NK129(to)001:2958: shes pa ni gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i rang rig du bden la /
NK129(to)001:2959: phyi rol gyi don ni gcig dang du ma la sogs pas gnod pas mi bden te /
NK129(to)001:2960: rdzun pa dngos med yin zer ro //
NK129(to)001:2961: 'o na phyi rol gyi don med na /
NK129(to)001:2962: da lta rags par snang ba 'di ji ltar yin zer na /
NK129(to)001:2963: ma rig pa 'khrul pa'i rgyu las grub pa /
NK129(to)001:2964: shes pa yod pa'i rnam pa gsal ba'i 'grog la /
NK129(to)001:2965: med pa'i rnam pa yang gsal ba yin te /
NK129(to)001:2966: bzhin dang me long lta bu yin zer ro //
NK129(to)001:2967: 'o na 'khrul pa zad pa'i sangs rgyas lta bu la gsal lam mi gsal byas pas /
NK129(to)001:2968: rnam rdzun dri bcas pa na re /
NK129(to)001:2969: sangs rgyas kyi sa na yang gsal lo zer ro //
NK129(to)001:2970: de ltar na 'khrul snang gi rgyu ma rig pa spangs sam ma spangs /
NK129(to)001:2971: ma spangs na sangs rgyas ma yin par thal /
NK129(to)001:2972: spangs na 'khrul pa 'di mi snang bar rigs so //
NK129(to)001:2973: 'o na sangs rgyas 'khrul par mi 'gyur ram byas pas /
NK129(to)001:2974: rnam pa gsal kyang mi bden par shes pas 'khrul bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)001:2976: de ltar ma rig pa spangs kyang 'bras bu 'khrul snang ma spangs par 'gyur ro /
NK129(to)001:2977: rnam brdzun dri med pa na re /
NK129(to)001:2978: yul rang snang 'di shes pa'i 'khrul pa'i cha yin pas /
NK129(to)001:2979: sangs rgyas la 'khrul pa'i rgyun chad pas /
NK129(to)001:2980: rnam pa gsal ba med do zer ro //
NK129(to)001:2981: de ltar na shes bya ji snyed pa med par thal /
NK129(to)001:2982: 'khrul pa mi gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:2983: de rnams spyir dgag pa ni gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i rang rig don dam du grub la /
NK129(to)001:2984: phyi rol gyi don mi bden par gang gis shes /
NK129(to)001:2986: rang rig tsam gcig yod par myong bas grub la /
NK129(to)001:2987: de la gzung 'dzin gyis stong par grub pa rjes dpag gis grub ste /
NK129(to)001:2988: nyan thos bkag pa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:2989: phyi rol gyi don gzugs can yin pa dang /
NK129(to)001:2990: gcig du bral la sogs pas gnod pas mi bden no zer /
NK129(to)001:2991: de ltar rang rig tsam zhig myong bas grub pas bden no //
NK129(to)001:2992: phyi rol kyang rnam pa gsal ba tsam gcig grub pa ci mi bden /
NK129(to)001:2993: phyi rol gyi don gzugs can yin pas gcig dang
NK129(to)001:2994: du ma la sogs pa'i gnod pas mi bden zer
NK129(to)001:2995: na / de ltar na shes pa yang myong ba tsam gcig yod pa de /
NK129(to)001:2998: gcig tu myong na gcig po de cha shas dang bcas par myong ngam /
NK129(to)001:2999: cha shas dang bral bar myong /
NK129(to)001:3000: cha shas dang bcas pa myong na /
NK129(to)001:3001: cha shas dang bcas pa'i phyir gcig ma yin te du mar thal /
NK129(to)001:3002: cha shas dang bral ba gcig tu myong na /
NK129(to)001:3003: bde sdug cha shas kyi dbye ba med par thal /
NK129(to)001:3004: yang na bde sdug myong ba ma yin par thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3006: du ma de gcig la ltos sam ma ltos /
NK129(to)001:3008: du ma mi 'grub de gcig tu thal /
NK129(to)001:3009: ma ltos na khyab byed gcig ma 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:3010: khyab bya du ma yang mi 'grub par thal /
NK129(to)001:3011: yang 'dzin bya bden pa dang gzung ba dngos med 'brel ba yod dam med /
NK129(to)001:3012: med na yul de shes pa la snang ngam mi snang /
NK129(to)001:3013: mi snang na mngon sum gyis gsal /
NK129(to)001:3015: mig gi yul du gzugs snang la /
NK129(to)001:3016: sgra mi snang ba ci'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:3017: de bdag po'i rkyen kyis byed pa'i lag rjes so so ba yin no zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3019: byed pa'i lag rjes so sor yong ba ci'i phyir ste rgyu mtshan med do //
NK129(to)001:3020: yang 'brel ba yod do zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3023: bdag gcig pa yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3025: ngo bo dbyer med pa'i tshul gyis chos gzhan mi 'dor ba yin la /
NK129(to)001:3026: dngos po dang dngos med phan tshun spang 'gal yin pas bdag gcig tu mi gtub bo //
NK129(to)001:3027: de las byung bas 'brel lam zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3028: de las byung ba ni rgyu 'bras kyi tshul gyis chos gzhan mi 'dor ba yin la /
NK129(to)001:3029: dngos med ni rgyur yang mi rung la /
NK129(to)001:3031: sems tsam gyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK129(to)001:3032: rang rig rang gsal gyi ngang la mnyam par 'jog pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3034: pha rol tu phyin pa drug sems can gyi don du spyod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3036: bskal pa grangs med gsum na kun tu 'od kyi sa thob pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3037: theg pa chen po dbu ma la yang bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:3042: de rnams nges par bya ba la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:3046: gzhi dbu ma la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:3047: nges par 'byed pa'i gzhung lugs kyi dbye ba dang /
NK129(to)001:3048: de'i don bden pa gnyis gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3049: gtan la 'beb par byed pa'i don lnga ngos bzung ba dang /
NK129(to)001:3050: rjes dpag gi 'jug yul bstan pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3051: nges par 'byed pa'i gzhung lugs la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:3054: gzhug phyi mo'i yang phyi ma'o //
NK129(to)001:3055: de la gzhung phyi mo ni /
NK129(to)001:3056: slob dpon klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa'i rigs pa'i tshogs drug ste /
NK129(to)001:3057: dbu ma rtsa ba shes rab /
NK129(to)001:3063: slob dpon +aar+ya d+he ba'i dbu ma bzhi brgya pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3065: gzhung phyi mo'i phyi mo ni /
NK129(to)001:3067: mdo phran bcu gsum dang bcas pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3068: phyogs 'dzin pa'i dbu ma la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:3069: mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma dang /
NK129(to)001:3070: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma dang /
NK129(to)001:3071: dbu ma spyi gzhung gi zhal mchu pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3072: mdo sde spyod pa'i dbu ma ni /
NK129(to)001:3073: bden gnyis mkhan po ye shes snying po'i zhal nas
NK129(to)001:3074: zab mo don gyi mthar thug pa la yul yang
NK129(to)001:3076: kun rdzob tsam du sems las tha dad pa'i phyi rol gyi yul yang yod par 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:3077: 'dod lugs nyan thos mdo sde pa dang mthun no //
NK129(to)001:3078: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma ni /
NK129(to)001:3079: rgyan gyi mkhan po zhi 'tsho'i zhal nas /
NK129(to)001:3080: zab mo'i don gyi mthar thug pa la yul yang med la /
NK129(to)001:3082: kun rdzob tsam du snang ba rang rig gi sems kyis snang bar 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:3084: dbu ma spyi gzhung gi zhal mchu ba ni /
NK129(to)001:3085: snang ba mkhan po ka ma la sh+ai li'i zhal nas /
NK129(to)001:3086: don dam mthar thug pa la yul kyang med la /
NK129(to)001:3088: spros pa thams cad bral bas chog la /
NK129(to)001:3089: kun rdzob tu phyi rol gyi don yod par 'dod pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3090: sems su 'dod pa gnyis gang ltar byas kyang chog /
NK129(to)001:3091: phyi rol gyi don yod na yang yod /
NK129(to)001:3092: med na yang med zer ro //
NK129(to)001:3093: de rnams ni rab tu dbye ba'i gzhung lugs so //
NK129(to)001:3094: de'i bden pa gnyis gtan la dbab pa la dgu ste /
NK129(to)001:3095: bden pa gnyis kyi dbye ba'i gzhi gcig dang /
NK129(to)001:3097: dbye ba'i rgyu mtshan gsum dang /
NK129(to)001:3099: go rim nges pa lnga dang /
NK129(to)001:3100: rgyas par dbye ba drug dang /
NK129(to)001:3101: so so'i mtshan nyid bdun dang /
NK129(to)001:3103: gcig dang tha dad kyis brtag pa dang dagu'o //
NK129(to)001:3104: dang po dbye ba'i gzhi ni /
NK129(to)001:3106: mkhas pa dang mi mkhas pa'i blo yul las phye zer /
NK129(to)001:3108: shes bya tsam po las phye zer /
NK129(to)001:3110: shes pa dang shes bya 'tshogs pa las phye zer /
NK129(to)001:3111: gnyis pa dbye ba'i don ni /
NK129(to)001:3112: don dam pa'i bden pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3114: gsum pa dbye ba'i rgyu mtshan ni snang ba'i shes ngo la ltos nas kun rdzob /
NK129(to)001:3115: stong pa'i shes ngo la ltos nas don dam mo //
NK129(to)001:3116: bzhi ba grangs nges pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3117: spyir shes bya la 'khrul ma 'khrul gnyis su nges
NK129(to)001:3118: pas 'khrul pa'i blo yul la ltos nas kun rdzob
NK129(to)001:3119: / ma 'khrul pa'i blo yul ltos nas don dam mo //
NK129(to)001:3120: lnga pa go rim nges pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3121: kun rdzob so so skye bo'i blo yul ltos nas dang po ston /
NK129(to)001:3122: don dam ni 'phags pa'i blo yul la ltos nas tha mar ston no //
NK129(to)001:3123: drug pa rgyas par dbye na bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:3124: kun rdzob dang don dam gnyis la gnyis gnyis ste bzhi'o //
NK129(to)001:3125: dang po kun rdzob la yang dag pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK129(to)001:3126: log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis so //
NK129(to)001:3128: rnam grangs kyi don dam pa'i bden pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3129: rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam pa'i bden pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3130: bdun pa so so'i mtshan nyid kyang kun rdzob spyi'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK129(to)001:3131: blo'i yul du gyur pa'i chos can mtshan ma can no //
NK129(to)001:3132: log pa'i kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK129(to)001:3133: snang ba la snang ba bzhin du don byed mi nus pa de /
NK129(to)001:3134: srab mo ltar snang ba lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:3135: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK129(to)001:3136: snang ba la snang ba bzhin du don byed nus pa ste /
NK129(to)001:3137: me la mer snang ba bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:3138: yang na chos bzhi ldan te /
NK129(to)001:3144: don dam gyi bden pa spyi'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK129(to)001:3146: rnam grangs kyi don dam pa'i bden pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3147: spros pa phyogs re dang bralaba'o //
NK129(to)001:3148: rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam pa'i bden pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3149: spros pa mtha' dag dang bral ba'o //
NK129(to)001:3152: sam bri ta zhes bya ste /
NK129(to)001:3153: yang dag la sgrib pa'am ngan pa'i sgrib pa mi bslu ba'o //
NK129(to)001:3155: pa ra mar+tha zhes bya ste /
NK129(to)001:3157: dam pa yang min pas mi bslu ba'o //
NK129(to)001:3158: gcig dang tha dad kyi brtag pa la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3159: gcig pa la bskal pa'i skyon bzhi /
NK129(to)001:3160: tha dad pa la bskal pa'i skyon bzhi'o //
NK129(to)001:3161: gcig pa la bskal pa skyon bzhi ni /
NK129(to)001:3162: bden pa gnyis gcig tu 'dod na /
NK129(to)001:3163: kun rdzob so so skye bo'i mngon sum du 'gyur ba bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:3164: don dam yang so so'i skye bos mngon sum du 'gyur bar thal /
NK129(to)001:3165: de 'dod na grol bar thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3166: gnyis pa yang kun rdzob blo yul du byas pas zag pa 'phel ba bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:3167: don dam yang blo yul du byas pas kyang zag pa 'phel bar thal bas gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3168: gsum pa don dam nyams su blangs pas grol ba
NK129(to)001:3169: bzhin du kun rdzob nyams su blangs pas kyang grol
NK129(to)001:3171: bzhi pa kun rdzob spros pa du ma dang bcas pa bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:3172: don dam kyang spros pa du ma dang bcas pas thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3174: tha dad na yang skyon bzhi las /
NK129(to)001:3175: dang po don dam rtogs kyang kun rdzob kyi 'khrul snang mi spongs par thal /
NK129(to)001:3177: gnyis pa don dam de kun rdzob kyi chos nyid ma yin par thal /
NK129(to)001:3179: gsum pa gang zag gcig gi rgyud la kun nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3180: rnam par byang ba gnyis ka 'tshogs par thal /
NK129(to)001:3182: bzhi pa kun rdzob dngos por snang ba bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:3183: don dam kyang dngos por snang bar thal /
NK129(to)001:3184: dngos po'i ldog phyogs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3185: des 'dir ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad pa'am /
NK129(to)001:3186: de nyid dang gzhan du brjod du med par 'dod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3187: gsum pa de gtan la 'bebs par byed pa'i don lnga ngos bzung ba ni /
NK129(to)001:3189: bdag dang gzhan du brjod du med par 'dod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3190: gsum pa de gtan la 'bebs par byed pa'i don lnga ngos bzung ba ni /
NK129(to)001:3192: bdag dang gzhan smra'i dngos 'di dag /
NK129(to)001:3193: yang dag par ni gcig pa'am /
NK129(to)001:3194: du ma'i rang bzhin bral ba'i phyir //
NK129(to)001:3195: rang bzhin med de gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK129(to)001:3201: khyab pa gtan la 'bebs pa'i dape'o //
NK129(to)001:3202: dang po rtsod gzhi chos can la drug ste /
NK129(to)001:3204: chos can kyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK129(to)001:3207: nges par byed pa'i tshad ma dang /
NK129(to)001:3208: de la rtsod pa'i skyon spang ba dang drug go /
NK129(to)001:3209: dang po chos can du 'gro tshod ni /
NK129(to)001:3210: gzhan sel snang brtags kyi sgra don cha ma phye ba'o /
NK129(to)001:3211: chos can gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK129(to)001:3212: dgag sgrub gang byed kyang de nyid la gnod pa
NK129(to)001:3213: ma zhugs shing shes 'dod dang ldan pa gcig yin
NK129(to)001:3214: zer / yang na rten rtsod byed kyi gzhir gyur pa gcig yin no //
NK129(to)001:3217: snang ba nyams su myong ba chos can du bzhag nas rang bzhin med par bsgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3219: rnam rtog yul la bden par zhen pa de chos can du bzhag nas /
NK129(to)001:3220: rang bzhin med par sgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3221: snang brtag cha ma phye ba'i chos ni /
NK129(to)001:3222: snang ba nyams su myong ba dang /
NK129(to)001:3223: brtag pa gnyis chos can du bzhag nas /
NK129(to)001:3224: rang bzhin med par sgrub ba'o //
NK129(to)001:3226: chos nyid stong pa nyid la sogs pa grags tshad chos can du bzhag nas /
NK129(to)001:3227: rang bzhin med par sgrub pa'o /
NK129(to)001:3228: chos can du bzhag pa'i dus ni /
NK129(to)001:3230: phyi rgol rtsod pa'i dus so //
NK129(to)001:3231: nges par 'byed pa'i tshad ma ni /
NK129(to)001:3232: snang ba chos can ni dbang po'i phyugs las nges /
NK129(to)001:3234: rang rig gi shugs las nges so //
NK129(to)001:3235: de la rtsod pa spang pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3236: 'o na chos can dang gzhan gyi sde pas brtags pa'i log rtog yin no //
NK129(to)001:3237: de chos can du 'jog pa'i tshe /
NK129(to)001:3238: snang ba tsam chos can du 'jog gam /
NK129(to)001:3239: snang ba'i khyad par 'ga' zhig chos can du 'jog /
NK129(to)001:3240: dang po ltar na de tsam blo la snang bar mi nus la /
NK129(to)001:3241: gnyis pa ltar na spros pa mtha' dag gcod pa'i rig par mi 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)001:3244: snang ba'i khyad par 'ga' zhig chos can du bzhag pas /
NK129(to)001:3245: kun gyi spros pa chod de /
NK129(to)001:3246: 'dam bu gcig khog stong na kun kyang khog stong bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:3248: gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid shes na chos thams cad kyi mdo dang rgyas par shes par 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)001:3250: gnyis pa rnam gcad dgag bya la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3252: dang po dgag bya spyi'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK129(to)001:3255: rigs pas dpyad nas rang bzhin gyi khyad par 'ga'
NK129(to)001:3256: zhig dang ldan par 'dod pa gang rnyed pa de
NK129(to)001:3258: dgag bya la bye brag tu phye na gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3264: phyi rol gyi don dngos por 'dod pa 'gogs la /
NK129(to)001:3265: ma yin pa dgag pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3266: sems can rang rig don dam du 'dod pa 'gogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3267: yongs spyod bsgrub bya la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3271: snang ba'i dngos por bkag nas /
NK129(to)001:3272: shul du sgyu ma tsam gcig sgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3273: rab tu mi gnas pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3274: snang ba'i dngos por 'dod pa bkag nas sgyu ma
NK129(to)001:3275: tsam du yang mi 'dod de rab tu mi gnas
NK129(to)001:3276: pa'o // bzhi pa 'thad pa gtan tshigs la lnga ste /
NK129(to)001:3277: rgyu 'gogs pa rdo rje gzegs ma'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK129(to)001:3278: 'bras bu 'gogs pa yod med skye 'gogs kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK129(to)001:3279: rgyu 'bras bu gnyis ka 'gogs pa mu bzhi skye 'gogs kyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK129(to)001:3280: rang gi ngo bo 'gogs pa gcig dang du bral
NK129(to)001:3281: gyi gtan tshigs dang 'gal zla bsgrubs nas 'brel zla
NK129(to)001:3282: 'gogs pa rten 'brel gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK129(to)001:3283: dang po rgyu 'gogs pa rdo rje gzegs ma'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK129(to)001:3285: yang dag par na rgyu 'bras med de //
NK129(to)001:3286: mu bzhi'i skye ba dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:3289: rang las ma yin gzhan las min //
NK129(to)001:3290: gnyis ka las min rgyu med min //
NK129(to)001:3291: dngos po gang dang gang dag la //
NK129(to)001:3292: skye ba nam yang yod ma yin //
NK129(to)001:3294: gtan tshigs ma sgrub zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3295: 'o na rgyu 'bras yang dag tu yod dam /
NK129(to)001:3300: rang las skye na rang grub pa las skye'am /
NK129(to)001:3302: ma grub pa las skye na /
NK129(to)001:3303: rgyu med las skye ba mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3304: rgyu med rkyen la mi ltos phyir /
NK129(to)001:3305: rtag tu yod pa'am med par thal /
NK129(to)001:3307: rang grub pa las skye na /
NK129(to)001:3308: grub pa las kyang skye dgos pa'i phyir thug pa med par thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3316: rtag pa mi 'gyur ba yin la /
NK129(to)001:3317: rim gyis 'gyur ba can yin pas /
NK129(to)001:3319: gcig char skye na rgyu'i dus nyid na 'bras bu smin bar thal /
NK129(to)001:3320: gcig char kha la rgyu 'bras gcig dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3321: 'dod na mngon sum gyis gsal lo /
NK129(to)001:3322: gzhan mi rtag pa las skye na /
NK129(to)001:3326: 'das pa las skye ba mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3327: rgyu 'bras spyad zin pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3328: ma 'ongs pa las skye ba mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3329: yul na med pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3333: dus mnyam la phan 'dogs byed med pas skye mi gtub bo //
NK129(to)001:3334: dus tha dad las skye na /
NK129(to)001:3335: rgyu 'bras la phrad pa yod dam med /
NK129(to)001:3336: phrad na dus mnyam du 'phrad dam /
NK129(to)001:3338: dus mnyam du phrad na rgyu 'bras kyi dam bca' bud /
NK129(to)001:3339: dus tha dad du phrad na /
NK129(to)001:3341: phan gdags bya dang 'dog byed med pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3343: rang gzhan las skye ba med par gnyis ka las ga nas skye /
NK129(to)001:3344: yang rgyu med las skye zer na /
NK129(to)001:3345: rgyu med rkyen la mi ltos phyir /
NK129(to)001:3346: rtag tu yod pa'ang med par thal te /
NK129(to)001:3347: dus glo bur du byung bas rgyu 'bras mi stub bo //
NK129(to)001:3348: gnyis pa 'bras bu 'gogs par byed pa yod med skye 'gogs kyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK129(to)001:3349: sems tsam rang rig don dam du 'dod pa de chos can /
NK129(to)001:3350: yang dag pa rang bzhin med de /
NK129(to)001:3351: 'bras bu yod med las ma skyes pa'i phyir nam mkha' bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:3353: yod pa skye ba rigs min te //
NK129(to)001:3354: med pa'ang nam mkha'i me tog bzhin //
NK129(to)001:3355: de ltar yod dang med pa la //
NK129(to)001:3356: mkhas pas gnas par mi bya'o //
NK129(to)001:3358: gtan tshigs ma grub zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3359: 'o na 'bras bu gcig skye ba de yod pa las skye'am med pa las skye /
NK129(to)001:3360: yod pa las skye na yod na ci skye dgos /
NK129(to)001:3362: ma legs pa legs par byed pa'am /
NK129(to)001:3363: chung ba che bar byed pa la sogs pa'i dgos pa yod do zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3364: 'o na yod pa las skye ba ma yin te /
NK129(to)001:3365: legs pa dang che ba med pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3367: med pa 'bras bu'i chos su mi rigs pas skye ba mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3368: gal te med pa las skye na /
NK129(to)001:3369: ri bong las ra skye bar thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3370: yang med pa las skye na /
NK129(to)001:3371: phyis skyes ba'i tshe sngar gyi med pa de log gam ma log /
NK129(to)001:3372: ma log na phyis kyang med par thal /
NK129(to)001:3373: log na sngar kyang yod par thal /
NK129(to)001:3374: sngar med pa las log pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3375: des na rang rig don dam du 'dod pa mi 'thad do //
NK129(to)001:3376: gsum pa rgyu 'bras gnyis ka 'gogs pa mu bzhi'i skye 'gogs gi gtan tshigs ni /
NK129(to)001:3377: sems tsam rang rig don dam du 'dod pa de chos can /
NK129(to)001:3378: yang dag par na rang bzhin med de /
NK129(to)001:3379: gcig dang du ma las 'bras bu ma skyes pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3381: du ma'i ngo bo gcig mi byed /
NK129(to)001:3382: gcig gis du ma'i dngos mi byed //
NK129(to)001:3384: gtan tshigs ma grub zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3385: 'o na rgyu du ma las 'bras bu gcig skye'am /
NK129(to)001:3386: rgyu gcig las 'bras bu ma skye 'am /
NK129(to)001:3387: rgyu du ma las 'bras bu du ma skye'am /
NK129(to)001:3389: rgyu du ma las 'bras bu gcig skye zer ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3390: rgyu sa bon mang po las 'bras bu gcig skye bar thal /
NK129(to)001:3391: 'dod na mngon sum gyi gsal lo //
NK129(to)001:3392: rgyu gcig las 'bras bu du ma skye zer ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3393: rgyu nas kyi sa bon gcig po las /
NK129(to)001:3394: 'bras bu gro dang sran ma la sogs pa du ma skye bar thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3395: rgyu du ma las 'bras bu du ma skyee ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3396: rgyur shing spyin la sogs pa'i grags dang ma nyams
NK129(to)001:3397: par 'bras bu gzhu yang de tsam 'byung bar thal
NK129(to)001:3398: lo // rgyu gcig la 'bras bu gcig skyes zer ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3399: rgyu nas 'bru gcig btab pas 'bras bu yang nas 'bru gcig rang smin bar thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3400: bzhi pa rang gi ngo bo 'gogs pa gcig dang du bral gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK129(to)001:3401: snang ba phyi nang gi dngos po 'di chos can /
NK129(to)001:3402: yang dag par na rang bzhin med de /
NK129(to)001:3403: gcig dang du ma bral ba'i phyir gzugs can bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:3404: de yang dbu ma'i rgyan las /
NK129(to)001:3405: bdag dang gzhan smra'i dngos 'di dag /
NK129(to)001:3406: yang dag par ni gcig pa dang //
NK129(to)001:3407: du ma'i rang bzhin bral ba'i phyir //
NK129(to)001:3408: rang bzhin med de gzugs can bzhin //
NK129(to)001:3410: gtan tshigs ma grub zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3411: 'o na snang ba 'di gcig tu yod dam du mar yod /
NK129(to)001:3412: gcig tu yod na cha shas dang bcas pa gcig tu yod dam /
NK129(to)001:3413: cha shas dang bral ba'i gcig tu yod /
NK129(to)001:3414: cha shas dang bcas na gcig mi stub ste du mar thal /
NK129(to)001:3415: cha shas dang bral bar yod na mi grub ste /
NK129(to)001:3416: phyogs cha drug dang bcas pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3417: zhib par nyan thos kyi skabs su bshad do //
NK129(to)001:3419: du ma de gcig la ltos sam mi ltos /
NK129(to)001:3420: mi ltos na khyab byed gcig ma grub la /
NK129(to)001:3421: khyab byed du ma yang mi 'grub par thal /
NK129(to)001:3422: ltos na gcig po de cha shas dang bcas sam ma bcas kyis brtag pa gong dang mtshungs so //
NK129(to)001:3423: lnga pa 'gal zla bsgrubs nas 'brel zla 'gogs pa rten 'brel gyi gtan tshigs ni /
NK129(to)001:3424: mig gi rnam par shes pa la sogs pas snang ba nyams su myong ba 'di chos can /
NK129(to)001:3426: yang dag pa'i rgyu 'bras min par dam bca'/
NK129(to)001:3428: re zhig pa'i rgyu yin te /
NK129(to)001:3429: rgyu rkyen sna tshogs bar rag lus pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3430: gtan tshigs ma grub bo zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3431: 'o na rgyu 'bras yang dag tu yod dam /
NK129(to)001:3434: dngos po thams cad la gcig dang du bral gyis gnod pas rang bzhin med /
NK129(to)001:3435: rang bzhin med pa la yang dag tu 'dod pa mi stub bo //
NK129(to)001:3436: rgyu 'bras yang dag tu med na /
NK129(to)001:3438: yang dag tu bden kyang rten 'brel min na ci sto ste khyab pa ma grub ce na /
NK129(to)001:3439: snang ba yang dag tu ma grub la sna tshogs su 'char ba de rten 'brel yin te /
NK129(to)001:3440: sgyu ma'i snang ba bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:3443: rnam shes gsum la rten nas /
NK129(to)001:3445: rnam shes gsum re re ma tshang yang rnam shes mi skye bar mngon sum gyis gsal lo //
NK129(to)001:3446: des na khyab pa rang rgyud la yang grub /
NK129(to)001:3447: mthun grub la yang grub pa rten 'brel yin no //
NK129(to)001:3448: lnga pa khyab pa gtan la 'bebs pa'i dpe la yang gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3454: bsgrub bya sgrub byed 'brel ba ltar snang zhing ldog pa'am /
NK129(to)001:3455: rnal ma gang rung la rjes su 'gro ldog pa gcig yin te /
NK129(to)001:3456: gang du ba yod pa de na me yod de tshang mang bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:3457: gang du ba med pa de na me med de /
NK129(to)001:3460: khyab pa bye brag la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3461: gang zhig dngos po rgyu mtshan du byas te /
NK129(to)001:3462: khyab pa rtsod gzhi'i thog tu bsgrub pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3463: gcig dang du ma bral ba la rang gzhin med pas khyab pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:3464: gang zhig khyab pa rgyu mtshan du byas nas /
NK129(to)001:3465: khyab pa mthun dpe'i thog tu bsgrub pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3466: gang du ba yod pa na me yod de tshang mang bzhin zhes pa lta bu'o /
NK129(to)001:3468: rang bzhin grub pa'i mthun dpe ni /
NK129(to)001:3469: yang dag par na rang bzhin med pa'i dpe ni /
NK129(to)001:3470: gzugs can bzhin zhes pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:3471: gzhan gzhung 'gogs pa mi mthun pa'i dpe ni /
NK129(to)001:3473: gzugs can da phar la song ba yin zer ba de mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3475: nyan thos pa na re 'byung ba las g.yar zer ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3476: gzugs can ma yin pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3477: thogs pa dang bcas pa gnyis go sa gcig na mi gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3479: rang gi sems yin zer ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK129(to)001:3480: gzugs can de la dpyad bzod med pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3481: de bas na sgyu ma tsam yin te rang bzhin med pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3482: spyi don bzhi pa rjes dpag gi 'jug yul la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3485: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK129(to)001:3486: rang rgyud kyi lta ba la dogs pa'i skyon sel tsam gcig rang rgyud yin la /
