NK129(to)001:3487: gzhan gyi khas len 'gogs pa de thal 'gyur ro //
NK129(to)001:3491: de gnyis kyi khyad par yang /
NK129(to)001:3492: rnam dpyad kyi dus su dgag bya bkag nas /
NK129(to)001:3494: sgyu ma lta bur khas len pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3496: rnam dpyad la bden pa'i dngos po bkag nas /
NK129(to)001:3497: yongs dpyod la khas len gang yang med pa ni rab tu mi gnas pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3500: rang gi khas len gang yang med pa la /
NK129(to)001:3501: gzhan gyis yang dag tu khas len pa 'gogs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3503: gong du bstan pa'i rigs pa lnga pos 'gogs so //
NK129(to)001:3505: lam dbu ma ni ting nge 'dzin ste /
NK129(to)001:3506: mnyam bzhag tu chos thams cad stong pa nyid nam mkha'i dkyil lta bur bsgom pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3508: rjes thob kyi dus su sems can gyi don du
NK129(to)001:3509: pha rol du phyin pa drug sgyu ma tsam du
NK129(to)001:3510: spyod pa'o // 'bras bu dbu ma ni /
NK129(to)001:3511: de ltar ye shes kyi tshogs stong pa nyid mngon du gyur nas /
NK129(to)001:3512: rang don chos skur grol nas rjes thob la bsod nams kyi tshogs la brten nas /
NK129(to)001:3513: gzhan snang la gzugs sku gnyis la brten nas sems can gyi don byed pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3515: khyed dbu ma la dgag sgrub skyon du che 'am mi che /
NK129(to)001:3517: yang dag pa'i don la dgag sgrub yod dam med /
NK129(to)001:3519: 'di la bsal bya ci yang med //
NK129(to)001:3520: bzhag par bya ba cung zad med //
NK129(to)001:3521: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK129(to)001:3522: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK129(to)001:3523: zhes pa lta bu dang 'gal lo //
NK129(to)001:3524: med na gtan tshigs chen po lngas /
NK129(to)001:3525: dngos 'dzin 'gog gam mi 'gog /'gog na dgag sgrub
NK129(to)001:3526: can du 'dug pas yang dag pa ma yin par
NK129(to)001:3527: thal / mi 'gog na gtan tshigs chen po lnga don med du thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3528: dgag sgrub skyon du mi che na /
NK129(to)001:3529: theg chung gi lta ba dgag sgrub can yang skyon med du thal /
NK129(to)001:3530: 'dod na dgag sgrub tshad mar 'dzin pas ci smras
NK129(to)001:3531: kyang bden pas bslus te ci smras kyang gtan la
NK129(to)001:3532: phebs pa min / zhes gsungs dang 'gal lo //
NK129(to)001:3533: yang mtshan nyid pa spyi la 'gal ba /
NK129(to)001:3534: khyod sems can gyi rgyud la gnas pa'i nyon mongs pa 'di spong ngam lam du byed /
NK129(to)001:3535: spongs na nyon mongs dngos por yod pa spong ngam /
NK129(to)001:3537: dngos por yod nas spong na khyod la dngos 'dzin skyon du che 'am mi che /
NK129(to)001:3538: mi che na so so skye bo dngos por 'dzin pa yang skyon med du thal dang /
NK129(to)001:3539: gtan tshigs bzhi po yang dgos med du thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3541: khyod nyon mongs pa dngos por 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:3542: skyon can gyi lta bar thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3543: yang nyon mongs pa dngos med du 'dod na /
NK129(to)001:3544: dngos med spong ngam mi spong /
NK129(to)001:3545: mi spong na nyon mongs pa spang ba'i dam bca' s+w+aa h+aa /
NK129(to)001:3549: dngos med kyi 'gal ba dngos po yin pas /
NK129(to)001:3552: bdag gcig pa'i 'brel bas spong ngam /
NK129(to)001:3554: bdag gcig pa'i 'brel bas spong na /
NK129(to)001:3555: gser gyi ser po spong dgos par thal /
NK129(to)001:3556: de las byung bas spong na /
NK129(to)001:3557: du bas kyang mi spong bar thal /
NK129(to)001:3558: yang nyon mongs pa lam du byed na /
NK129(to)001:3559: rang rgyud pa lam du byed dam /
NK129(to)001:3560: gnyen po brten nas lam du byed /
NK129(to)001:3561: rang rgyud pa lam du byed na /
NK129(to)001:3563: grol na so so skye bo yang grol bar thal /
NK129(to)001:3564: mi grol na lam du byed pa don med du thal lo /
NK129(to)001:3565: gnyen pos nyon mongs pa spong ngom mi spong /
NK129(to)001:3566: mi spong na gnyen po brten pa don med du thal /
NK129(to)001:3567: spong na nyon mongs mi spong bar lam du byed pa'i dam bca' s+w+aa h+aa /
NK129(to)001:3568: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3569: phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud dang /
NK129(to)001:3570: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud do //
NK129(to)001:3571: phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:3574: gnyis ka'i rgyud u p+aa ya /
NK129(to)001:3582: don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral te /
NK129(to)001:3586: tha dad yang ma yin par 'dod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3587: kun rdzob du rigs gsum gyi dkyil 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK129(to)001:3588: mtho mtho thams cad spyan ras gzigs /
NK129(to)001:3590: rtsub rtsub thams cad phyag na rdo rje'i ngo bor sangs rgyas par 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:3592: mthong ba'i dngos po mtho 'jam rtsub //
NK129(to)001:3593: drug phyed rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK129(to)001:3594: mthong bas rnam par dag ces bya //
NK129(to)001:3597: kri ya don gyi lha drug gi sgo nas bdag dam tshig sems par bskyed de /
NK129(to)001:3598: stong pa nyid kyi lha dang /
NK129(to)001:3603: sku yongs su rdzogs pa'i lha dang drug gis bdag bskyed nas /
NK129(to)001:3604: ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs /
NK129(to)001:3605: mchod bstod bzlas pa byas nas rje khol gyi tshul du dngos grub zhu ba'o //
NK129(to)001:3607: gza' skar dus tshig la gtso bor byas nas /
NK129(to)001:3608: khrus dang gtsang sbra la gnas shing /
NK129(to)001:3609: dkar gsum mngar gsum la longs spyod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3611: mi tshe bdun gyi rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob par 'dod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3613: khyod kri ya ba don dam pa mtha' bzhi bral ba'i ting nge 'dzin la /
NK129(to)001:3614: kun rdzob tu rigs gsum lha'i dal du bsgom cir dgos mi dgos pas mi sgom na /
NK129(to)001:3616: yang don dam par dag kyang ma rtogs pas kun rdzob du bsgom dgos zer na /
NK129(to)001:3617: don des kun rdzob la khyab bam ma khyab /
NK129(to)001:3618: khyab na kun rdzob kyang dag par thal /
NK129(to)001:3619: dag kyang bsgom dgos na dag pa don med du thal /
NK129(to)001:3620: don des kun rdzob la ma khyab na /
NK129(to)001:3621: don dam de kun rdzob kyi chos nyid ma yin par thal /
NK129(to)001:3624: sbrang mas nam 'phang gcod du gshog rgyangs ye nas med //
NK129(to)001:3625: kri yas byang chub thob tu rtogs pa'i rlung la gnas //
NK129(to)001:3627: u p+aa ya la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:3633: don dam skye 'gag med pa'i 'od gsal bar 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:3634: ting nge 'dzin yang yo ga dang mthun te /
NK129(to)001:3635: mngon par byang chub pa lngas lha'i sku bskyed do //
NK129(to)001:3636: spyod pa kri ya dang mthun te /
NK129(to)001:3637: gza' dang dus tshigs bzang po la brten nas khrus dang gtsang sbra gtso bor byed do //
NK129(to)001:3638: 'bras bu yang mi tshe lnga na rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gi sa thob par 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:3640: khyed u pa ba'i lugs kyi lta spyod tha dad
NK129(to)001:3641: gnyis kyis 'bras bu gcig grub par mi 'thad de
NK129(to)001:3643: lta spyod ji ltar 'dzol zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3644: lta ba don dam skye 'gag med pa la /
NK129(to)001:3645: spyod pa dgag sgrub can du song bas 'dzol lo //
NK129(to)001:3646: lta spyod 'dzol yang 'bras bu byung na cis sto ste /
NK129(to)001:3647: khyab pa med do zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3648: gang mar dang sbyin bsres pa la nus pa med pa bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:3649: lta spyod 'dzol ba la 'bras bu mi 'byung ste /
NK129(to)001:3650: pra bo'i sa bon kun btab pa la /
NK129(to)001:3651: nas kyi 'bras bu'i ston mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:3652: de yang sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las /
NK129(to)001:3653: kha cig lta ba mnyam nas kyang //
NK129(to)001:3654: spyod pa dag dang yongs mi ldan //
NK129(to)001:3655: kha cig spyod pa bde spyod kyang //
NK129(to)001:3656: mnyam pa'i lta ba ga la yod //
NK129(to)001:3658: rnal 'byor yo ga la bzhi las /
NK129(to)001:3664: don dam skye 'gag med pa'i 'od gsal stong pa nyid la /
NK129(to)001:3665: kun rdzob tu rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:3667: mngon par byang chub lnga'i sgo nas lha'i sku bskyed de /
NK129(to)001:3668: stong pa nyid las mngon par byang chub pa /
NK129(to)001:3669: gdan pad zla las byang chub pa /
NK129(to)001:3672: sku yongs su rdzogs pa las byang chub pa dang lngas dam tshig pa bskyed /
NK129(to)001:3674: mchod bstod bzlas pa byas nas /
NK129(to)001:3675: spun nam grogs po'i tshul gyis dngos grub zhu ba'o //
NK129(to)001:3677: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la longs spyod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3679: mi tshe lnga'am gsum tshun chad kyis stug po bkod pa'i sa thob par 'dod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3681: khyed yo ga ba ni lta ba don dam skye 'gag med pa de la /
NK129(to)001:3683: yod na skyes 'gag med pa ma yin te /
NK129(to)001:3684: dgag sgrub can du thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3685: med na dam rdzas lnga 'gogs sam ma 'gogs mi 'gogs na de yo ga'i gzhung ma yin te /
NK129(to)001:3687: 'gegs dgag sgrub can du thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3689: spal pas mkha' lding byas kyang rang gi srog dang bral /
NK129(to)001:3690: yo gas skye med bsgoms kyang gnas lugs don mi mthong //
NK129(to)001:3692: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:3695: man ngag a ti yo ga'i //
NK129(to)001:3696: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:3700: don dam par rig pa spros pa dang bral ba
NK129(to)001:3701: la snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi skur lhun gyis
NK129(to)001:3704: e ma phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben /
NK129(to)001:3705: snyigs ma lnga nyid dag pa'i zhing //
NK129(to)001:3706: phung po lnga nyid bde ldan gnas //
NK129(to)001:3707: thams cad mchog gi snying po las //
NK129(to)001:3708: gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi rtsal //
NK129(to)001:3709: nyid las gzhan zhes bya ba'i chos //
NK129(to)001:3710: rtsal kyang rgyal bas mi rnyed do //
NK129(to)001:3713: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK129(to)001:3715: kun rdzob tu rig pa sgyu ma'i rtsal /
NK129(to)001:3716: rtogs tshogs lha dang lha mo'i rang bzhin du ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:3718: kye phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK129(to)001:3719: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK129(to)001:3721: phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK129(to)001:3722: 'byung ba lnga nyid rigs kyi yum //
NK129(to)001:3723: khams dang skye mched mang po kun //
NK129(to)001:3724: byang chub sems dpa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK129(to)001:3726: de gnyis kyang snang stong phyogs re ba ma yin te /
NK129(to)001:3727: snang stong nges mnyam gyi shes bya bden pa dbyer med la /
NK129(to)001:3728: dbyer med tsam du'ang mi 'dzin pas /
NK129(to)001:3729: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba'o //
NK129(to)001:3730: bden pa dbyer med yin pa yang //
NK129(to)001:3732: bden pa gnyis kar dbyer med pas /
NK129(to)001:3733: 'phrul dag'i tshul de tha dad min //
NK129(to)001:3735: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral bar yang /
NK129(to)001:3736: lam rim las de min zhen pa grol phyir las //
NK129(to)001:3737: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das //
NK129(to)001:3739: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3740: chos nyid de bzhin sgom pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3743: mtshan ma bsgom pa'i rim pa dang //
NK129(to)001:3744: de bzhin nyid du bsgom pa ste /
NK129(to)001:3745: bye brag rnam pa gnyis su gsungs /
NK129(to)001:3747: chos nyid de bzhin nyid bsgoms pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3748: dbang po rnon pos lta ba rtogs pa'i don la
NK129(to)001:3749: goms par bya ba'i phyir sems ma bcos par 'jog
NK129(to)001:3750: pa ste / bsam bya bsam par mi bya ste //
NK129(to)001:3751: mi bsam par yang mi bsam mo //
NK129(to)001:3752: gang la rnam par mi bsam pa //
NK129(to)001:3755: 'dzin rtsol med pa'i sems kyi 'du zhes so //
NK129(to)001:3756: mtshan bcas lha sgom pa la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3757: lam dgos pas sgom pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3758: nges par yongs rdzogs sgom pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3760: nub gcig gi bskyed rim lta bu ste /
NK129(to)001:3761: ting nge 'dzin gsum la brten nas /
NK129(to)001:3762: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed spyan drangs mchod cing bsnyen pa 'bul /
NK129(to)001:3763: brtan pa ma thob kyang rnam pa tsam du nga rgyal tsam bsgom pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3765: lam kun skad cig chas bsgoms na //
NK129(to)001:3766: spros pa'i 'khor lo mi sgom zhing //
NK129(to)001:3768: nges pa yongs rdzogs sgom pa gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3769: lam zag bcas dang zag med do //
NK129(to)001:3774: bar chad med pa'i lam du tshogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3776: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK129(to)001:3777: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK129(to)001:3778: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK129(to)001:3780: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen mthong //
NK129(to)001:3781: rang rig snying rje ye shes gzigs //
NK129(to)001:3782: phyag rgya gcig kun 'bras bu'i lha //
NK129(to)001:3783: thams cad gsal ba'i lta ba dang //
NK129(to)001:3784: bar chad med pa'i tshogs chen mthong /
NK129(to)001:3785: dbang bsgyur mnyam nyid mi g.yo ba //
NK129(to)001:3786: ye shes kun ldan lha grangs dgu zhes so //
NK129(to)001:3787: spyod pa ni thabs kyi zin pa'i sgo nas /
NK129(to)001:3788: 'khor ba'i chos nyi shu rtsa lnga la spyod de /
NK129(to)001:3790: mi spang par bya ba lnga /
NK129(to)001:3796: bar do la yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3798: khyed ma h+aa yo ga'i dbyer med spyod yul dang
NK129(to)001:3799: bral ba de la gtan la dbab du yod dam
NK129(to)001:3800: med / med na spyod yul dang bral ba de rtogs su mi stub ste /
NK129(to)001:3801: gtan la dbab tu med pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3802: dper na mig gi sgra snyan mi snyan ma rtogs pa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:3803: gtan la dbab tu yod na /
NK129(to)001:3805: de blos gtan la 'bebs pa yin nam min /
NK129(to)001:3806: yin na blo'i spyod yul dang bral ba'i dam bca' bud /
NK129(to)001:3807: blo'i spyod yul min te blos gtan la mi phebs so zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3808: 'o na ji ltar gtan la 'bebs te /
NK129(to)001:3809: gtan la phabs su mi stub bo //
NK129(to)001:3811: dper na nam mkha' ma grub pa la ma grub pa la grub par gtan la phebs pa'i blos /
NK129(to)001:3812: dbyibs dang kha dog tsam stong pa tsam du blo yul na yod kyang /
NK129(to)001:3813: nam mkha' la 'di yin bya ba gcig grub nas blo yul na yod pa min pa bzhin du /
NK129(to)001:3814: 'dir yang snang stong tha dad kyi zhen pa dgag
NK129(to)001:3815: pa'i phyir dbyer med du brjod kyis dbyer med la
NK129(to)001:3816: 'di yin gyi spyod yul dang bral /
NK129(to)001:3817: spyod yul dang bral ba tsam du gtan la 'beb pa'i blo yod kyang /
NK129(to)001:3818: dbyer med la 'di lta bu gcig yin gyi ngos
NK129(to)001:3819: bzung dang bral ba'i spyod yul dang bral ba yin
NK129(to)001:3820: no zer na / nam mkha' dngos po med pa la stong par gtan la phabs pas /
NK129(to)001:3821: stong par yid ches pa'i blo yod kyis /
NK129(to)001:3822: khyed kyi dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba la /
NK129(to)001:3823: spyod yul dang bral ba tsam du gtan la 'bebs pa'i blo yod pa mi 'gegs kyis /
NK129(to)001:3824: spyod yul dang bral ba tsam du rtogs pa'i nges shes yod dam med /
NK129(to)001:3825: nges shes med na don la spros pas mi chod pas /
NK129(to)001:3826: yang dag pa'i lta ba ma yin par thal /
NK129(to)001:3827: nges shes yod na de ka blo'i spyod yul yin nam min /
NK129(to)001:3828: min de spyod yul dang bral ba la nges shes gang lta bu gcig skye te mi srid la /
NK129(to)001:3829: blo yin na blo'i spyod lus dang bral ba'i dam bca' bud /
NK129(to)001:3830: yang gnas lugs blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pa la /
NK129(to)001:3831: ma gyur bar yid ches pa tsam yin no zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3832: yid ches pa'i blo de gang gi spong ste /
NK129(to)001:3834: lung a nu yo ga la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:3837: lta ba ni yul pas snang ba ni dbyings skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin /
NK129(to)001:3838: yum kun tu bzang mo'i mkha'/
NK129(to)001:3839: rig pa nang nas 'char ba ni ye shes 'gag pa med pa kun tu bzang po'i rol pa /
NK129(to)001:3840: de gnyis gnyis su med pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3841: dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sras bde ba
NK129(to)001:3842: chen po'i rang bzhin du ye nas sangs rgyas par
NK129(to)001:3843: 'dod la / kun tu bzang po'i rol pa /
NK129(to)001:3844: ma 'gags pa'i rtsa lha'i skur 'char bar 'dod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3846: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas gdal ba la //
NK129(to)001:3847: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK129(to)001:3848: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //
NK129(to)001:3850: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:3854: lta ba'i ngang nas ma bcos par 'jog ste /
NK129(to)001:3855: mtshan ma med pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK129(to)001:3857: ji bzhin pa yi chos nyid la //
NK129(to)001:3858: de bzhin pa yi blo bzhag nas //
NK129(to)001:3859: brjod pa med pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK129(to)001:3860: ma yengs rgyun du dran pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3863: lha'i sku grangs dang mdog dbyibs ma nges pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3864: nges pa can ci rigs su /
NK129(to)001:3865: sngags brjod pa tsam gyis chu las nya ldang gi tshul du bskyed pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3867: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //
NK129(to)001:3868: byung dang 'byung 'gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK129(to)001:3871: rgyud lung nyi shu rtsa gcig gi sgo nas sems can gyi don byed pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3873: tshe gcig gis yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis sa thob par 'dod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3875: khyed a nu yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK129(to)001:3876: dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i bde ba chen por sangs rgyas nas /
NK129(to)001:3877: lha chu las nya ldang ba'i tshul gyis sgom dgos sam mi dgos //
NK129(to)001:3878: mi dgos pas mi sgom na sgom par bshad pa 'gal /
NK129(to)001:3880: sangs rgyas pa don med du thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3883: de ltar ye nas sangs rgyas kyang /
NK129(to)001:3884: de ltar ma rtogs pa rtogs pa bya ba'i phyir sgom dgos so //
NK129(to)001:3886: ye nas yin pa la bsgoms pas bskyed byung ngam ma byung /
NK129(to)001:3887: ma byung na bsgom pa don med du thal /
NK129(to)001:3888: bskyed byung na gzhi 'pho 'gyur can du thal /
NK129(to)001:3890: de steng du lhag pa'i skyed byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3892: ngo bo la skyed med kyang don rtogs ma rtogs kyi skyed yod do zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3893: 'o na lta ba'i dus su yang nyid kyi sras bde ba chen po de rtogs sam ma rtogs /
NK129(to)001:3894: ma rtogs na lta ba ma yin par thal /
NK129(to)001:3895: rtogs na bsgom kyang mi 'byung bar thal /
NK129(to)001:3896: 'dod na bsgoms pa don med du thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3897: man ngag a ti yo ga la bzhi ste /
NK129(to)001:3902: bye brag tu gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3904: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK129(to)001:3905: thig le chen po chos kyi sku rang byung gi ye shes chen po'i ngo bor /
NK129(to)001:3906: bya rtsol med par ye nas sangs rgyas par gnas pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3909: rang byung ye shes rtsal mched pas /
NK129(to)001:3910: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston /
NK129(to)001:3913: rang byung ye shes kun tu ji bzhin gnas /
NK129(to)001:3915: bye brag tu gtan la dbab pa la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:3916: gzhi dngos po'i gnas lugs bstan pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3917: de ltar ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i tshul bstan pa dang /
NK129(to)001:3918: 'khrul pa ye shes su gtan la dbab pa bstan pa'o //
NK129(to)001:3919: dang po dngos po'i gnas lugs ni /
NK129(to)001:3920: gzhi chos bzhi ldan yin te /
NK129(to)001:3921: sems kyi rang bzhin shes bya dngos po'i gnas lugs te /
NK129(to)001:3922: rang gi ngo bo tsam yang ma grub par kun
NK129(to)001:3923: la khyab par nam mkha' lta bu gcig yin ngos
NK129(to)001:3924: bzung med par cir yang 'char ba nor bu'i dgos
NK129(to)001:3926: snang gzhi ma grub par snang ba dngos med phyogs
NK129(to)001:3927: med du 'char ba rmi lam lta bu gcig yin
NK129(to)001:3928: / bcos slad med pa ye nas chen por gnas
NK129(to)001:3929: pa gser sa le sbram lta bu gcig yin no
NK129(to)001:3930: / // ma rtogs te 'khrul pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:3931: gang las 'khrul pa'i gzhi dang gcig ji ltar 'khrul pa'i tshul dang gnyis /
NK129(to)001:3932: de ltar 'khrul pa'i 'bras bu gsum mo //
NK129(to)001:3933: dang po gang las 'khrul pa'i gzhi la gsum ste /
NK129(to)001:3934: gzhi la yod pa las 'khrul na /
NK129(to)001:3935: 'khrul pa spang gis mi spong bar 'gyur te /
NK129(to)001:3936: gzhi la yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK129(to)001:3937: gzhi la 'khrul pa med kyang 'khrul na /
NK129(to)001:3938: rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas la 'khrul pa 'byung bar thal lo //
NK129(to)001:3939: 'o na ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:3941: 'khrul pa la gzhi yod par thag pa la sprul du 'khrul pa lta bu yin te /
NK129(to)001:3942: thag pa la sprul gyi rnam pa gang yang med kyang /
NK129(to)001:3943: sprul du 'khrul pa'i gzhi thag pas byas so //
NK129(to)001:3944: dpe de bzhin du shes bya'i gshis la 'khrul pa'i gzhi gang yang grub pa med kyang /
NK129(to)001:3945: 'khrul pa ni shes bya'i gshis ma rtogs pas byas so //
NK129(to)001:3947: gzhi ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid rang
NK129(to)001:3948: gi ngo bor cir yang ma grub pa la rtsal
NK129(to)001:3951: dran pa rang ngo rang gis ma shes pas lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa rgyu byas /
NK129(to)001:3952: des yul kun la log par brtags pa'i ma rig pas rkyen byas nas /
NK129(to)001:3953: yul rang rgyud du bzung nas /
NK129(to)001:3954: rang gi gzugs brnyan la bden par bzung ba me long dang bzhin lta bur gyur /
NK129(to)001:3955: min pa la yin par bzung ba tho yor la mir 'khrul ba lta bur gyur //
NK129(to)001:3956: rang gi rang bcings pa srin gyi kha chu ltar gyur to //
NK129(to)001:3960: log par 'khrul pa mu stegs rtag chad gnyis /
NK129(to)001:3961: phyogs tsam 'khrul pa theg pa rim pa dgu rnams yin no //
NK129(to)001:3962: 'khrul pa chos nyid du gtan la 'bebs pa la /
NK129(to)001:3963: spyir rdzogs pa chen po la bshad gzhung mang du yod pa las /
NK129(to)001:3971: blo ngo bo nyid du grol ba dang bzhir 'dod /
NK129(to)001:3972: dgongs pa klong chen pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3980: nyams su blang lugs gsum du 'dod do //
NK129(to)001:3981: de rnams kyang grub mtha' phyogs re'i zhen pa dang ma bral ba'o //
NK129(to)001:3982: da res rdzogs pa chen po'i rang gzhung phyin ci
NK129(to)001:3983: ma log pa shes bya mtha' med du gtan la
NK129(to)001:3985: gshis skye ba med pa thig le nyag gcig rtsal 'gag pa med pa rang byung gi ye shes /
NK129(to)001:3986: ngo bo gnyis med rang grol chos kyi sku'i dgongs pa dang gsum mo //
NK129(to)001:3988: shes bya kha phyir bltas te gtan la 'bebs pa dang gcig shes bya kha nang du bltas te /
NK129(to)001:3990: shes bya spyir gtan la 'bebs pa dang gsum /
NK129(to)001:3991: shes bya don thog tu bzhag ste gtan la 'bebs pa dang bzhi'o //
NK129(to)001:3992: dang po shes bya phyir bltas te gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK129(to)001:3993: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos nyid thams cad yang
NK129(to)001:3994: dag par cir yang ma grub par gnas pa ni
NK129(to)001:3995: gshis skye ba med pa thig le nyag gcig go
NK129(to)001:3996: /'khor 'das snod bcud sna tshogs su snang ba ni
NK129(to)001:3997: rtsal 'gag pa med pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK129(to)001:3998: so // de ltar snang yang stong pa'i gzugs brnyan cir yang 'char ba'i rtsal las /
NK129(to)001:3999: rang rgyud du 'dzin pa gang yang med par gnas pa ni /
NK129(to)001:4000: ngo bo gnyis med rang grol chos kyi sku'i dgongs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4001: shes bya kha nang du bltas te gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK129(to)001:4002: sems kyi rang bzhin cir yang ma grub pa ni gshis skye ba med pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4003: bzang rtog ngan rtog cir yang 'char ba ni rtsal 'gags pa med pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4004: ci shar dran stong gnyis med 'dzin pa rang grol
NK129(to)001:4005: du shes pa ni ngo bo gnyis med rang grol
NK129(to)001:4006: lo // shes bya spyir gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK129(to)001:4007: shes pa dang shes byas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK129(to)001:4008: yang dag par na cir yang grub pa med de
NK129(to)001:4009: nam mkha' dwangs pa'i dkyil ltar gnas pa ni gshis
NK129(to)001:4011: cir yang ma grub pa'i ngang las cir yang 'char
NK129(to)001:4012: te nges med phyogs med du 'char ba ni rtsal
NK129(to)001:4013: 'gag pa med pa nam mkha'i cho 'phrul lta bu'o
NK129(to)001:4014: // cir yang shar ba tsam na cir yang ma grub /
NK129(to)001:4015: cir yang ma grub tsam na cir yang 'char te /
NK129(to)001:4016: de gnyis gnyis su med pa rgya mtsho'i gzugs brnyan ltar snang ba ni /
NK129(to)001:4017: ngo bo gnyis med rang grol lo //
NK129(to)001:4018: rnal 'byor pa don thog tu bzhag ste gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK129(to)001:4019: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang gi rig pa
NK129(to)001:4020: byang chub sems kyi 'char lugs su shes par byas
NK129(to)001:4021: la / sems kyis sems la bltas pas cir yang ma grub la /
NK129(to)001:4022: stong nyid blo bral du rjen par mthong ba ni /
NK129(to)001:4023: ston gyi bar snang dwangs pa lta bu ste /
NK129(to)001:4024: gshis skye ba med pa thig le nyag gcig go /
NK129(to)001:4025: stong pa'i ngang las bzang ngan gyi dran rtog cir yang 'char ba ni /
NK129(to)001:4026: stong lam gyi 'grul pa lta bu rtsal 'gag pa med pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4027: de ltar bshad kyang dran pa rang gi ngo bos stong ste rtsa bral rang dwangs chen po //
NK129(to)001:4028: ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang la lhan ne gnas pa ni /
NK129(to)001:4029: bar snang stong pa la nyi ma shar ba lta bu ste /
NK129(to)001:4030: ngo bo rang grol chos kyi sku'i dgongs pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4031: de ni lta ba'i gnas lugs so //
NK129(to)001:4032: bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK129(to)001:4033: lta ba'i ngang bsgom pa dang /
NK129(to)001:4035: lta ba'i ngang sgom ni rtogs pa'i don las ma
NK129(to)001:4036: g.yos par thig le chen po chos kyi sku'i ngang
NK129(to)001:4037: du lhod de shig gi gnas pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4039: lhun gyis gnas pas bzhag pa yin //
NK129(to)001:4042: rdzogs pa chen po la sems 'dzin gyi skor dpag tu med pa zhig bzhugs te /
NK129(to)001:4043: de thams cad kyang gnas lugs rtogs par byed pa'i thabs yin te /
NK129(to)001:4045: rnam grangs brgya stong phrag yas pa //
NK129(to)001:4046: gang ltar bsgrubs kyang rtog med skye //
NK129(to)001:4049: cir snang chos nyid kyi rol par shar ba'i sgo nas //
NK129(to)001:4050: dgag bsgrub dang spang blang med par spyod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4052: bya ba med lta las rnams te //
NK129(to)001:4055: ma bsgrubs lhun gyis grub pa dngos grub chen po 'bras bu /
NK129(to)001:4056: kun tu bzang po dbye ba med pa'i sa la gnas pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4058: bsgrubs med rtsal sprugs smon med pas /
NK129(to)001:4060: de ltar a ti yo ga la theg pa gong mas sun 'don pa med kyang /
NK129(to)001:4061: 'og ma'i rtsod byed yod pas de gsal ba ni /
NK129(to)001:4063: khyed rdzogs pa chen po la thig le chen po
NK129(to)001:4064: chos kyi skur ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod dam
NK129(to)001:4065: mi 'dod / 'dod na de la thos bsam gyis gtan la dbab tu yod dam med /
NK129(to)001:4066: yod na ye nas sangs ma rgyas par thal /
NK129(to)001:4067: med na thos bsam bya mi dgos /
NK129(to)001:4069: ye nas sangs rgyas kyang sangs rgyas par ngo ma
NK129(to)001:4070: shes pa de shes par bya ba'i phyir thos bsam
NK129(to)001:4071: dgos te // dper na dbul mo'i khyim na gter yod kyang /
NK129(to)001:4072: de ngo shes pa ded dpon gyis ngo bstan pa lta bu yin no //
NK129(to)001:4074: ye nas sangs rgyas bdag nyid la gnas pa la //
NK129(to)001:4075: grib ma gzugs kyi dpe bzhin de la rtog pa byung /
NK129(to)001:4077: ye nas sangs rgyas na da ltar 'khor ba 'khrul
NK129(to)001:4078: ba'i snang ba 'char ba 'di ces lan zhe na
NK129(to)001:4079: / chos nyid kyi rol par cir yang shar ba
NK129(to)001:4080: las ma rtogs pas dngos por bzung ba ni 'dod
NK129(to)001:4081: pa'i khams kyi lha gnyid log pa lta bu ste
NK129(to)001:4083: ma nges 'ja' tshon kha dog las //
NK129(to)001:4084: rigs kyi khyad par mngon par snang //
NK129(to)001:4086: 'o na rigs drug gi sdug bsngal sna tshogs su shar ba 'di sangs rgyas yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4087: don las ma g.yos shing rtogs na sangs rgyas yin te /
NK129(to)001:4088: rgyal po dmangs su 'khyams kyang rigs mi 'gyur ba lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:4090: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal byang chub sems //
NK129(to)001:4091: kun tu chub bas rnam par rol //
NK129(to)001:4093: 'o na nyon mongs pa dug lnga po 'di yang sangs rgyas yin nam zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4094: rtogs na sangs rgyas yin te /
NK129(to)001:4095: khyag pa chu las ma 'das pa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:4097: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug kyang //
NK129(to)001:4098: byang chub chen po'i lam las byung //
NK129(to)001:4101: sa rdo ri brag 'di yang sangs rgyas yin nam /
NK129(to)001:4103: rtogs na chos nyid kyi rol pa /
NK129(to)001:4104: rig pa'i rang rtsal 'di kho na ltar sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK129(to)001:4108: 'o na theg pa 'og ma'i dka' thub la don med dam zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4109: ye nas sangs rgyas ba'i don rtogs par du dgos te /
NK129(to)001:4111: rnam grangs brgya stong phrag yas pa //
NK129(to)001:4112: gang ltar bsgrubs kyang mi rtog skye //
NK129(to)001:4115: 'gro ba las ngan sna tshogs byed pa 'di yang sangs rgyas yin nam /
NK129(to)001:4117: rtogs na las kyi dbang du mi 'gro ba sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK129(to)001:4119: khyad par cir yang mtshungs pa la //
NK129(to)001:4120: las so zhes ni rnam par brtags //
NK129(to)001:4121: ji ltar las kyi dbang mi 'gyur //
NK129(to)001:4124: sa lam rim par bsgrod du med dam zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4127: lam med lam du 'jug par 'dod pas lam gyi
NK129(to)001:4128: gnad che sar phyin par 'dod pas ri dwags smrig
NK129(to)001:4131: 'o na sangs rgyas pa'i chos 'ga' tsam yod do zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4132: rtogs bar 'khor ba bya ba grub pa med de /
NK129(to)001:4133: thams cad sangs rgyas kyi ngo bor gnas pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:4135: lhag ma med pa yongs su rdzogs //
NK129(to)001:4137: shes bya'i yul ngos 'dzin par byed pa shes byed skyes bu'i blo bstan pa ste /
NK129(to)001:4138: sa gcod kyi dmigs pa gnyis pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4139: spyi don gsum pa de gnyis su med pa /
NK129(to)001:4140: shes bya dngos po'i gnas lugs ni /
NK129(to)001:4141: de ltar shes bya'i yul dang //
NK129(to)001:4144: theg pa'i mtha' ji snyed pa rnams tha dad du yod dam zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4145: yang dag pa'i don la shes bya dngos po don gyi gnas lugs shes pa dang /
NK129(to)001:4149: rtsal gang du yang ma 'gags la /
NK129(to)001:4150: yang dag par na ci yang grub pa med de /
NK129(to)001:4151: de la dpe don gnyis las /
NK129(to)001:4153: shes pa dang shes bya gnyis su snang yang /
NK129(to)001:4154: rang rang gi ngo bo tha dad du grub pa med pa ni /
NK129(to)001:4155: bzhin dang me long lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:4156: me long nang gi bzhin dang /
NK129(to)001:4157: rang gi bzhin gnyis la tha dad par snang yang gnyis su grub pa med pa ltar du /
NK129(to)001:4158: shes pa dang shes bya'i chos /
NK129(to)001:4159: yul dang yul can tha dad snang yang /
NK129(to)001:4160: rang gi ngo bo dang dbyer med de //
NK129(to)001:4161: shes pa phyi yul gyi gzugs brnyan ltar du shar /
NK129(to)001:4162: phyi shes bya'i yul nyid shes pa'i gzugs brnyan yin te /
NK129(to)001:4164: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK129(to)001:4165: sna tshogs kha dog dbyibs su snang //
NK129(to)001:4167: 'o na shes pa dang shes bya'i ngo bo dbyer med na /
NK129(to)001:4168: de gnyis ka yang dag tu grub pa yod dam zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4169: yang dag tu grub pa med de /
NK129(to)001:4171: chos rnams rang gi sems su blos rtogs nas /
NK129(to)001:4172: de nas sems kyang med par rig par bya /
NK129(to)001:4174: yang dag par grub pa med na /
NK129(to)001:4175: da lta snod bcud sna tshogs su snang ba'i ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4176: stong pa las rig pa shar /
NK129(to)001:4177: rig pa'i rtsal dug lngar shar /
NK129(to)001:4178: dug lnga'i rtsal 'byung ba lngar shar nas phyi nang
NK129(to)001:4179: snod bcud kyi 'khrul snang cir yang shar ba yin
NK129(to)001:4180: te / nam mkha' stong pa las 'byung ba bzhi 'char ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:4182: nam mkha'i rang bzhin de la 'byung ba'i dran pa skye /
NK129(to)001:4184: de ltar snod bcud kyi 'khrul pa sna tshogs su shar yang /
NK129(to)001:4185: yang dag pa'i don las g.yos pa med de /
NK129(to)001:4186: 'byung ba bzhis nam mkha' las 'phags ma nus pa lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:4188: 'gre ldog spyi gtsug gar song yang //
NK129(to)001:4189: snying po don las g.yos pa med //
NK129(to)001:4191: yang dag pa'i don phyin ci ma log pa de rtogs na /
NK129(to)001:4192: nam rtogs pa na grol ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:4193: de ltar rtogs yod na chos ci dgos shes na /
NK129(to)001:4194: de ma rtogs na grol ba nam yang med de /
NK129(to)001:4196: bsam gtan rdzun pas thar pa thob bam ci /
NK129(to)001:4198: yang dag pa'i don des sems can thams cad la khyab bam ma khyab zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4199: til 'bru la mar gyis khyab pa ltar bgos pa med par mnyam par khyab ste /
NK129(to)001:4200: de yang bde gshegs snying pos 'gro kun yongs la khyab /
NK129(to)001:4202: sems can thams cad bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po can du mnyam na /
NK129(to)001:4203: dbang po la rno brtul yong ba ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4205: rang bzhin gyis dbang po la rno rtul yong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK129(to)001:4206: sems can 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas 'khrul kyang mnyam du 'khrul /
NK129(to)001:4207: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po yod par mnyam ste /
NK129(to)001:4208: las ngan tshabs che chung byung gis /
NK129(to)001:4210: des chos nyid rtogs dka' sla rim par byung bas dbang po rno rtul du gyur pa yin no //
NK129(to)001:4211: dper na me long yongs su dwangs par mnyam kyang /
NK129(to)001:4212: dri ma srab thug gis gsal mi gsal du snang ba bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:4215: gnas ngan len sgrib pa de ji tsam gyis dag par gyur /
NK129(to)001:4217: gnas ngan len gyi sgrib pa ni bskal pa grangs med pas sam /
NK129(to)001:4220: skad cig yud tsam gyis kyang dag par 'gyur te /
NK129(to)001:4222: gnas ngan len gyi dri ma tshan che chung gi dbang gis so //
NK129(to)001:4224: sbyangs pa'i dbang po la rno rtul yong ba'i rgyu mtshan yang /
NK129(to)001:4225: gnas ngan lenagyi dri ma tshan che chung mnyam yang /
NK129(to)001:4226: skye ba gong ma sbyangs pa che chung gi bye brag gis /
NK129(to)001:4227: 'di la dbang po rno rtul du 'gyur ba yin te /
NK129(to)001:4229: lcags kyi rgyu mnyam po la /
NK129(to)001:4230: rkyen mgal ba mkhas mi mkhas kyi khyad kyis mtshon rno brtul byung ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:4231: thos dang bsam la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK129(to)001:4232: shes rab mig ldan rnams kyis bzungs //
NK129(to)001:4234: yang shes bya de kho na nyid tha dad med cing gcig tu gnas /
NK129(to)001:4235: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos theg pa du ma gsungs pa ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4238: ma bu tsha mang po gso ba de /
NK129(to)001:4239: bu tsha'i lo tshod dang sbyar nas /
NK129(to)001:4240: kha zas rigs mi 'dra ba ster ba ltar du /
NK129(to)001:4241: sangs rgyas kyis kyang gdul bya'i dbang po'i rim pa
NK129(to)001:4242: dang sbyar nas theg pa du ma gsungs pa yin
NK129(to)001:4243: te / rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK129(to)001:4244: nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen
NK129(to)001:4245: por chos kyi sgo mo stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa
NK129(to)001:4250: sangs rgyas rnams kyis de kho na nyid kyi theg pa gcig las ma gsungs kyang /
NK129(to)001:4251: gdul bya rnams kyis rang rang gi dbang po dang
NK129(to)001:4252: mthun par chos theg pa tha dad du thos te
NK129(to)001:4253: / thub pa sbrid pa sangs pa bzhin no //
NK129(to)001:4255: ngas ni gzugs kyi de bzhin nyid gcig pu las ma gsungs te /
NK129(to)001:4256: la las ni gzugs stong zhes bya bar thos /
NK129(to)001:4257: la las ni gzugs mi stong zhes bya bar thos so //
NK129(to)001:4260: gsang nyid nges par 'jug par du /
NK129(to)001:4261: theg pa'i sgo yang bsam mi khyab /
NK129(to)001:4262: gsang nyid snying por nges pa ni /
NK129(to)001:4263: theg pa'i sgo yang gcig las med //
NK129(to)001:4265: yang theg pa tha dad du byung ba dang gang
NK129(to)001:4266: zag dbang po'i rim pa dang bstun pa yin na
NK129(to)001:4267: / gang zag gcig la sa lam gyi rim pa mang po 'ong ba ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4268: dper na zla ba la 'pheb 'grib med kyang rang
NK129(to)001:4269: gi sgrib ma'i bye brag gis 'pheb 'grib du snang
NK129(to)001:4270: ba ltar du / sems can gyi gnas lugs la 'gyur ba med kyang /
NK129(to)001:4271: de rtogs tshabs che chung gi bye brag gis sa
NK129(to)001:4272: lam la mtho dman yod par snang ba yin te
NK129(to)001:4275: rang gi sems kyang rim gyi 'phel //
NK129(to)001:4276: de la sa zhes btags par zad //
NK129(to)001:4279: yang chos thams cad mthar thug sems nyid gtan la phab pa la mthun pa las /
NK129(to)001:4280: sems kyi rang bzhin la bzang ngan dang che chung med pa la /
NK129(to)001:4281: grub mtha' re re la mthar thug gi rtogs pa
NK129(to)001:4282: mi 'dra ba re re 'ong ba ji ltar yin
NK129(to)001:4283: zhe na / dper na ri rab kyi kha dog dang /
NK129(to)001:4284: lung pa'i dbyibs la brten nas nam mkha' la kha dog dang dbyibs su mthong ba ltar du /
NK129(to)001:4285: theg pa rim pa dgu pos kyang /
NK129(to)001:4286: chos nyid dngos med phyogs med la /
NK129(to)001:4287: blo ngos can du mthong nas rang 'dod kyi lta ba re re byed de /
NK129(to)001:4288: de goms 'dris kyi bstan pa thob pas chos nyid
NK129(to)001:4289: dam sems nyid kyi phyogs re re tsam mthong ba
NK129(to)001:4290: yin te / kun byed rgyal po las /
NK129(to)001:4291: yod ni gcig las med pa la //
NK129(to)001:4292: bstan ni rnam pa gnyis su bstan //
NK129(to)001:4293: byung ni theg pa rims dgur byung //
NK129(to)001:4297: sems kyi rang bzhin byang chub kyi sems rnam pa dag pa la /
NK129(to)001:4298: 'khrul pa sna tshogs su 'char ba 'di ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4299: dper na nam mkha'i rang bzhin stong par gnas pa'i yon tan gyis /
NK129(to)001:4300: rtsal 'gags med cho 'phrul sna tshogs su shar ba ltar du /
NK129(to)001:4301: sems kyi rang bzhin stong pa yin pa'i gnad kas /
NK129(to)001:4302: rtsal 'gags med sna tshogs su shar ba yin no //
NK129(to)001:4304: nam mkha'i rang bzhin de las 'byung ba'i dran pa skye /
NK129(to)001:4306: yang sems nyid stong pa las sems kyi rtsal dngos por 'char ba ji lta bu zhe na /
NK129(to)001:4307: dper na lcags phag grang mo las rkyen dbang gis me tsha mo 'byung ba ltar /
NK129(to)001:4308: sems stong par ma rtogs pas 'khrul pa'i rkyen gyis
NK129(to)001:4309: sems kyi rtsal bden bden yod yod ltar shar ba
NK129(to)001:4310: yin te / skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK129(to)001:4312: yang stong pa'i rtsal dngos por shar bar snang yang dngos por yod pa ma yin te /
NK129(to)001:4313: rmi lam bden par bzung ba lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:4315: dngos po med la dngos po'i sprin //
NK129(to)001:4316: sna tshogs rnam par 'byung ba snang //
NK129(to)001:4318: mdor na kun rdzob 'khrul snang la gang du'ang snang /
NK129(to)001:4320: 'di yin 'di min med de sngor snang dgu 'gyur gyi rtsa ba lta bu'o //
NK129(to)001:4321: yang dag par na gnas lugs kyi don la 'di yin med de /
NK129(to)001:4325: chos thams cad gzhi bzhengs gtan bzhengs su ye gdod ma nas chos skur yod pa'o //
NK129(to)001:4326: de yang chos sku khyab pa cig pa'i phyir /
NK129(to)001:4329: theg pa du ma'i don rtogs te /
NK129(to)001:4330: ma rtogs log rtog blo yi the tshom spros bcad nas //
NK129(to)001:4331: shes bya'i gnas lugs ji bzhin gtan la phab pa'i don //
NK129(to)001:4332: rog gi ban+d+he shes rab 'od kyis yi ger bkod //
NK129(to)001:4333: de las byung ba'i dge ba stobs chen rab 'phel nas //
NK129(to)001:4334: 'gro kun shes bya'i gnas lugs mthar phyin rtogs par shog /
NK129(to)001:4335: shes bya'i don gsal bar ston pa chos kyi 'byung
NK129(to)001:4336: gnas grub mtha' chen mo bstan pa'i sgron me zhes
NK129(to)001:4344: bla ma rog gi ban+d+he shes rab 'od kyis mdzad
NK129(to)001:4345: pa'i grub mtha' chos 'byung chen po bstan pa'i sgron
NK129(to)001:4346: me 'di la gzhan dang gzhan las 'phags pa'i khyad
NK129(to)001:4347: nor du mas phyug kyang dpe rgyun dkon pas /
NK129(to)001:4348: rab byung bcu drug pa'i nang bses lcags pho rta'i
NK129(to)001:4349: lor 'bras ljongs khang gsar bla ma o rgyan bstan
